INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(1, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:20', '2019-08-23 17:43:33', 1, 'Laravel Debugbar không hiển thị trên Laravel 5.2', 'laravel-debugbar-khong-hien-thi-tren-laravel-52', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p><img src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/user/1/logo-laravel.png\" /><br />\r\nNếu bạn đ&atilde; c&agrave;i package&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/barryvdh/laravel-debugbar\" target=\"_blank\">Laravel Debugbar</a>&nbsp;m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng hiển thị ra view mặc d&ugrave; đ&atilde; config th&igrave; h&atilde;y thử c&aacute;ch n&agrave;y</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Mở cmd root website (Shift + Mouse Right -&gt; Open command window here)</li>\r\n	<li>Clear cache:&nbsp;<code>php artisan cache:clear</code></li>\r\n	<li>Refresh config cache:&nbsp;<code>php artisan config:cache</code></li>\r\n	<li>Refresh route:&nbsp;<code>php artisan route:clear</code></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-debugbar-khong-hien-thi-tren-laravel-5-2', 9, 1, 'Laravel Debugbar không hiển thị trên Laravel 5.2', 'Nếu bạn đã cài package&nbsp;Laravel Debugbar&nbsp;mà không hiển thị ra view mặc dù đã config thì hãy thử cách này', 'laravel-debugbar-khong-hien-thi-tren-laravel-52', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Nếu bạn đã cài package&nbsp;Laravel Debugbar&nbsp;mà không hiển thị ra view mặc dù đã config thì hãy thử cách này'),
(2, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:22', '2019-09-05 15:02:20', 1, 'Lỗi Laravel: 1071 - Specified key was too long; max key length is 767 bytes', 'loi-laravel-1071-specified-key-was-too-long-max-key-length-is-767-bytes', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p><img alt=\"Lỗi Laravel: 1071 - Specified key was too long; max key length is 767 bytes\" height=\"290\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/sqlstate42000-syntax-error-or-access-violation-1071-specified-key-was-too-long-max-key-length-is-767-bytes.png\" title=\"Lỗi Laravel: 1071 - Specified key was too long; max key length is 767 bytes\" width=\"600\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Lỗi n&agrave;y xảy ra khi d&ugrave;ng lệnh <code>php artisan migrate</code></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n l&agrave; những cột được string được đ&aacute;nh index với kiểu m&atilde; db (utf8mb4) sẽ <strong>kh&ocirc;ng được vượt qu&aacute; 191</strong> k&yacute; tự.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">Trong file migration <code>database\\migrations\\2017_04_12_052246_create_abcxyz_table.php</code> c&oacute; d&ograve;ng $table-&gt;string(&#39;column&#39;); n&ecirc;n đổi th&agrave;nh&nbsp;$table-&gt;string(&#39;column&#39;, 255);</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong<code> project_name\\app\\Providers\\AppServiceProvider.php</code> function&nbsp;<code>boot()</code> th&ecirc;m đoạn code n&agrave;y v&agrave;o:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #99cc00;\">Update 2017-06-11</span>: khai b&aacute;o class <code>use Illuminate\\Support\\Facades\\Schema;</code> ở đầu file nếu k sẽ bị b&aacute;o lỗi nh&eacute; (Thanks&nbsp;<a class=\"UFICommentActorName\" dir=\"ltr\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hmh95\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Minh Hiếu Hồ</a>)</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Schema<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">defaultStringLength</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">191</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// mặc định l&agrave; 255</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>M&igrave;nh &aacute;p dụng c&aacute;ch n&agrave;y ok, hi vọng bạn &aacute;p dụng th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng khi gặp lỗi n&agrave;y&nbsp;?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #99cc00;\">Update 2017-09-08</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Với c&aacute;ch tr&ecirc;n th&igrave; to&agrave;n bộ c&aacute;c field <code>varchar</code> kh&ocirc;ng li&ecirc;n quan sẽ bị giảm số lượng k&iacute; tự xuống c&ograve;n 191 v&agrave; đều đ&oacute; l&agrave;m bạn kh&ocirc;ng h&agrave;i l&ograve;ng h&atilde;y l&agrave;m theo c&aacute;ch dưới đ&acirc;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong thư mục<code> database/migrations</code>&nbsp;kiểm tra c&aacute;c file tạo bảng. C&aacute;c trường <code>string</code> m&agrave; c&oacute; <code>index</code> hoặc <code>unique</code> th&igrave; th&ecirc;m tham số thứ 2 l&agrave; 191 v&agrave;o l&agrave; ổn.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// File database\\migrations\\2014_10_12_000000_create_users_table.php</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;email&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">unique</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Th&agrave;nh</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;email&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">191</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">unique</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// File database\\migrations\\2014_10_12_100000_create_password_resets_table.php</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;email&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">index</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Th&agrave;nh</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;email&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">191</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">index</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/loi-laravel-1071-specified-key-was-too-long-max-key-length-is-767-bytes', 3, 1, 'Lỗi Laravel: 1071 - Specified key was too long; max key length is 767 bytes', '', 'loi-laravel-1071-specified-key-was-too-long-max-key-length-is-767-bytes', '[\"\"]', 1, '');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(3, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:24', '2019-08-23 17:43:33', 1, 'Code Laravel với Sublime Text Editor', 'code-laravel-voi-sublime-text-editor', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>H&ocirc;m nay m&igrave;nh xin được giới thiệu c&aacute;ch coding <strong>Laravel</strong> với <strong>Sublime Text Editor</strong> v&agrave; tận dụng c&aacute;c package của n&oacute; để code nhanh hơn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Đối với những bạn chưa code với <strong>Sublime Text</strong> bao giờ th&igrave; tải tại trang chủ&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.sublimetext.com/3\">https://www.sublimetext.com/3</a>&nbsp;v&agrave; c&agrave;i đặt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Việc tiếp theo l&agrave; c&agrave;i <strong>package control</strong>. <strong>Package control</strong> l&agrave; nơi tập trung c&aacute;c package, ở đ&acirc;y c&oacute; mọi thứ m&agrave; c&aacute;c bạn cần. Trang chủ&nbsp;<a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/\">https://packagecontrol.io/</a>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bckbg4400\">C&agrave;i đặt package control cho sublime text</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Update (03-05-2018):</strong> <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\">Phi&ecirc;n bản release mới nhất đ&atilde; t&iacute;ch hợp package control cho sublime text rồi, chỉ cần thao t&aacute;c Mở sublime text, tr&ecirc;n thanh navbar chọn Tools&nbsp;&rArr; Install Package Control... đợi t&iacute; l&agrave; ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh, ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n tự động kh&ocirc;ng phải thủ c&ocirc;ng như ở dưới nh&eacute;.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;c bạn nhấn tổ hợp ph&iacute;m <code>ctrl</code> + <code>`</code> hoặc <code>View</code>&rarr; <code>Show Console</code> sau đ&oacute; copy đoạn code sau v&ocirc; (đoạn code tr&ecirc;n trang chủ m&igrave;nh copy về&nbsp;?)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/installation#st3\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Code Laravel với Sublime Text Editor\">Sublime Text version 3</a>:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">import urllib.request,os,hashlib; h = &#39;df21e130d211cfc94d9b0905775a7c0f&#39; + &#39;1e3d39e33b79698005270310898eea76&#39;; pf = &#39;Package Control.sublime-package&#39;; ipp = sublime.installed_packages_path(); urllib.request.install_opener( urllib.request.build_opener( urllib.request.ProxyHandler()) ); by = urllib.request.urlopen( &#39;http://packagecontrol.io/&#39; + pf.replace(&#39; &#39;, &#39;%20&#39;)).read(); dh = hashlib.sha256(by).hexdigest(); print(&#39;Error validating download (got %s instead of %s), please try manual install&#39; % (dh, h)) if dh != h else open(os.path.join( ipp, pf), &#39;wb&#39; ).write(by)</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/installation#st2\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Code Laravel với Sublime Text Editor\">Sublime Text version 2</a>:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">import urllib2,os,hashlib; h = &#39;df21e130d211cfc94d9b0905775a7c0f&#39; + &#39;1e3d39e33b79698005270310898eea76&#39;; pf = &#39;Package Control.sublime-package&#39;; ipp = sublime.installed_packages_path(); os.makedirs( ipp ) if not os.path.exists(ipp) else None; urllib2.install_opener( urllib2.build_opener( urllib2.ProxyHandler()) ); by = urllib2.urlopen( &#39;http://packagecontrol.io/&#39; + pf.replace(&#39; &#39;, &#39;%20&#39;)).read(); dh = hashlib.sha256(by).hexdigest(); open( os.path.join( ipp, pf), &#39;wb&#39; ).write(by) if dh == h else None; print(&#39;Error validating download (got %s instead of %s), please try manual install&#39; % (dh, h) if dh != h else &#39;Please restart Sublime Text to finish installation&#39;)</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau khi install package control xong kiểm tra xem <code>Sublime Text</code>&rArr; <code>Preferences</code> &rArr; đ&atilde; c&oacute; <code>Package Control</code> hay chưa, nếu c&oacute; l&agrave; ok rồi c&ograve;n chưa th&igrave; bạn tắt Sublime Text rồi mở lại, nếu vẫn chưa c&oacute; th&igrave; thử c&agrave;i lại lần nữa cũng được&nbsp;?</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bckbg4401\">C&agrave;i đặt package cho sublime text</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><code>Sublime Text</code>&rArr;<code>Preferences</code> &rArr; <code>Package Control</code>&rArr; <code>Install Package</code><br />\r\nhoặc<br />\r\nNhấn tổ hợp <code>Ctrl + Shift + P</code> để mở list command, t&igrave;m kiếm <code>Package Control: Install Package</code> v&agrave; nhấn <code>Enter</code>&nbsp;<br />\r\n&rArr; chờ 1 ch&uacute;t cho n&oacute; load c&aacute;c danh s&aacute;ch package. Sau khi danh s&aacute;ch c&aacute;c package load xong g&otilde; từ kh&oacute;a v&agrave;o để t&igrave;m kiếm package m&igrave;nh cần, chọn v&agrave; <code>enter</code> để c&agrave;i đặt, c&oacute; 1 số package sau khi c&agrave;i cần <strong>restart Sublime Text</strong> mới c&oacute; hiệu lực nha.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bck2ddag0\"><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/LaravelDumpMan\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"LaravelDumpMan\">1. LaravelDumpMan</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Laravel​Dump​Man\" class=\"img-responsive center-block lazy loaded\" data-src=\"https://packagecontrol.io/readmes/img/647bc1204e49b170ffc55dcabb403b1a6c82de38.gif\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"604\" src=\"https://packagecontrol.io/readmes/img/647bc1204e49b170ffc55dcabb403b1a6c82de38.gif\" title=\"Laravel​Dump​Man\" width=\"803\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>G&oacute;i n&agrave;y d&ugrave;ng để debug rất tiện, thay v&igrave; g&otilde; dd(&#39;test&#39;) th&igrave; chỉ cần bấm F1, dd($result) th&igrave; double click v&agrave;o biến nhấn F1.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bck4mmgr3\"><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/Laravel%20Blade%20Highlighter\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Laravel Blade Highlighter\">2. Laravel Blade Highlighter</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Với sự ra đời của Blade View Engineer n&ecirc;n đu&ocirc;i mở rộng *.blade.php kh&ocirc;ng 1 IDE hay Editor n&agrave;o hiểu nổi m&agrave; đưa về PHP file hết. V&igrave; vậy code Laravel bắt buộc phải c&agrave;i package n&agrave;y, hiện đ&atilde; c&oacute; 178K lượt tải</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau khi c&agrave;i xong th&igrave; <strong>restart Sublime Text</strong> để package c&oacute; hiệu lực. Dưới đ&acirc;y l&agrave; h&igrave;nh ảnh khi chưa c&agrave;i package</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Laravel Blade Highlighter\" class=\"img-responsive center-block lazy loaded\" data-src=\"https://packagecontrol.io/readmes/img/d0d30bb824bd0b55a1a1d7bf84be0b98b541ff3a.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://packagecontrol.io/readmes/img/d0d30bb824bd0b55a1a1d7bf84be0b98b541ff3a.jpg\" title=\"Laravel Blade Highlighter\" width=\"554\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&ograve;n đ&acirc;y l&agrave; sau khi c&agrave;i, với việc phủ m&agrave;u sẽ dễ nh&igrave;n hơn khi code phải k n&agrave;o&nbsp;?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Laravel Blade Highlighter\" class=\"img-responsive center-block lazy loaded\" data-src=\"https://packagecontrol.io/readmes/img/b98f3d71c4a1ca81ad881a031310d778fdfa4061.jpg\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://packagecontrol.io/readmes/img/b98f3d71c4a1ca81ad881a031310d778fdfa4061.jpg\" title=\"Laravel Blade Highlighter\" width=\"561\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bckbg4402\"><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/Laravel%205%20Snippets\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Laravel 5 Snippets for Sublime Text\">3.&nbsp;Laravel 5 Snippets for Sublime Text</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Phải n&oacute;i đ&acirc;y l&agrave; 1 package tuyệt vời, x&agrave;i rất đ&atilde;&nbsp;?. B&acirc;y giờ việc code đ&atilde; tr&ecirc;n n&ecirc;n rất chi l&agrave; &quot;phỏe re&quot; hehehe. Với cấu tr&uacute;c&nbsp;{category}::{function name} rất tiện sử dụng, V&iacute; dụ g&otilde; Auth:: l&agrave; n&oacute; ra h&agrave;ng loạt bạn chỉ việc chọn chẳng hạng Auth::check()</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dưới đ&acirc;y l&agrave; c&aacute;c prefix hỗ trợ c&aacute;c bạn chỉ g&otilde; những từ c&oacute; prefix như tr&ecirc;n l&agrave; n&oacute; sẽ liệt k&ecirc; ra cho m&igrave;nh chọn, nếu n&oacute; chưa ra th&igrave; nhấn ph&iacute;m <kbd>Ctrl</kbd> + <kbd>Space</kbd></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">Auth  Blade //Chỉ sử dụng được trong file *.blade.php  Cache  Config  Console  Cookie  Crypt  DB  Event  Hash  Helper  Input  Log  Mail  Redirect  Relation  Response  Route  Schema  Session  Storage  View</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bckbg4403\"><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/LaravelCollective%20HTML%20Form%20Snippets\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"LaravelCollective HTML Form Snippets\">4. LaravelCollective HTML Form Snippets</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Kể từ khi <strong>Laravel n&acirc;ng cấp</strong> l&ecirc;n phi&ecirc;n bản 5.0. Laravel đ&atilde; quyết định loại bỏ package <strong>HTML/Form</strong> ra khỏi core của m&igrave;nh, nhưng vẫn tiếp tục bảo tr&igrave; v&agrave; cung cấp cho người d&ugrave;ng c&agrave;i đặt nếu cần. Ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; sự tiện lợi của n&oacute; n&ecirc;n vẫn được y&ecirc;u th&iacute;ch cho đến tận ng&agrave;y h&ocirc;m nay, <strong>c&agrave;i package n&agrave;y cho Sublime Text n&agrave;y đồng nghĩa với việc bạn phải instal package&nbsp;laravelcollective/html trong Laravel</strong>&nbsp;, bạn c&oacute; thể tham khảo b&agrave;i viết <a href=\"/posts/html-form-class-not-found-error-trong-laravel-5\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"HTML/Form Class not found error trong Laravel 5\">HTML/Form Class not found error trong Laravel 5</a>&nbsp;của m&igrave;nh nếu chưa biết c&aacute;ch c&agrave;i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sử dụng package n&agrave;y bằng c&aacute;ch g&otilde; c&aacute;c từ kh&oacute;a snippets dưới đ&acirc;y, v&agrave; nhấn <code>tab</code> hoặc <code>Ctrl + space</code> l&agrave; ok.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.or