0Snippets\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Laravel Forms Bootstrap Snippets\">5.&nbsp;Laravel Forms Bootstrap Snippets</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Laravel Collective Forms + Bootstrap Snippets for Sublime Text n&agrave;y tương tự như package số 4 ở tr&ecirc;n, package n&agrave;y <strong>hỗ trợ bootstrap</strong>&nbsp;tức l&agrave; ở tr&ecirc;n n&oacute; sẽ ra một c&aacute;i form gọn lỏn kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; g&igrave;, c&ograve;n package n&agrave;y sẽ ra đầy đủ html form theo style bootstrap</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"form-group{{ $errors-&gt;has(\'email\') ? \' has-error\' : \'\' }}\">{!! Form::label(&#39;email&#39;, &#39;Email&#39;) !!} {!! Form::text(&#39;email&#39;, null, [&#39;class&#39; =&gt; &#39;form-control&#39;, &#39;required&#39; =&gt; &#39;required&#39;]) !!} <small class=\"text-danger\">{{ $errors-&gt;first(&#39;email&#39;) }}</small></div>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Laravel Collective Forms + Bootstrap Snippets for Sublime Text\" class=\"img-responsive center-block lazy loaded\" data-src=\"https://packagecontrol.io/readmes/img/1fdc739e3e461f2d69071847215aedb90e8667d2.gif\" data-was-processed=\"true\" height=\"339\" src=\"https://packagecontrol.io/readmes/img/1fdc739e3e461f2d69071847215aedb90e8667d2.gif\" title=\"Laravel Collective Forms + Bootstrap Snippets for Sublime Text\" width=\"962\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dưới đ&acirc;y l&agrave; danh s&aacute;ch <strong>snippets</strong>, hỗ trợ cả <strong>form horizontal</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">General    Form		bootform  Form model	bootformmodel    Inputs    Button		bootbutton  Checkbox	bootcheckbox  Date		bootdate  Email		bootemail  File		bootfile  Hidden		boothidden  Number		bootnumber  Password	bootpassword  Radio		bootradio  Select		bootselect  SelectMonth	bootselectmonth  SelectYear	bootselectyear  SelectRange	bootselectrange  Text		boottextarea  Textarea	boottext    Horizontal inputs    Checkbox	bootcheckboxh  Date		bootdateh  Email		bootemailh  File		bootfileh  Number		bootnumberh  Password	bootpasswordh  Radio		bootradioh  Select		bootselecth  SelectMonth	bootselectmonthh  SelectYear	bootselectyearh  SelectRange	bootselectrangeh  Text		boottextareah  Textarea	boottexth</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bckcrrj60\"><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/Blade%20Snippets\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Blade Snippets\">6.&nbsp;Blade Snippets</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;c package ở tr&ecirc;n cũng đ&atilde; hỗ trợ kha kh&aacute; <strong>Blade View Template Enginee</strong>r rồi nhỉ&nbsp;?&nbsp;nhưng m&igrave;nh vẫn giới thiệu th&ecirc;m package n&agrave;y nữa kaka, c&agrave;i nhiều x&agrave;i cho đ&atilde; chứ chả chết chỉ ai phải kh&ocirc;ng h&ecirc; h&ecirc;&nbsp;?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;i t&ecirc;n đ&atilde; n&oacute;i l&ecirc;n tất cả rồi phải k anh em nhỉ, chỉ hỗ trợ file <code>*.blade.php</code> th&ocirc;i nhen. C&ograve;n key word để <strong>Sublime Text trigger</strong>&nbsp;th&igrave; qu&aacute; trời trời lu&ocirc;n, anh em v&agrave;o đọc xem rồi code v&agrave;i bữa l&agrave; thuộc liền&nbsp;?&nbsp;m&agrave; thấy cũng dễ nhớ, v&iacute; dụ <code>@extends</code> th&igrave; l&agrave; <code>ext</code>, <code>@layout</code> th&igrave; l&agrave; <code>lay</code> hỗ trợ <code>if</code> <code>else</code> <code>for