gger</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/master/helpers#method-method_field\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">method_field</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/master/helpers#method-old\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">old</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/master/helpers#method-redirect\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">redirect</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/master/helpers#method-request\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">request</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/master/helpers#method-response\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">response</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/master/helpers#method-rety\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">rety</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/master/helpers#method-session\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">session</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/master/helpers#method-view\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">view</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/master/helpers#method-value\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">value</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/master/helpers#method-with\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">with</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bckff9l67\"><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/Bootstrap%203%20Snippets\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bootstrap 3 Snippets\">8.&nbsp;Bootstrap 3 Snippets</a>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/Bootstrap%203%20Autocomplete\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Bootstrap&nbsp;3&nbsp;Autocomplete</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Package n&agrave;y hỗ trợ snippets&nbsp;twitter bootstrap css</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;ch sử dụng: g&otilde;<code> bs3-*</code> l&agrave; 1 list danh s&aacute;ch hiện ra cho c&aacute;c bạn tha hồ lựa chọn chẳng hạn <code>bs3-row</code>, <code>bs3-panel</code>, <code>bs3-alert</code>, nếu đ&atilde; quen với css, components, ... của bootstrap rồi th&igrave; x&agrave;i rất lẹ, trang chủ bootstrap cho bạn n&agrave;o chưa biết:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://getbootstrap.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bootstrap 3 Snippets\">http://getbootstrap.com/</a>&nbsp;bản tiếng việt cho bạn n&agrave;o k r&agrave;nh tiếng anh&nbsp;<a href=\"http://getbootstrap.com.vn/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Bootstrap 3 Snippets\">http://getbootstrap.com.vn/</a>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bootstrap 3 AutoComplete sẽ gợi &yacute; cho bạn c&aacute;c class hiện c&oacute; nếu bạn đang g&otilde; thuộc t&iacute;nh class cho html n&oacute; sẽ hiện thị danh s&aacute;ch tương ứng.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%; height: auto; clear: none;\"><ins class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-1450596627252330\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; background-color: transparent;\"><ins id=\"aswift_3_expand\" style=\"display: inline-table; border: none; height: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 698px; background-color: transparent;\"><ins id=\"aswift_3_anchor\" style=\"display: block; border: none; height: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 698px; background-color: transparent; overflow: visible; opacity: 1;\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"175\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_3\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_3\" onload=\"var i=this.id,s=window.google_iframe_oncopy,H=s&amp;&amp;s.handlers,h=H&amp;&amp;H[i],w=this.contentWindow,d;try{d=w.document}catch(e){}if(h&amp;&amp;d&amp;&amp;(!d.body||!d.body.firstChild)){if(h.call){setTimeout(h,0)}else if(h.match){try{h=s.upd(h,i)}catch(e){}w.location.replace(h)}}\" scrolling=\"no\" style=\"left:0;position:absolute;top:0;border:0px;width:698px;height:175px;\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"698\"></iframe></ins></ins></ins></div>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu bạn x&agrave;i bootstrap 4 th&igrave; tương ứng c&oacute; <a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/Bootstrap%204%20Snippets\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Bootstrap 4 Snippets</a> v&agrave; <a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/Bootstrap%204%20Autocomplete\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bootstrap 4 autocomplete</a> lu&ocirc;n nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bckfsacta\"><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/DocBlockr\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"DocBlockr\">9.&nbsp;DocBlockr</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; package d&ugrave;ng để viết document rất th&iacute;ch hợp cho l&agrave;m việc theo nh&oacute;m, dễ bảo tr&igrave; hoặc đơn giản sau n&agrave;y đọc lại hiểu m&igrave;nh viết g&igrave; th&ocirc;i&nbsp;??</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chỉ cần g&otilde; <code>/*</code> hoặc <code>/**</code> nhấn <code>tab</code> hoặc <code>enter</code> l&agrave; n&oacute; sẽ show ra document th&iacute;ch hợp, t&ugrave;y theo vị tr&iacute; đang g&otilde; ở đ&acirc;u<img alt=\"DocBlockr\" class=\"img-responsive center-block lazy\" data-src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/415148aecc6dac2e5ebb12b7f7584f4a8744eca4/687474703a2f2f73706164676f732e6769746875622e696f2f7375626c696d652d6a73646f63732f696d616765732f66756e6374696f6e2d74656d706c6174652e676966\" height=\"192\" src=\"/image/web/lazy.png\" title=\"DocBlockr\" width=\"368\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bckh32feb\"><a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/ApacheConf.tmLanguage\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"10. Apache Conf Syntax Highlighting\">10. Apache Conf Syntax Highlighting</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Package n&agrave;y khi search tr&ecirc;n Package Control l&agrave;&nbsp;Apache​Conf.tm​Language nh&eacute;.<br />\r\nPackage n&agrave;y hỗ trợ đọc c&aacute;c file:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul style=\"list-style-type: square;\">\r\n	<li>.conf</li>\r\n	<li>.htaccess</li>\r\n	<li>.htgroups</li>\r\n	<li>.htpasswd</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bdl5tq4s0\">11. <a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/SublimeLinter\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Sublime​Linter\">Sublime​Linter</a>&nbsp;v&agrave; <a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/SublimeLinter-php\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Sublime​Linter-php\">Sublime​Linter-php</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau khi c&agrave;i xong 2 g&oacute;i n&agrave;y th&igrave; khi code bạn sai c&uacute; ph&aacute;p sẽ tự động b&aacute;o dấu chấm đỏ ở đầu d&ograve;ng hoặc b&ocirc;i đỏ đoạn code rất c&oacute; &iacute;ch với những bạn code l&aacute;u như m&igrave;nh, thiếu chấm phẩy 1 c&aacute;i th&ocirc;i l&agrave; mất cả mớ thời gian để t&igrave;m n&oacute; ở đ&acirc;u..</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Sublime​Linter va Sublime​Linter-php trong sublime text\" class=\"img-responsive center-block lazy\" data-src=\"/image/sublimelinter-va-sublimelinter-php-trong-sublime-text.png\" height=\"200\" src=\"/image/web/lazy.png\" title=\"Sublime​Linter va Sublime​Linter-php trong sublime text\" width=\"400\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1be4efr570\">13. <a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/DeleteBlankLines\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Delete​Blank​Lines\">Delete​Blank​Lines</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>C&agrave;i xong package n&agrave;y khi nhấn tổ hợp ph&iacute;m dưới đ&acirc;y sẽ x&oacute;a hết<code> Blank Line</code> hoặc&nbsp;<code>Surplus Blank Lines</code> <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><em><strong>(Lưu &yacute; phải b&ocirc;i đen đoạn text cần x&oacute;a)</strong></em></span></p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\nWindows: - Ctrl+Alt+Backspace &ndash;&gt; Delete Blank Lines - Ctrl+Alt+Shift+Backspace &ndash;&gt; Delete Surplus Blank Lines\r\n\r\nOSX: - Fn+Ctrl+Option+Delete &ndash;&gt; Delete Blank Lines - Fn+Ctrl+Option+Shift+Delete &ndash;&gt; Delete Surplus Blank Lines\r\n\r\nLinux: - Ctrl+Alt+Backspace &ndash;&gt; Delete Blank Lines - Ctrl+Alt+Shift+Backspace &ndash;&gt; Delete Surplus Blank Lines</pre>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bkanhbcr0\">14. <a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/Autoprefixer\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Autoprefixer\">Autoprefixer</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Đối với những bạn code CSS th&igrave; đ&acirc;y l&agrave; 1 package hữu dụng. Để css &aacute;p dụng tr&ecirc;n mọi tr&igrave;nh duyệt bạn phải viết lại v&agrave; th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o tiếp đầu ngữ, đ&acirc;y đ&uacute;ng l&agrave; 1 c&ocirc;ng việc nh&agrave;m ch&aacute;n phải kh&ocirc;ng n&agrave;o, hơn nữa lại l&agrave; những tay g&agrave; mờ css như dev th&igrave; khỏi phải b&agrave;n rồi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau khi c&agrave;i xong package, mặc định n&oacute; sẽ hỗ trợ tất cả, kể cả IE 7. Tại file css, scss ... nhấn tổ hợp ph&iacute;m Ctrl + Shift + P g&otilde;&nbsp;Autoprefix CSS v&agrave; nhấn Enter l&agrave; ok ngay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Autoprefixer Demo\" class=\"lazy\" data-src=\"https://packagecontrol.io/readmes/img/031788ec7915ae6f8718b8d294a0fdd84f36e6bc.gif\" height=\"332\" src=\"/image/web/lazy.png\" title=\"Autoprefixer Demo\" width=\"874\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bobls6q60\">15. <a href=\"https://packagecontrol.io/packages/EditorConfig\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">EditorConfig</a></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Bạn tự hỏi tại sao lại c&agrave;i g&oacute;i n&agrave;y th&igrave; xem b&agrave;i viết sau đ&acirc;y sẽ r&otilde; hơn nh&eacute;:&nbsp;<a href=\"/posts/chuan-hoa-code-style-tren-editor-ide-bang-editorconfig\" title=\"Chuẩn hóa code style trên Editor/IDE bằng EditorConfig\"><strong>Chuẩn h&oacute;a code style tr&ecirc;n Editor/IDE bằng EditorConfig</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"16._...\">16. ...</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>... c&ograve;n nữa (mong c&aacute;c bạn bổ sung th&ecirc;m cho m&igrave;nh)</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bckdenva1\">Một số mẹo khi x&agrave;i Sublime Text</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1bckdfjvj2\">1. Format code</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>M&igrave;nh thấy l&agrave; anh em rất khổ sở khi code, nhấn tab 3 4 5 lần rồi x&oacute;a v&ocirc; thụt v&agrave;o nh&igrave;n rất tội. Mấy bạn biết rồi đọc đến đ&acirc;y sẽ rất mắc cười phần v&igrave; m&igrave;nh đ&atilde; từng hoặc kh&ocirc;ng biết rằng tại sao lại c&oacute; những người l&agrave;m vậy.&nbsp;?<br />\r\nFormat code l&agrave; 1 h&agrave;nh động l&agrave;m cho code đẹp hơn, thụt ra thụt v&agrave;o ngay h&agrave;ng thẳng lối, c&aacute;c bạn l&agrave;m như sau:<br />\r\n<code>Sublime text</code>&nbsp;&rArr; <code>Preferences</code>&nbsp;&rArr; <code>Key Binddings</code><br />\r\nN&oacute; sẽ hiện ra 1 cửa số mới, b&ecirc;n tr&aacute;i l&agrave; những key mặc định của sublime text b&ecirc;n phải l&agrave; những key m&igrave;nh sẽ add th&ecirc;m v&ocirc;, hiện tại l&agrave; như vầy:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-json\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Th&ecirc;m d&ograve;ng n&agrave;y v&ocirc;:</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"default prettyprint prettyprinted\"><code><span class=\"pun\">{</span> <span class=\"str\">&quot;keys&quot;</span><span class=\"pun\">:</span> <span class=\"pun\">[</span><span class=\"str\">&quot;ctrl+shift+r&quot;</span><span class=\"pun\">],</span> <span class=\"str\">&quot;command&quot;</span><span class=\"pun\">:</span> <span class=\"str\">&quot;reindent&quot;</span> <span class=\"pun\">,</span> <span class=\"str\">&quot;args&quot;</span><span class=\"pun\">:</span> <span class=\"pun\">{</span> <span class=\"str\">&quot;single_line&quot;</span><span class=\"pun\">:</span> <span class=\"kwd\">false</span> <span class=\"pun\">}</span> <span class=\"pun\">}</span></code></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-json\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>      <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>          <span class=\"token property\">&quot;keys&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">&quot;ctrl+shift+r&quot;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>          <span class=\"token property\">&quot;command&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">&quot;reindent&quot;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>          <span class=\"token property\">&quot;args&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">&quot;single_line&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Từ giờ code thụt ra thụt v&ocirc; th&igrave; chỉ cần nhấn <strong>Ctrl + Shift + R</strong> l&agrave; đẹp ngay&nbsp;?</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1bcke12gg3\">2. Comments</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi comments đoạn code kh&ocirc;ng cần thiết hay ch&uacute; th&iacute;ch cho người sau x&agrave;i c&aacute;c bạn hay d&ugrave;ng ph&iacute;m g&igrave;? M&igrave;nh th&igrave; d&ugrave;ng <code>Ctrl + /</code> miết</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">getHTML</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>      <span class=\"token comment\">//đ&acirc;y l&agrave; một function hay v&ocirc; đối      foreach ($variable as $key =&gt; $value) {          # code...      }      # code...        // dưới n&agrave;y m&aacute;t lắm, wifi mạnh code sướng      return $abc;  }</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Điều n&agrave;y sẽ chẳng c&oacute; g&igrave; cho đến một h&ocirc;m ch&uacute;ng ta thay đổi 1 v&agrave;i d&ograve;ng code, thụt ra thụt v&ocirc; kh&ocirc;ng đều v&agrave; <strong>format code</strong> như mẹo số 1 ở tr&ecirc;n th&igrave; &ocirc;i th&ocirc;i những d&ograve;ng <code>//</code> nằm im ru kh&ocirc;ng <strong>format</strong> được&nbsp;?&nbsp;r&otilde; khổ hen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>N&ecirc;n mẹo n&agrave;y l&agrave; chuyển từ <code>Ctrl + /</code> sang <code>Ctrl + Shift + /</code>&nbsp;vẫn l&agrave; <strong>comment</strong> nhưng đẹp hơn, thanh t&uacute; hơn ?&nbsp;nhưng c&oacute; c&aacute;i l&agrave; phải b&ocirc;i đen text rồi nhấn nhen, chứ kh&ocirc;ng được rồi chửi tui ah&nbsp;?</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">getHTML</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>      <span class=\"token comment\">/*đ&acirc;y l&agrave; một function hay v&ocirc; đối*/</span>      <span class=\"token keyword\">foreach</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$variable</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$key</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>          <span class=\"token shell-comment comment\"># code...      }      # code...        </span><span class=\"token comment\">/*do ch&agrave;ng trai kh&ocirc;i ng&ocirc; tuấn t&uacute; viết*/</span>      <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$abc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1bepauf410\">3. Mở một file nhiều lần</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong code của bạn c&oacute; function a gọi đến function b, khổ nỗi thằng nằm đầu thằng nằm đ&iacute;t chả nhẽ k&eacute;o l&ecirc;n k&eacute;o xuống rồi so s&aacute;nh c&aacute;c kiểu. Mẹo ở đ&acirc;y l&agrave; mở file đ&oacute; nhiều lần bằng c&aacute;ch&nbsp;<code>File</code> &rArr; <code>New View into File</code> rồi chỉnh sửa nha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>... c&ograve;n nữa</p>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;c bạn c&oacute; g&igrave; cần bổ sung hay nhận x&eacute;t g&igrave; để lại comments để m&igrave;nh ho&agrave;n thiện b&agrave;i viết nhen&nbsp;?</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/code-laravel-voi-sublime-text-editor', 6, 1, 'Code Laravel với Sublime Text Editor', 'H&ocirc;m nay m&igrave;nh xin được giới thiệu c&aacute;ch coding Laravel với Sublime Text Editor v&agrave; tận dụng c&aacute;c package của n&oacute; để code nhanh hơn.', 'code-laravel-voi-sublime-text-editor', '[\"\"]', 1, 'H&ocirc;m nay m&igrave;nh xin được giới thiệu c&aacute;ch coding Laravel với Sublime Text Editor v&agrave; tận dụng c&aacute;c package của n&oacute; để code nhanh hơn.');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(4, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:26', '2019-08-23 17:43:33', 1, 'Laravel Blade tip: Sử dụng câu lệnh @unless thay vì @if', 'laravel-blade-tip-su-dung-cau-lenh-at-unless-thay-vi-at-if', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p><img alt=\"Laravel Blade tip: Sử dụng câu lệnh @unless thay vì @if\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/laravel_logo/laravel-blade.png\" title=\"Laravel Blade tip: Sử dụng câu lệnh @unless thay vì @if\" width=\"600\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Phải n&oacute;i rằng <strong>Laravel</strong> cung cấp 1 bộ giải m&atilde; <strong>Blade</strong> (engine) hết sức mạnh mẽ v&agrave; linh hoạt t&ugrave;y biến.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi kiểm tra điều kiện g&igrave; đ&oacute; chắc hẳn ch&uacute;ng ta thường nghĩ ngay đến c&acirc;u lệnh if v&agrave; trong <strong>Laravel Blade</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">@<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span>Auth<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">check</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    Vui l&ograve;ng đăng nhập<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\r\n@<span class=\"token keyword\">endif</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>R&otilde; r&agrave;ng n&oacute; sẽ chạy v&agrave; cho ra kết quả đ&uacute;ng, thế nhưng Laravel cung cấp cho ch&uacute;ng ta 1 c&uacute; ph&aacute;p tốt hơn, tr&aacute;nh được lỗi typing cũng như r&otilde; r&agrave;ng hơn đ&oacute; l&agrave; <code>@unless</code></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">@unless <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Auth<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">check</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    Vui l&ograve;ng đăng nhập<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\r\n@endunless</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>??&nbsp;Hehe, th&uacute; vị phải kh&ocirc;ng n&agrave;o!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-blade-tip-su-dung-cau-lenh-atunless-thay-vi-atif', 2, 1, 'Laravel Blade tip: Sử dụng câu lệnh @unless thay vì @if', '', 'laravel-blade-tip-su-dung-cau-lenh-at-unless-thay-vi-at-if', '[\"\"]', 1, ''),
(5, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:28', '2019-08-12 13:09:34', 1, 'Truyền dữ liệu ra View trong Laravel', 'truyen-du-lieu-ra-view-trong-laravel', '<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n              <p>Trong bài viết này, giả sử chúng ta có view <code>welcome.blade.php</code>&nbsp;như sau</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-markup\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-markup\"><span class=\"token doctype\">&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n	<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n	<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Hello, {{ $name }}<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Như vậy để <strong>truyền dữ liệu ra View</strong> (<strong>Passing Data To Views</strong>) chúng ta có các cách như sau đây để trên view <code>welcome.blade.php</code> có thể sử dụng được &nbsp;được biến <code>$name</code>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bak0m1re0\">Cách 1: Truyền vào 1 mảng</h2>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'welcome\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n		<span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'name\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Chung Nguyễn\'</span>\r\n	<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Nếu cần truyền thêm dữ liệu thì thêm vào mảng trên bây nhiêu thôi.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bak131de1\">Cách 2: Sử dụng with method</h2>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'welcome\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">with</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Chung Nguyễn\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Với việc dùng view helper function, chúng ta hoàn toàn có thể pass data to views 1 cách dễ dàng thông qua phương thức with, cũng giống như ở trên nhưng code chúng ta sẽ trở nên sáng sủa, dễ nhìn hơn phải k nào&nbsp;?</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bak18c2l2\">Cách 3: Lồng compact</h2>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$name</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Chung Nguyễn\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'welcome\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">compact</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Cách này trong <a title=\"Laravel document\" href=\"http://chungnguyen.xyz/laravel/docs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Laravel document</a> không có nhắc tới, mình hay dùng cách này vì số lần gõ phím là ít nhất hehe&nbsp;?</p>\r\n<p>Nếu muốn truyền thêm nhiều dữ liệu hơn thì thêm như dưới đây</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$name</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Chung Nguyễn\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$age</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">25</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'welcome\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">compact</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'age\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bak1f9g63\">Cách 4: Chia sẻ dữ liệu cho toàn bộ Views</h2>\r\n<p>Laravel cung cấp phương thức <code>share</code> chia sẻ dữ liệu cho toàn bộ Views (<strong>Sharing Data With All Views</strong>) hay nói cách khác là biến toàn cục.</p>\r\n<p>Thông thường, bạn nên đặt <code>share</code> trong method <code>boot</code> của&nbsp;<code>service provider</code>&nbsp;chẳng hạn <code>app/Providers/AppServiceProvider.php</code> hoặc trong&nbsp;<code>__construct</code> function của Controller</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Providers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Support<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Facades<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>View</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">AppServiceProvider</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ServiceProvider</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Bootstrap any application services.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">boot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        View<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">share</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Chung Nguyễn\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// &lt;= Truyền dữ liệu</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Register the service provider.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">register</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">//</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h2 id=\"Cách_5:_Sử_dụng_composer_truyền_dữ_liệu_cho_một_số_views_được_chỉ_định\">Cách 5: Sử dụng composer truyền dữ liệu cho một số views được chỉ định</h2>\r\n<p>Giống như cách 4 ở trên bạn có thể dùng view composer để truyền dữ liệu cho một số views nhất định, trong <code>AppServiceProvider</code> hàm <code>boot</code></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Khai báo class App\\Http\\ViewComposers\\ProfileComposer</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// sẽ được gọi khi 1 trong 2 view profile, profile2 được render</span>\r\nView<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">composer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'profile\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'profile2\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'App\\Http\\ViewComposers\\ProfileComposer\'</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Sử dụng Closure callback nhanh gọn</span>\r\nView<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">composer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'profile\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'dashboard\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$view</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">with</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Chung Nguyễn\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Với cách sử dụng composer ở trên thì bạn phải tạo một class mới có tên&nbsp;<code>ProfileComposer</code> nằm trong thư mục <code>app/Http/ViewComposers</code></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Http<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>ViewComposers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>View<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>View</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ProfileComposer</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Create a new profile composer.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return  void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">__construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">//</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Bind data to the view.\r\n     *\r\n     * @param    View  $view\r\n     * @return  void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">compose</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>View <span class=\"token variable\">$view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// truyền dữ liệu ở đây nè</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$view</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">with</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Chung Nguyễn\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>??????????</p>\r\n            </div>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/truyen-du-lieu-ra-view-trong-laravel', 4, 1, 'Truyền dữ liệu ra View trong Laravel', 'Trong b&agrave;i viết n&agrave;y, giả sử ch&uacute;ng ta c&oacute; view welcome.blade.php&nbsp;như sau', 'truyen-du-lieu-ra-view-trong-laravel', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Trong b&agrave;i viết n&agrave;y, giả sử ch&uacute;ng ta c&oacute; view welcome.blade.php&nbsp;như sau'),
(6, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:30', '2019-08-11 13:11:59', 1, 'Tạo helpers function tùy biến trong Laravel 5', 'tao-helpers-function-tuy-bien-trong-laravel-5', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i c&aacute;c <strong>function helpers</strong> m&agrave; <strong>Laravel</strong> hỗ trợ ra, c&aacute;c bạn c&oacute; thể t&ugrave;y biến th&ecirc;m c&aacute;c function cần thiết cho project của m&igrave;nh. C&oacute; nhiều c&aacute;ch để thực hiện, sau đ&acirc;y cho ph&eacute;p m&igrave;nh hướng dẫn 1 c&aacute;ch nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bạn tạo 1 <strong>files helpers function</strong> đặt ở đ&acirc;u t&ugrave;y &yacute;, v&iacute; dụ đặt trong <code>app/helpers.php</code></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">//app/helpers.php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">helloWorld</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Hello, World!&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Khai b&aacute;o composer load file n&agrave;y khi chạy:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-json\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token property\">&quot;autoload&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token property\">&quot;classmap&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n        ...\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token property\">&quot;psr-4&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token property\">&quot;App\\\\&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">&quot;app/&quot;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token property\">&quot;files&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token string\">&quot;app/helpers.php&quot;</span> // &lt;---- Th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o đ&acirc;y\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau khi th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o <code>composer.json</code> file xong, chạy command sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-bash\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-bash\">composer dump-autoload</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Kiểm tra file&nbsp;<code>vendor\\composer\\autoload_files.php</code> đ&atilde; c&oacute; d&ograve;ng&nbsp;<code>$baseDir . &#39;/app/helpers.php&#39;,</code> chưa? Nếu c&oacute; l&agrave; ok rồi đ&oacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vậy l&agrave; b&acirc;y giờ ngo&agrave;i view hay bất cứ đ&acirc;u, c&aacute;c bạn c&oacute; thể sử dụng helpers function được rồi đ&oacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>Gọi helper <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token function\">helloWorld</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>p<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch&uacute;c c&aacute;c bạn th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/tao-helpers-function-tuy-bien-trong-laravel-5', 2, 1, 'Tạo helpers function tùy biến trong Laravel 5', 'Ngo&agrave;i c&aacute;c function helpers m&agrave; Laravel hỗ trợ ra, c&aacute;c bạn c&oacute; thể t&ugrave;y biến th&ecirc;m c&aacute;c function cần thiết cho project của m&igrave;nh. C&oacute; nhiều c&aacute;ch để thực hiện, sau đ&acirc;y cho ph&eacute;', 'tao-helpers-function-tuy-bien-trong-laravel-5', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Ngo&agrave;i c&aacute;c function helpers m&agrave; Laravel hỗ trợ ra, c&aacute;c bạn c&oacute; thể t&ugrave;y biến th&ecirc;m c&aacute;c function cần thiết cho project của m&igrave;nh. C&oacute; nhiều c&aacute;ch để thực hiện, sau đ&acirc;y cho ph&eacute;p'),
(7, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:32', '2019-09-05 17:02:11', 1, 'HTML/Form Class not found error trong Laravel 5', 'htmlform-class-not-found-error-trong-laravel-5', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>Kể từ khi Laravel n&acirc;ng cấp l&ecirc;n phi&ecirc;n bản 5.0. Laravel đ&atilde; quyết định loại bỏ package HTML/Form ra khỏi core của m&igrave;nh, nhưng vẫn tiếp tục bảo tr&igrave; v&agrave; cung cấp cho người d&ugrave;ng c&agrave;i đặt nếu cần.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chạy <code>command prompt</code> v&agrave; run command:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">composer require laravelcollective/html</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Tiếp theo, th&ecirc;m mới <code>provider</code> v&agrave;o mảng <code>providers</code> trong <code>config/app.php</code>:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;providers&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\r\n    Collective\\<span class=\"token package\">Html<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>HtmlServiceProvider</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Cuối c&ugrave;ng, th&ecirc;m 2 class <code>aliases</code> v&agrave;o mảng <code>aliases</code> trong file <code>config/app.php</code>:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;aliases&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Form&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> Collective\\<span class=\"token package\">Html<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>FormFacade</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n      <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Html&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> Collective\\<span class=\"token package\">Html<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>HtmlFacade</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// ...</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Xem th&ocirc;ng tin đầy đủ tại trang chủ:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://laravelcollective.com/docs/5.3/html\">https://laravelcollective.com/docs/5.3/html</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/html-form-class-not-found-error-trong-laravel-5', 4, 1, 'HTML/Form Class not found error trong Laravel 5', 'Kể từ khi Laravel n&acirc;ng cấp l&ecirc;n phi&ecirc;n bản 5.0. Laravel đ&atilde; quyết định loại bỏ package HTML/Form ra khỏi core của m&igrave;nh, nhưng vẫn tiếp tục bảo tr&igrave; v&agrave; cung cấp cho người d&ugrave;ng c&agrave;i đặt nếu cần.', 'htmlform-class-not-found-error-trong-laravel-5', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Kể từ khi Laravel n&acirc;ng cấp l&ecirc;n phi&ecirc;n bản 5.0. Laravel đ&atilde; quyết định loại bỏ package HTML/Form ra khỏi core của m&igrave;nh, nhưng vẫn tiếp tục bảo tr&igrave; v&agrave; cung cấp cho người d&ugrave;ng c&agrave;i đặt nếu cần.');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(8, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:34', '2019-08-12 14:20:28', 1, 'Laravel đăng nhập thông qua các mạng xã hội Facebook, Google, Twitter, Github', 'laravel-dang-nhap-thong-qua-cac-mang-xa-hoi-facebook-google-twitter-github', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>H&ocirc;m nay m&igrave;nh xin giới thiệu một phương thức <strong>đăng nhập th&ocirc;ng qua mạng x&atilde; hội</strong> phổ biến hiện nay như <strong>Facebook</strong>, <strong>Google</strong>, <strong>Twitter</strong>, <strong>Github</strong>, ...<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Đăng nhập th&ocirc;ng qua mạng x&atilde; hội</strong> l&agrave; một t&iacute;nh năng quan trọng ngo&agrave;i c&aacute;ch đăng nhập th&ocirc;ng thường, v&igrave; hiện nay số lượng người d&ugrave;ng mạng x&atilde; hội l&agrave; rất lớn, t&iacute;nh tiện lợi khi <strong>đăng nhập bằng&nbsp;Social authentication</strong>.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTrong v&iacute; dụ h&ocirc;m nay m&igrave;nh demo tr&ecirc;n Facebook.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1b9s8tkij0\">H&igrave;nh ảnh demo</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Laravel đăng nhập thông qua các mạng xã hội Facebook, Google\" height=\"337\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/laravel-dang-nhap-thong-qua-cac-mang-xa-hoi-facebook-google.jpg\" title=\"Laravel đăng nhập thông qua các mạng xã hội Facebook, Google\" width=\"714\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1b9s8tkij1\">Bước 1: C&agrave;i đặt Laravel Socialite Package</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; package do ch&iacute;nh <strong>Laravel</strong> cung cấp đ&oacute; nha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mở&nbsp;<code>terminal</code> tại thư mục root website v&agrave; chạy command sau để c&agrave;i đặt:</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\ncomposer require laravel/socialite</pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau khi c&agrave;i đặt xong, ch&uacute;ng ta tiến h&agrave;nh th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o&nbsp;<code>providers</code> v&agrave; <code>aliases</code>&nbsp;trong file config <code>config/app.php</code>&nbsp;(<em><strong>Bỏ qua bước n&agrave;y đối với laravel 5.5 trở đi</strong></em>)</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;providers&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\r\n Laravel\\<span class=\"token package\">Socialite<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>SocialiteServiceProvider</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;aliases&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\r\n <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Socialite&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> Laravel\\<span class=\"token package\">Socialite<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Facades<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Socialite</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1b9s8tkik2\">Bước 2: Tạo facebook app</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Bước n&agrave;y ch&uacute;ng ta tiến h&agrave;nh tạo 1 app tr&ecirc;n&nbsp;<a href=\"https://developers.facebook.com/apps/\">https://developers.facebook.com/apps/</a>&nbsp;v&agrave; tiến h&agrave;nh tạo app. C&aacute;ch tạo app cũng đơn giản kh&ocirc;ng cần phải n&oacute;i.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Laravel đăng nhập thông qua các mạng xã hội Facebook, Google\" height=\"392\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/laravel-dang-nhap-thong-qua-cac-mang-xa-hoi-facebook-google-1.png\" title=\"Laravel đăng nhập thông qua các mạng xã hội Facebook, Google\" width=\"877\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Sau khi tạo xong app, ở mục <code>Th&ecirc;m sản phẩm</code>&nbsp;&rArr; <strong>Đăng nhập Facebook</strong> để c&oacute; thể sử dụng t&iacute;nh năng.</li>\r\n	<li><code>Tab X&eacute;t duyệt ứng dụng</code> tiến h&agrave;nh Nộp c&aacute;c mục để duyệt *(email,&nbsp;public_profile, user_friends)</li>\r\n	<li>Cũng tại <code>tab&nbsp;X&eacute;t duyệt ứng dụng</code>:&nbsp;Ứng dụng của bạn đang được <strong>ph&aacute;t triển</strong> v&agrave; <strong>kh&ocirc;ng khả dụng với mọi người</strong>. Bạn tiến h&agrave;nh click v&agrave;o để ứng dụng được c&ocirc;ng khai nếu như bạn muốn đưa l&ecirc;n web server cho mọi người d&ugrave;ng.</li>\r\n	<li>V&agrave; cuối c&ugrave;ng tại <code>tab Bảng điều khiển</code> ch&uacute;ng ta c&oacute; được:&nbsp;<strong>ID ứng dụng</strong> v&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>Kh&oacute;a b&iacute; mật của ứng dụng</strong></li>\r\n	<li>Trong file <span style=\"color: #ffcc00; background-color: #339966; font-size: 18pt;\">config/services.php</span> th&ecirc;m&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;facebook&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;client_id&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;ID ứng dụng&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;client_secret&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Kh&oacute;a b&iacute; mật của ứng dụng&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;redirect&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;https://yourwebsite.com/auth/facebook/callback&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-warning h3\">Sau sự cố bảo mật th&ocirc;ng tin, FB đ&atilde; thắc chặt ch&iacute;nh s&aacute;ch hơn. To&agrave;n bộ callback URL y&ecirc;u cầu phải l&agrave; https hết.</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-info h3\">Nếu bạn l&agrave;m localhost, cứ khai b&aacute;o <a href=\"https://localhost/auth/facebook/callback\">https://localhost/auth/facebook/callback</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-info h3\">Sau đ&oacute; truy cập <a href=\"https://localhost\">https://localhost</a>&nbsp;v&agrave; l&agrave;m theo h&igrave;nh sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"https-localhost-proceed\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/https-localhost-proceed.png\" title=\"https-localhost-proceed\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1b9s9eigi3\"><strong>Bước 3:&nbsp;Tạo facebook login</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Facebook sẽ trả về th&ocirc;ng tin của user, bạn cần phải lưu v&agrave;o datatabase. Lưu như thế n&agrave;o th&igrave; t&ugrave;y c&aacute;c bạn, ở đ&acirc;y để đơn giản h&oacute;a demo m&igrave;nh th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o table users 2 trường l&agrave; <strong>provider</strong> v&agrave; <strong>provider_id</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong app/Http/routes.php</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;auth/facebook&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Auth\\AuthController@redirectToFacebook&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;auth.facebook&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;auth/facebook/callback&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Auth\\AuthController@handleFacebookCallback&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong&nbsp;<code>app/Http/Controllers/Auth/AuthController.php</code> th&ecirc;m 2 functions sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">redirectToFacebook</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> Socialite<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">driver</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;facebook&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">redirect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">handleFacebookCallback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">try</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$user</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Socialite<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">driver</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;facebook&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">user</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;name&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$user</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;email&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$user</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">email</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;facebook_id&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$user</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$userModel</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">User</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$createdUser</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$userModel</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">addNew</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        Auth<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">loginUsingId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$createdUser</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">redirect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">route</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;home&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Exception <span class=\"token variable\">$e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">redirect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;/&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong Models: <code>app/User.php</code> th&ecirc;m function sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">addNew</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$input</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$check</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">where</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;facebook_id&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token variable\">$input</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;facebook_id&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">first</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">is_null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$check</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$input</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$check</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    \r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>V&agrave; cuối c&ugrave;ng trong login page c&aacute;c bạn đặt url l&agrave; được:<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token function\">route</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;auth.facebook&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Gặp vấn đề g&igrave; vui l&ograve;ng để lại comment nh&eacute;!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch&uacute;c c&aacute;c bạn th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-dang-nhap-thong-qua-cac-mang-xa-hoi-facebook-google-twitter-github', 5, 1, 'Laravel đăng nhập thông qua các mạng xã hội Facebook, Google, Twitter, Github', 'H&ocirc;m nay m&igrave;nh xin giới thiệu một phương thức đăng nhập th&ocirc;ng qua mạng x&atilde; hội phổ biến hiện nay như Facebook, Google, Twitter, Github, ...Đăng nhập th&ocirc;ng qua mạng x&atilde; hội l&agrave; một t&iacute;nh năng quan trọng ng', 'laravel-dang-nhap-thong-qua-cac-mang-xa-hoi-facebook-google-twitter-github', '[\"\"]', 1, 'H&ocirc;m nay m&igrave;nh xin giới thiệu một phương thức đăng nhập th&ocirc;ng qua mạng x&atilde; hội phổ biến hiện nay như Facebook, Google, Twitter, Github, ...\r\n\r\nĐăng nhập th&ocirc;ng qua mạng x&atilde; hội l&agrave; một t&iacute;nh năng quan trọng ngo'),
(9, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:36', '2019-08-11 14:12:26', 1, 'Lỗi Laravel: ReflectionException in RouteDependencyResolverTrait.php line 57', 'loi-laravel-reflectionexception-in-routedependencyresolvertraitphp-line-57', '<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n              <p>Lỗi này xảy ra khi trong file route <code>web.php</code> bạn khai báo không phải là 1 route parameter (tham số) nhưng trong controller lại truyền vào parameter. Ví dụ</p>\r\n<p><code>Route::get(\'/\', \'BlogController@index\');</code></p>\r\n<p>Trong BlogController.php bạn viết</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"&quot; language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">index</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$param</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//code</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Rõ ràng trong route khai báo không hề có tham số nên xảy ra lỗi là điều tất nhiên. Hãy xóa <code>$param</code> kia đi là ok ngay.</p>\r\n<p>Chúc các bạn thành công!</p>\r\n            </div>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/loi-laravel-reflectionexception-in-routedependencyresolvertrait-php-line-57', 1, 1, 'Lỗi Laravel: ReflectionException in RouteDependencyResolverTrait.php line 57', 'Lỗi n&agrave;y xảy ra khi trong file route web.php bạn khai b&aacute;o kh&ocirc;ng phải l&agrave; 1 route parameter (tham số) nhưng trong controller lại truyền v&agrave;o parameter. V&iacute; dụ', 'loi-laravel-reflectionexception-in-routedependencyresolvertraitphp-line-57', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Lỗi n&agrave;y xảy ra khi trong file route web.php bạn khai b&aacute;o kh&ocirc;ng phải l&agrave; 1 route parameter (tham số) nhưng trong controller lại truyền v&agrave;o parameter. V&iacute; dụ'),
(10, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:38', '2019-08-20 15:38:49', 1, 'Lỗi Laravel: NotFoundHttpException in RouteCollection.php line 161', 'loi-laravel-notfoundhttpexception-in-routecollectionphp-line-161', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p><img alt=\"Lỗi Laravel: NotFoundHttpException in RouteCollection.php line 161\" height=\"300\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/loi-laravel-notfoundhttpexception-in-routecollection-php-line-161.png\" title=\"Lỗi Laravel: NotFoundHttpException in RouteCollection.php line 161\" width=\"600\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong Laravel c&oacute; nhiều lỗi, theo đ&aacute;nh gi&aacute; của m&igrave;nh th&igrave; hay gặp v&agrave; g&acirc;y kh&oacute; chịu nhất l&agrave; lỗi NotFoundHttpException in RouteCollection.php line 161.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nĐể khắc phục lỗi n&agrave;y m&igrave;nh đề xuất hướng giải quyết sau, hi vọng gi&uacute;p &iacute;ch cho c&aacute;c bạn.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGiả sử thư mục gốc của trang web bạn l&agrave;: <kbd>C:/xampp/htdocs/laravel</kbd><br />\r\n<br />\r\nNhư vậy tr&ecirc;n tr&igrave;nh duyệt sẽ l&agrave;: <kbd>http://localhost/laravel</kbd></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1b9q3e6940\">Bước 1: Check index route</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Bạn h&atilde;y kiểm tra chắc chắn website m&igrave;nh đang chạy tr&ecirc;n:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">http://localhost/laravel</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>hay</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">http://localhost/laravel/public</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Laravel được cấu h&igrave;nh để chạy tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c server chuy&ecirc;n dụng như homestead.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>N&ecirc;n sau khi setup website xong sẽ c&oacute; trang index mặc định l&agrave; <code>http://localhost/laravel/public</code>&nbsp;<br />\r\nc&aacute;c bạn lưu &yacute; điểm n&agrave;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1b9q3e6940\">Bước 2: Check .htaccess</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Giả sử sau khi bước 1 đ&atilde; check xong bạn thu được kết quả l&agrave; website chạy tr&ecirc;n</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">http://localhost/laravel/public</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>v&agrave; đường dẫn bạn đang chạy bị gặp lỗi l&agrave;:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">http://localhost/laravel/public/hello</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Bạn cần kiểm tra xem <code>.htaccess</code> rewriting rules đ&atilde; c&oacute; hiệu lực hay chưa bằng c&aacute;ch truy cập li&ecirc;n kết sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">http://localhost/laravel/public/index.php/hello</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu ok như vậy c&oacute; nghĩa l&agrave; file <code>.htaccess</code> kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; hoặc&nbsp;<strong>rewrite module php chưa được c&agrave;i đặt hoặc bị disable</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1b9q49qpl1\">Bước 3: Kiểm tra trong cmd</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Bước 1 v&agrave; 2 l&agrave; những nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n thường hay gặp nhất, nếu vẫn chưa được y&ecirc;n t&acirc;m c&aacute;c bạn h&atilde;y thử c&aacute;ch sau đ&acirc;y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nĐầu ti&ecirc;n c&aacute;c bạn chạy cmd tại thư mục root của website, trong v&iacute; dụ của m&igrave;nh l&agrave; <strong>laravel</strong>. Sau đ&oacute; g&otilde; lệnh:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">php artisan route:list</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Lưu &yacute;: trong routes của bạn c&oacute; callback function chẳng hạn như dưới đ&acirc;y th&igrave; c&oacute; khả năng b&aacute;o lỗi nh&eacute;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;users/{id}&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;callback function&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Laravel sẽ liệt k&ecirc; to&agrave;n bộ route c&oacute; trong project của bạn gồm c&aacute;c trường sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">+--------+--------------------------------------------------------------+-------------\r\n| Domain | Method | URI | Name | Action                                 | Middleware |\r\n+--------+--------------------------------------------------------------+-------------\r\n|         GET|HEAD  /    home App\\Http\\Controllers\\HomeController@index | web        |</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Ở đ&acirc;y c&aacute;c bạn quan t&acirc;m đến 2 thuộc t&iacute;nh đ&oacute; l&agrave; URI v&agrave; Method, đầu ti&ecirc;n l&agrave; URI bạn kiểm tra xem URL bạn truy cập c&oacute; trong danh s&aacute;ch kh&ocirc;ng. C&aacute;c bạn c&oacute; thể kiểm tra thủ c&ocirc;ng bằng mắt, hoặc nhấn Ctrl + F (win 8 trở l&ecirc;n mới c&oacute; th&igrave; phải) để kiểm tra.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGiả sử URL bạn truy cập khớp với 1 bạn ghi trong URI th&igrave; bạn kiểm tra xem method của URI đ&oacute; c&oacute; hỗ trợ hay kh&ocirc;ng. Như ở tr&ecirc;n hỗ trợ method GET hoặc HEAD m&agrave; bạn đặt trong form với method POST th&igrave; chắn chắn xảy ra lỗi.<br />\r\nNếu tới đ&acirc;y biết được lỗi rồi th&igrave; ok rồi phải kh&ocirc;ng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNếu vẫn chưa giải quyết được lỗi, h&atilde;y để lại cmt nh&eacute;!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch&uacute;c c&aacute;c bạn th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng!&nbsp;??</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/loi-laravel-notfoundhttpexception-in-routecollection-php-line-161', 1, 1, 'Lỗi Laravel: NotFoundHttpException in RouteCollection.php line 161', '', 'loi-laravel-notfoundhttpexception-in-routecollectionphp-line-161', '[\"\"]', 1, ''),
(11, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:39', '2019-08-11 14:14:20', 1, 'Lỗi Laravel: Call to undefined method Illuminate\\Session\\Store::set()', 'loi-laravel-call-to-undefined-method-illuminatesessionstoreset', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<header>\r\n<hr /></header>\r\n\r\n<section>\r\n<p><img alt=\"Đây là bug mình gặp trên Laravel 5.4, nguyên nhân là do cài package laravel/socialite Laravel cập nhật lên phiên bản 5.4 xảy ra lỗi.\" height=\"280\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/call-to-undefined-method-illuminate-session-store-set.jpg\" title=\"Đây là bug mình gặp trên Laravel 5.4, nguyên nhân là do cài package laravel/socialite Laravel cập nhật lên phiên bản 5.4 xảy ra lỗi.\" width=\"600\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; bug m&igrave;nh gặp tr&ecirc;n&nbsp;<strong>Laravel 5.4</strong>, nguy&ecirc;n nh&acirc;n l&agrave; do c&agrave;i package&nbsp;<strong>laravel/socialite</strong>&nbsp;Laravel cập nhật l&ecirc;n phi&ecirc;n bản 5.4 n&ecirc;n xảy ra lỗi.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1b9q0bud50\">Sửa lỗi</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong file&nbsp;<strong>composer.json</strong>&nbsp;sửa&nbsp;<strong>&quot;laravel/socialite&quot;: &quot;^2.0&quot;</strong>&nbsp;th&agrave;nh&nbsp;<strong>&quot;laravel/socialite&quot;: &quot;^3.0&quot;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau đ&oacute; chạy&nbsp;<strong>composer update</strong></p>\r\n</section>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/loi-laravel-call-to-undefined-method-illuminate-session-store-set', 1, 1, 'Lỗi Laravel: Call to undefined method Illuminate\\Session\\Store::set()', '', 'loi-laravel-call-to-undefined-method-illuminatesessionstoreset', '[\"\"]', 1, '');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(12, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:42', '2019-08-11 14:15:41', 1, 'Hướng dẫn update project từ Laravel 5.4 lên Laravel 5.5', 'huong-dan-update-project-tu-laravel-54-len-laravel-55', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>Sau đ&acirc;y Chung xin hướng dẫn c&aacute;c bạn update project từ <strong>Laravel 5.4</strong> l&ecirc;n <strong>Laravel 5.5</strong> nh&eacute;, qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh update n&agrave;y Chung &aacute;p dụng tr&ecirc;n ch&iacute;nh project của m&igrave;nh lu&ocirc;n.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bp3i1u560\">Update composer.json</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>V&igrave; <strong>composer</strong> quản l&yacute; c&aacute;c package bạn c&agrave;i trong app <strong>Laravel</strong> của m&igrave;nh n&ecirc;n cần phải cập nhật theo <strong>Laravel</strong>. Bạn h&atilde;y d&ugrave;ng tool&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14pt; background-color: #ff6600; color: #ffffff;\"><strong><a href=\"https://www.devart.com/codecompare/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"background-color: #ff6600; color: #ffffff;\" target=\"_blank\">code compare</a></strong></span>&nbsp;để so s&aacute;nh file&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #ffffff;\"><strong><span style=\"background-color: #ff6600;\"><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/laravel/laravel/master/composer.json\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"background-color: #ff6600; color: #ffffff;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"composer.json của Laravel 5.5\">composer.json của Laravel 5.5</a></span></strong></span>&nbsp;với file <strong>composer</strong> hiện tại của bạn. Sau khi merge code từ 2 file n&agrave;y lại ta sẽ c&oacute; file<code> composer.json</code> mới.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau khi c&oacute; file mới, việc cập nhật sẽ kh&ocirc;ng diễn ra su&ocirc;n sẻ m&agrave; bạn phải thay đổi 1 ch&uacute;t đ&oacute; l&agrave; phần require trong file <code>composer.json</code> phải đổi th&agrave;nh <code>*</code> hết (nếu si&ecirc;ng th&igrave; bạn v&agrave;o&nbsp;<a href=\"https://packagist.org\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"packagist\">packagist</a>&nbsp;để check xem package n&agrave;o update l&ecirc;n version n&agrave;o).</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-json\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-json\">    <span class=\"token property\">&quot;require&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token property\">&quot;php&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">&quot;&gt;=7.0.0&quot;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token property\">&quot;fideloper/proxy&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">&quot;~3.3&quot;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token property\">&quot;laravel/framework&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">&quot;5.5.*&quot;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token property\">&quot;laravel/tinker&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">&quot;*&quot;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token property\">&quot;artesaos/seotools&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">&quot;*&quot;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token property\">&quot;baum/baum&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">&quot;*&quot;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token property\">&quot;cviebrock/eloquent-sluggable&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">&quot;*&quot;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        // ...\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Chạy <code>composer update</code> trong command</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">composer update</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bp3i1u561\">Automatic Package Discovery</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu bạn chưa biết th&igrave; trong <strong>Laravel 5.5</strong> c&oacute; sự thay đổi mới đ&oacute; l&agrave;&nbsp;<a href=\"/posts/cap-nhat-laravel-5-5-phan-6-automatic-package-discovery\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 6: Automatic Package Discovery\">Automatic Package Discovery</a>&nbsp;bạn c&oacute; thể xem&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: #ff6600; color: #ffffff;\"><strong><a href=\"/posts/cap-nhat-laravel-5-5-phan-6-automatic-package-discovery\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"background-color: #ff6600; color: #ffffff;\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 6: Automatic Package Discovery\">tại đ&acirc;y</a></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Như vậy c&aacute;c package c&oacute; hỗ trợ discovery th&igrave; sẽ kh&ocirc;ng cần phải khai b&aacute;o trong&nbsp;<code>config\\app.php</code> ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; vậy bạn c&oacute; 2 sự lựa chọn để check xem package n&agrave;o đ&atilde; kịp thời cập nhật l&ecirc;n <strong>Laravel 5.5</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>C&aacute;ch 1:</strong>&nbsp;Comment tất cả c&aacute;c <code>Service Provider</code> m&agrave; bạn đ&atilde; th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o danh s&aacute;ch&nbsp;<code>providers</code> trong&nbsp;<code>config\\app.php</code>, chạy trang web của bạn <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><em>(nhớ bật chế độ debug l&ecirc;n)</em></span>. <strong>Whoops</strong> (<a href=\"/posts/cap-nhat-laravel-5-5-phan-1-su-tro-lai-cua-whoops\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 1: Sự trở lại của Whoops\">đọc b&agrave;i về Sự trở lại của Whoops tại đ&acirc;y</a>) sẽ chỉ ra&nbsp;<code>Service Provider</code> n&agrave;o cần phải c&oacute;, v&igrave; package đ&oacute; chưa hỗ trợ&nbsp;<strong>Package Discovery&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Whoops show error\" height=\"216\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/whoops-show-error.png\" title=\"Whoops show error\" width=\"419\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Như h&igrave;nh tr&ecirc;n th&igrave; m&igrave;nh sẽ biết l&agrave; cần phải uncomment proivder dưới đ&acirc;y</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Artesaos\\<span class=\"token package\">SEOTools<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Providers<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>SEOToolsServiceProvider</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong project của m&igrave;nh th&igrave; c&oacute; 1 số package n&agrave;y chưa hỗ trợ&nbsp;<a href=\"/posts/cap-nhat-laravel-5-5-phan-6-automatic-package-discovery\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 6: Automatic Package Discovery\">Automatic Package Discovery</a>&nbsp;cho bạn n&agrave;o c&oacute; package giống m&igrave;nh th&igrave; đỡ phải thử</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Artesaos\\<span class=\"token package\">SEOTools<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Providers<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>SEOToolsServiceProvider</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\nBarryvdh\\<span class=\"token package\">Elfinder<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>ElfinderServiceProvider</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\nBarryvdh\\<span class=\"token package\">TranslationManager<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>ManagerServiceProvider</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\nConner\\<span class=\"token package\">Tagging<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Providers<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>TaggingServiceProvider</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>C&aacute;ch 2:</strong>&nbsp;C&aacute;ch n&agrave;y th&igrave; c&aacute;c bạn v&agrave;o github v&agrave; kiểm tra xem package đ&oacute; c&oacute; hỗ trợ&nbsp;<strong>Package Discovery</strong> trong <code>composer.json</code> hay kh&ocirc;ng? Nếu file <code>composer.json</code> <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">vừa được cập nhật khoảng v&agrave;i ng&agrave;y lại đ&acirc;y th&igrave; chắc chắn l&agrave; c&oacute; hỗ trợ</span>, c&ograve;n kh&ocirc;ng th&igrave; bạn v&agrave;o file <code>composer.json</code> c&oacute; đoạn n&agrave;y th&igrave; tức l&agrave; c&oacute; hỗ trợ, v&iacute; dụ m&igrave;nh check g&oacute;i&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/davejamesmiller/laravel-breadcrumbs\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/davejamesmiller/laravel-breadcrumbs</a>&nbsp;thấy n&oacute; được cập nhật 9 ng&agrave;y trước v&agrave; file composer.json c&oacute; đoạn n&agrave;y, tức l&agrave; đ&atilde; cập nhật hỗ trợ <strong>Laravel 5.5</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-json\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-json\">    <span class=\"token property\">&quot;extra&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token property\">&quot;laravel&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token property\">&quot;providers&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n                <span class=\"token string\">&quot;DaveJamesMiller\\\\Breadcrumbs\\\\BreadcrumbsServiceProvider&quot;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token property\">&quot;aliases&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n                <span class=\"token property\">&quot;Breadcrumbs&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">&quot;DaveJamesMiller\\\\Breadcrumbs\\\\Facades\\\\Breadcrumbs&quot;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>L&uacute;c n&agrave;y trang&nbsp;<a href=\"/\">https://chungnguyen.xyz/</a>&nbsp;đ&atilde; l&ecirc;n version 5.5.1</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" class=\"img-responsive center-block\" height=\"265\" src=\"/image/posts/php-artisan-version-5-5-1.png\" width=\"495\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bp3i1u562\">Thay đổi file source ch&iacute;nh</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy c&aacute;c package đ&atilde; cập nhật nhưng source ch&iacute;nh vẫn c&ograve;n l&agrave; 5.4 m&igrave;nh sẽ d&ugrave;ng tool code compare b&ecirc;n tr&ecirc;n để check xem c&oacute; những file n&agrave;o thay đổi (c&aacute;c bạn nhớ download source&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/laravel/laravel\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/laravel/laravel\"><strong>Laravel 5.5</strong></a>&nbsp;về nh&eacute;), dưới đ&acirc;y l&agrave; những file c&oacute; thay đổi</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<ul>\r\n		<li>app\\Console\\Kernel.php (<span style=\"background-color: #99cc00; color: #ffffff;\">cập nhật</span>)</li>\r\n		<li>app\\Exceptions\\Handler.php&nbsp;(<span style=\"background-color: #99cc00; color: #ffffff;\">cập nhật</span>)</li>\r\n		<li>app\\Http\\Controllers\\Controller.php&nbsp;(<span style=\"background-color: #99cc00; color: #ffffff;\">cập nhật</span>)</li>\r\n		<li>app\\Http\\Middleware\\EncryptCookies.php&nbsp;(đổi từ&nbsp;BaseTrimmer sang&nbsp;Middleware)&nbsp;(<span style=\"background-color: #99cc00; color: #ffffff;\">cập nhật</span>)</li>\r\n		<li>app\\Http\\Middleware\\TrimStrings.php&nbsp;(đổi từ&nbsp;BaseTrimmer sang&nbsp;Middleware)&nbsp;(<span style=\"background-color: #99cc00; color: #ffffff;\">cập nhật</span>)</li>\r\n		<li>app\\Http\\Middleware\\VerifyCsrfToken.php (đổi từ&nbsp;BaseTrimmer sang&nbsp;Middleware)&nbsp;(<span style=\"background-color: #99cc00; color: #ffffff;\">cập nhật</span>)</li>\r\n		<li>file&nbsp;app\\Http\\Middleware\\TrustProxies.php (<span style=\"background-color: #ff6600; color: #ffffff;\">Th&ecirc;m mới&nbsp;</span>)</li>\r\n		<li>app\\Http\\Kernel.php&nbsp;(<span style=\"background-color: #99cc00; color: #ffffff;\">cập nhật</span>)</li>\r\n		<li>app\\Providers\\BroadcastServiceProvider.php&nbsp;(<span style=\"background-color: #99cc00; color: #ffffff;\">cập nhật</span>)</li>\r\n		<li>app\\Providers\\RouteServiceProvider.php&nbsp;(<span style=\"background-color: #99cc00; color: #ffffff;\">cập nhật</span>)</li>\r\n		<li>routes\\channels.php&nbsp;(<span style=\"background-color: #ff6600; color: #ffffff;\">Th&ecirc;m mới&nbsp;</span>)</li>\r\n		<li>artisan (<span style=\"background-color: #99cc00; color: #ffffff;\">cập nhật</span>) - <span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>quan trọng</strong></span></li>\r\n		<li>public\\index.php&nbsp;&nbsp;(<span style=\"background-color: #99cc00; color: #ffffff;\">cập nhật</span>) -&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #0000ff;\"><strong>quan trọng</strong></span></li>\r\n		<li>bootstrap\\autoload.php (<span style=\"background-color: #ff0000; color: #ffffff;\">x&oacute;a bỏ</span>)&nbsp;b&acirc;y giờ artisan sẽ v&agrave;o composer/autload.php chứ kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n v&agrave;o&nbsp;bootstrap\\autoload.php nữa</li>\r\n		<li>bootstrap\\cache\\packages.php&nbsp;(<span style=\"background-color: #ff0000; color: #ffffff;\">x&oacute;a bỏ</span>)</li>\r\n		<li>bootstrap\\cache\\services.php&nbsp;(<span style=\"background-color: #ff0000; color: #ffffff;\">x&oacute;a bỏ</span>)</li>\r\n	</ul>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau khi l&agrave;m cẩn thận c&aacute;c bước tr&ecirc;n bạn h&atilde;y chạy tất cả c&aacute;c lệnh sau trong command</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">composer dumpautoload\r\nphp artisan optimize\r\nphp artisan view:clear\r\nphp artisan cache:clear\r\nphp artisan config:clear</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu bạn quản l&yacute; vps hay c&oacute; quyền truy cập ssh th&igrave; dễ rồi, c&ograve;n kh&ocirc;ng h&atilde;y đọc b&agrave;i n&agrave;y của Chung nh&eacute; <a href=\"/posts/huong-dan-update-code-len-hosting-khi-cai-package-moi-trong-laraevl-5-4\" title=\"Hướng dẫn update code lên hosting khi cài package mới trong Laraevl 5.4\">Hướng dẫn update code l&ecirc;n hosting khi c&agrave;i package mới trong Laraevl 5.4</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chi tiết c&oacute; tr&ecirc;n <a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/master/upgrade#upgrade-5.5.0\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Laravel Docs\">Laravel Docs</a>&nbsp;bạn c&oacute; thể xem tham khảo th&ecirc;m.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr&ecirc;n đ&acirc;y l&agrave; qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh update blog Chung Nguyễn l&ecirc;n Laravel 5.5. Ch&uacute;c c&aacute;c bạn th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng nh&eacute;&nbsp;??</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/huong-dan-update-project-tu-laravel-5-4-len-laravel-5-5', 1, 1, 'Hướng dẫn update project từ Laravel 5.4 lên Laravel 5.5', 'Sau đ&acirc;y Chung xin hướng dẫn c&aacute;c bạn update project từ Laravel 5.4 l&ecirc;n Laravel 5.5 nh&eacute;, qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh update n&agrave;y Chung &aacute;p dụng tr&ecirc;n ch&iacute;nh project của m&igrave;nh lu&ocirc;n.', 'huong-dan-update-project-tu-laravel-54-len-laravel-55', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Sau đ&acirc;y Chung xin hướng dẫn c&aacute;c bạn update project từ Laravel 5.4 l&ecirc;n Laravel 5.5 nh&eacute;, qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh update n&agrave;y Chung &aacute;p dụng tr&ecirc;n ch&iacute;nh project của m&igrave;nh lu&ocirc;n.'),
(13, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:44', '2019-08-11 14:16:18', 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 6: Automatic Package Discovery', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-6-automatic-package-discovery', '<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n              <p>Ở các phiên bản trước <strong>Laravel 5.5</strong> muốn cài 1 package nào đó chẳng hạn:&nbsp;<code>laracasts/flash</code> bạn phải chạy lên command <strong>composer</strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-markup\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-markup\">composer require laracasts/flash</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Sau đó add vào danh sách <code>providers</code> trong <code>app/config.php</code></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'providers\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    Laracasts\\<span class=\"token package\">Flash<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>FlashServiceProvider</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;Cuối cùng nếu có&nbsp;<code>aliase</code> và bạn muốn dùng phải thêm vào mảng&nbsp;<code>aliases</code> trong <code>app/config.php</code></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'aliases\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'View\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> Illuminate\\<span class=\"token package\">Support<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Facades<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>View</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Flash\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> Laracasts\\<span class=\"token package\">Flash<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Flash</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Kể từ <strong>phiên bản Laravel 5.5</strong> này, package nào tích hợp&nbsp;<strong>Package Discovery</strong> thì không cần phải làm gì cả, nếu bạn là nhà phát triển các gói cho mình xài hoặc cho cộng đồng xài thì nên cập nhật file <code>composer.json</code> cho package như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-json\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-json\"><span class=\"token property\">\"extra\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"laravel\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token property\">\"providers\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token string\">\"Laracasts\\\\Flash\\\\FlashServiceProvider\"</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token property\">\"aliases\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"Flash\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Laracasts\\\\Flash\\\\Flash\"</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Nếu như bạn muốn package nào đó không tự động tích hợp vào project của mình thì sửa file&nbsp;<code>composer.json</code> ở root project</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-json\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-json\">    <span class=\"token property\">\"extra\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token property\">\"laravel\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"dont-discover\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n                <span class=\"token string\">\"laracasts/flash\"</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Nếu muốn tự làm thủ công tất cả thì sẽ như thế này:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-json\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-json\">    <span class=\"token property\">\"extra\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token property\">\"laravel\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token property\">\"dont-discover\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n                <span class=\"token string\">\"*\"</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>??????</p>\r\n            </div>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/cap-nhat-laravel-5-5-phan-6-automatic-package-discovery', 1, 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 6: Automatic Package Discovery', 'Ở c&aacute;c phi&ecirc;n bản trước Laravel 5.5 muốn c&agrave;i 1 package n&agrave;o đ&oacute; chẳng hạn:&nbsp;laracasts/flash bạn phải chạy l&ecirc;n command composer', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-6-automatic-package-discovery', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Ở c&aacute;c phi&ecirc;n bản trước Laravel 5.5 muốn c&agrave;i 1 package n&agrave;o đ&oacute; chẳng hạn:&nbsp;laracasts/flash bạn phải chạy l&ecirc;n command composer'),
(14, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:45', '2019-08-11 14:16:46', 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 5: Phương thức Routing mới', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-5-phuong-thuc-routing-moi', '<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n              <p>Bản <strong>Laravel 5.5</strong> mới này <strong>Laravel</strong> bổ sung thêm 2 phương thức mới trong Route đó là <code>Route::view</code> và&nbsp;<code>Route::redirect</code>.</p>\r\n<p>Bình thường để trả về 1 <strong>view</strong> chúng ta thường làm 2 cách như sau:</p>\r\n<p>1 là trong <code>routes/web.php</code></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'/\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'welcome\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>2 là&nbsp;trong&nbsp;<code>routes/web.php&nbsp;</code></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'/\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'HomeController@index\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>và trong <code>HomeController</code> function <code>index</code> chúng ta viết chỉ có vỏn vẹn 1 dòng&nbsp;<code>return view(\'welcome\');</code> đó là lí do vì sao <code>Route::view</code> xuất hiện trong bản <strong>Laravel 5.5</strong> này, giờ đây chúng ta chỉ cần viết như thế này trong&nbsp;<code>routes/web.php</code></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'/\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'welcome\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Trường hợp muốn truyền dữ liệu cho welcome.blade.php</span>\r\n\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'/\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'welcome\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'name\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Chung Nguyễn\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Còn về&nbsp;<code>Route::redirect</code> thì cũng khá đơn, ví dụ route bạn thay đổi cần phải <strong>redirect</strong> về địa chỉ đích hoặc có những chỗ bạn muốn <strong>redirect</strong> lúc này chỉ cần:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">redirect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'/dia-chi-cu\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'/dia-chi-moi\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">301</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 301 là http response code</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Xem thêm tại: https://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec10.html nhé</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Hi vọng sự thay đổi &nbsp;nhỏ này giúp cho các bạn code thảnh thơi hơn.. hehe&nbsp;??</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n            </div>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/cap-nhat-laravel-5-5-phan-5-phuong-thuc-routing-moi', 1, 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 5: Phương thức Routing mới', 'Bản Laravel 5.5 mới n&agrave;y Laravel bổ sung th&ecirc;m 2 phương thức mới trong Route đ&oacute; l&agrave; Route::view v&agrave;&nbsp;Route::redirect.', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-5-phuong-thuc-routing-moi', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Bản Laravel 5.5 mới n&agrave;y Laravel bổ sung th&ecirc;m 2 phương thức mới trong Route đ&oacute; l&agrave; Route::view v&agrave;&nbsp;Route::redirect.');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(15, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:47', '2019-08-11 14:17:18', 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 4: Exception Cực Chất&#039;ss', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-4-exception-cuc-chat039ss', '<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n              <p>Đối với anh em code dù là web hay app gì thì <strong>exception</strong> là thứ rất cần, đặt <strong>Exception</strong> thích hợp, chúng ta sẽ nắm bắt được lỗi xảy ra trên web của mình để khắc phục lỗi sớm nhất.</p>\r\n<p>Bây giờ bắt tay vào tìm hiểu nào&nbsp;???</p>\r\n<p>Trong routes/web.php ta khai báo url:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'posts/{id}\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'PostsController@show\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Chạy cmd command sau để tạo PostsController:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-markup\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-markup\">php artisan make:controller PostsController</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Trong PostsController tạo function show:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Exceptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>PostIsPrivate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PostsController</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Controller</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">show</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">throw</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PostIsPrivate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Trong thư mục <code>app\\Exceptions</code> tạo file PostIsPrivate.php có nội dung như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Exceptions</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PostIsPrivate</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Exception</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Chạy trên trình duyệt xem thử nào:</p>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail\" title=\"Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 4: Exception Cực Chất\'ss\" src=\"/image/posts/laravel/renderable-reportable-exceptions-1.png\" alt=\"Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 4: Exception Cực Chất\'ss\" width=\"788\" height=\"377\">\r\n<figcaption>Đã bắt được PostIsPrivate&nbsp;&nbsp;Exception</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Ok bây giờ bắt được&nbsp;<strong>PostIsPrivate&nbsp;Exception</strong> ta sẽ show ra 1 thông báo, chỉnh sửa lại function <code>show</code> trong <code>PostsController</code> như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">show</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">try</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">throw</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PostIsPrivate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">catch</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>PostIsPrivate <span class=\"token variable\">$e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"Bài viết riêng tư\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Chạy lại trình duyệt xem nào:</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"img-thumbnail\" src=\"/image/posts/laravel/renderable-reportable-exceptions-render.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"351\" height=\"208\"></p>\r\n<p>Ok nhé, đến đây thì các bạn có thể tùy ý làm gì với&nbsp;<strong>PostIsPrivate&nbsp;Exception</strong> nhé. Thế nhưng, ở function khác bạn cũng dùng <strong>Exception</strong> này thì sao, nên tập trung lại 1 chỗ để dễ xử lý chứ phải không.</p>\r\n<p>Bây giờ function <code>show</code> trong <code>PostsController</code> trả lại như cũ:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">show</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">throw</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PostIsPrivate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Vào&nbsp;<code>app\\Exceptions\\Handler.php</code> function&nbsp;<code>render</code>:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Exceptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>PostIsPrivate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Exception <span class=\"token variable\">$exception</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$exception</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">instanceof</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PostIsPrivate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"Bài viết riêng tư\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n        \r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">parent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$exception</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Chạy lại trình duyệt:</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"img-thumbnail\" src=\"/image/posts/laravel/renderable-reportable-exceptions-render.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"351\" height=\"208\"></p>\r\n<p>Vẫn ok phải không nào anh em&nbsp;?&nbsp;Nhưng nếu như trong web app của mình có nhiều Exception thì sẽ thành như thế này sao:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Exception <span class=\"token variable\">$exception</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$exception</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">instanceof</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PostIsPrivate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"Bài viết riêng tư\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$exception</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">instanceof</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PostIsPrivate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"Bài viết riêng tư\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$exception</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">instanceof</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PostIsPrivate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"Bài viết riêng tư\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$exception</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">instanceof</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PostIsPrivate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"Bài viết riêng tư\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$exception</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">instanceof</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PostIsPrivate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"Bài viết riêng tư\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n        \r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">parent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$exception</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Chính vì vậy nên Laravel 5.5 mới đưa Exception vào xử lý riêng biệt, tránh project càng to càng phình ra không kiểm soát được.&nbsp;Tiếp theo trả lại&nbsp;<code>app\\Exceptions\\Handler.php</code>&nbsp;function&nbsp;<code>render</code>&nbsp;như cũ:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Exception <span class=\"token variable\">$exception</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">parent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$exception</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Quay lại&nbsp;app\\Exceptions\\PostIsPrivate.php lúc nãy chúng ta tạo function render:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Exceptions</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">PostIsPrivate</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Exception</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    	<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"Bài viết riêng tư\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>F5 trình duyệt thử xem nào&nbsp;?&nbsp;Kết quả vẫn giống lúc trước chứ.</p>\r\n<p>Lúc này mọi thứ đã trở nên sạch sẽ vô cùng phải không anh em. Bài viết có hơi vòng vo xí anh em nào rành rồi đừng ném gạch em nha&nbsp;??</p>\r\n            </div>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/cap-nhat-laravel-5-5-phan-4-exception-cuc-chat-ss', 1, 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 4: Exception Cực Chất&#039;ss', 'Đối với anh em code d&ugrave; l&agrave; web hay app g&igrave; th&igrave; exception l&agrave; thứ rất cần, đặt Exception th&iacute;ch hợp, ch&uacute;ng ta sẽ nắm bắt được lỗi xảy ra tr&ecirc;n web của m&igrave;nh để khắc phục lỗi sớm nhất.', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-4-exception-cuc-chat039ss', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Đối với anh em code d&ugrave; l&agrave; web hay app g&igrave; th&igrave; exception l&agrave; thứ rất cần, đặt Exception th&iacute;ch hợp, ch&uacute;ng ta sẽ nắm bắt được lỗi xảy ra tr&ecirc;n web của m&igrave;nh để khắc phục lỗi sớm nhất.'),
(16, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:49', '2019-08-11 14:17:51', 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 3: Blade Directives mới', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-3-blade-directives-moi', '<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n              <p>Ở bản <strong>Laravel 5.5</strong> sẽ được bổ sung 2&nbsp;<strong>Blade Directives</strong> mới đó là <code>@auth</code> và <code>@guest</code>. Chúng được sử dụng để check xem user đã đăng nhập hay chưa?</p>\r\n<p>Đến đây các bạn tự hỏi rằng với <a title=\"Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 2: Blade::if() Directives\" href=\"/posts/cap-nhat-laravel-5-5-blade-if-directives\">phần 2 Blade::if</a>&nbsp;thì các bạn có thể hoàn toàn tự custom được bằng đoạn code dưới đây mà.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Support<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Facades<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Blade</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\nBlade<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'auth\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">auth</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">check</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Xin thưa rằng, chính xác&nbsp;?&nbsp;Vậy <strong>Laravel</strong> đưa ra chi vậy, mình nghĩ chắc là 2&nbsp;<strong>Blade Directives</strong> được sử dụng khá nhiều nên được đưa vào.</p>\r\n<p>Với việc có thêm 2&nbsp;<strong>Blade Directives</strong> này thì ngoài view chúng ta khá dễ dàng tùy biến view mà k phải code nhiều và lặp lại như trước nữa.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">@auth\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Bạn đã đăng nhập</span>\r\n@<span class=\"token keyword\">else</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Bạn chưa đăng nhập</span>\r\n@endauth</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Và <code>@guest</code>:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">@guest\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Bạn chưa đăng nhập</span>\r\n@endguest</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Với website đang sử dụng multi auth thì với <code>@auth</code>&nbsp;<strong>Blade Directive</strong> sẽ&nbsp;pass vào 1 parameter.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-markup\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-markup\">@auth(\'admin\')\r\n    // Bạn đã đăng nhập với tư cách là Admin\r\n@else\r\n    // Bạn chưa đăng nhập\r\n@endauth</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Hi vọng sự thay đổi này sẽ giúp cho code của bạn trở nên dễ dàng và gọn gàng hơn!</span></p>\r\n            </div>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/cap-nhat-laravel-5-5-phan-3-blade-directives-moi', 1, 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 3: Blade Directives mới', 'Ở bản Laravel 5.5 sẽ được bổ sung 2&nbsp;Blade Directives mới đ&oacute; l&agrave; @auth v&agrave; @guest. Ch&uacute;ng được sử dụng để check xem user đ&atilde; đăng nhập hay chưa?', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-3-blade-directives-moi', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Ở bản Laravel 5.5 sẽ được bổ sung 2&nbsp;Blade Directives mới đ&oacute; l&agrave; @auth v&agrave; @guest. Ch&uacute;ng được sử dụng để check xem user đ&atilde; đăng nhập hay chưa?'),
(17, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:50', '2019-08-11 14:18:25', 1, 'Laravel 5.5 sẽ là phiên bản LTS Release tiếp theo', 'laravel-55-se-la-phien-ban-lts-release-tiep-theo', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>Phi&ecirc;n bản 5.1 l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n bản LTS đầu ti&ecirc;n của Laravel v&agrave;&nbsp;với hai năm sửa lỗi của n&oacute; sẽ kết th&uacute;c v&agrave;o cuối năm nay. C&acirc;u hỏi đặt ra l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n bản n&agrave;o sẽ được ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh l&agrave; LTS tiếp theo v&agrave; c&acirc;u trả lời ch&iacute;nh thức từ Laravel l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n bản Laravel&nbsp;5.5.</p>\r\n\r\n<figure><img alt=\"Laravel 5.5 sẽ là bản LTS Release tiếp theo - Twitter\" height=\"205\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel/laravel-5-5-release-twitter.PNG\" title=\"Laravel 5.5 sẽ là bản LTS Release tiếp theo - Twitter\" width=\"543\" />\r\n<figcaption>Laravel 5.5 sẽ l&agrave; bản LTS Release tiếp theo ra mắt th&aacute;ng 7/8 n&agrave;y - Twitter ch&iacute;nh thức từ Laravel</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>N&atilde;y giờ n&oacute;i về LTS th&igrave; c&oacute; nhiều bạn thắc mắc LTS l&agrave; g&igrave; nhỉ&nbsp;?</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p><strong>LTS</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave; viết tắt của &quot;<strong>Long Term Support</strong>&quot; - c&oacute; nghĩa l&agrave; &quot;Hỗ trợ d&agrave;i hạn&quot;.&nbsp;Phi&ecirc;n bản Laravel LTS l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n bản được fix bugs trong 2 năm v&agrave; cập nhật bảo mật trong 3 năm.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-5-5-se-la-phien-ban-lts-release-tiep-theo', 1, 1, 'Laravel 5.5 sẽ là phiên bản LTS Release tiếp theo', 'Phi&ecirc;n bản 5.1 l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n bản LTS đầu ti&ecirc;n của Laravel v&agrave;&nbsp;với hai năm sửa lỗi của n&oacute; sẽ kết th&uacute;c v&agrave;o cuối năm nay. C&acirc;u hỏi đặt ra l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n bản n&agrave;o sẽ được ph&aacute;t h&agrav', 'laravel-55-se-la-phien-ban-lts-release-tiep-theo', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Phi&ecirc;n bản 5.1 l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n bản LTS đầu ti&ecirc;n của Laravel v&agrave;&nbsp;với hai năm sửa lỗi của n&oacute; sẽ kết th&uacute;c v&agrave;o cuối năm nay. C&acirc;u hỏi đặt ra l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n bản n&agrave;o sẽ được ph&aacute;t h&agrave'),
(18, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:52', '2019-08-11 14:19:03', 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 1: Sự trở lại của Whoops', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-1-su-tro-lai-cua-whoops', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>Như c&aacute;c bạn đ&atilde; biết&nbsp;<strong>Whoops</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave; 1 framework xử l&yacute; lỗi được c&agrave;i đặt trong&nbsp;<strong>Laravel 4</strong>&nbsp;v&agrave; bị gỡ 1 c&aacute;ch phũ ph&agrave;ng ở phi&ecirc;n bản&nbsp;<strong>Laravel 5.0</strong>. Nhưng giờ đ&acirc;y n&oacute; đ&atilde; quay trở lại&nbsp;<strong>Laravel 5.5</strong>&nbsp;v&agrave; lợi hại hơn xưa&nbsp;?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dưới đ&acirc;y l&agrave; 1 số t&iacute;nh năng của&nbsp;<strong>Whoops</strong>:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Flexible, stack-based error handling</li>\r\n	<li>Stand-alone library with (currently) no required dependencies</li>\r\n	<li>Simple API for dealing with exceptions, trace frames &amp; their data</li>\r\n	<li>Includes a pretty rad error page for your webapp projects</li>\r\n	<li>Includes the ability to open referenced files directly in your editor and IDE</li>\r\n	<li>Includes handlers for different response formats (JSON, XML, SOAP)</li>\r\n	<li>Easy to extend and integrate with existing libraries</li>\r\n	<li>Clean, well-structured &amp; tested code-base</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Tạm dịch google ?&nbsp;l&agrave;:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Xử l&yacute; lỗi dựa tr&ecirc;n ngăn xếp, linh hoạt.</li>\r\n	<li>Thư viện độc lập với (hiện tại) kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; phụ thuộc bắt buộc</li>\r\n	<li>API đơn giản để giải quyết c&aacute;c trường hợp ngoại lệ, đ&oacute;ng khung dấu vết&nbsp;v&agrave; dữ liệu của ch&uacute;ng</li>\r\n	<li>Bao gồm một trang error&nbsp;<strong>rad</strong>&nbsp;cực đẹp cho c&aacute;c dự &aacute;n webapp của bạn</li>\r\n	<li>Bao gồm khả năng mở c&aacute;c tệp được tham chiếu trực tiếp trong tr&igrave;nh soạn thảo v&agrave; IDE của bạn</li>\r\n	<li>Bao gồm tr&igrave;nh xử l&yacute; cho c&aacute;c định dạng phản hồi kh&aacute;c nhau (JSON, XML, SOAP)</li>\r\n	<li>Dễ d&agrave;ng mở rộng v&agrave; t&iacute;ch hợp với c&aacute;c thư viện hiện c&oacute;.</li>\r\n	<li>Sạch, c&oacute; cấu tr&uacute;c tốt v&agrave; đ&atilde; được thử nghiệm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>H&atilde;y xem nhưng g&igrave; Whoops l&agrave;m được dưới đ&acirc;y, chỉ lỗi đến tận ch&acirc;n răng&nbsp;?</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img height=\"450\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel/laravel-55-whoops-2.png\" width=\"800\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/cap-nhat-laravel-5-5-phan-1-su-tro-lai-cua-whoops', 1, 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 1: Sự trở lại của Whoops', 'Như c&aacute;c bạn đ&atilde; biết Whoops l&agrave; 1 framework xử l&yacute; lỗi được c&agrave;i đặt trong Laravel 4 v&agrave; bị gỡ 1 c&aacute;ch phũ ph&agrave;ng ở phi&ecirc;n bản Laravel 5.0. Nhưng giờ đ&acirc;y n&oacute; đ&atilde; quay trở lại Laravel', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-1-su-tro-lai-cua-whoops', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Như c&aacute;c bạn đ&atilde; biết Whoops l&agrave; 1 framework xử l&yacute; lỗi được c&agrave;i đặt trong Laravel 4 v&agrave; bị gỡ 1 c&aacute;ch phũ ph&agrave;ng ở phi&ecirc;n bản Laravel 5.0. Nhưng giờ đ&acirc;y n&oacute; đ&atilde; quay trở lại Laravel 5'),
(19, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:56', '2019-08-11 14:19:39', 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 2: Blade::if() Directives', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-2-bladeif-directives', '<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n              <h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bohv396m0\">Viết Blade::if() Directives</h2>\r\n<p>Trong phiên bản <strong>laravel 5.5</strong> sẽ bổ sung thêm 1&nbsp;<strong>Directives</strong> mới hỗ trợ cú pháp if trong <strong>blade views</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>Cú pháp được viết&nbsp;trong phương thức <code>boot</code> của <code>Service Provider</code> chẳng hạn <code>AppServiceProvider :: boot ()</code>:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Support<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Facades<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Blade</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\nBlade<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'admin\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">auth</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">check</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;&amp;</span> <span class=\"token function\">auth</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">user</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">isAdmin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Với&nbsp;<strong>Blade::if()</strong> mới này sẽ tạo sự thuận tiện trong code views, dễ đọc hơn rất nhiều và tránh sự lặp đi lặp lại 1 đoạn code nào đó nhiều lần, mà các bạn biết rồi <strong>DRY (Don\'t Repeat Yourself - Đừng lặp lại chính mình)</strong> đây hẳn là 1 điều mà tôi mà mong chờ, bây giờ ngoài view chỉ cần viết như thế này:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">@admin\r\n    Page này chỉ dành cho Admin\r\n@<span class=\"token keyword\">else</span>\r\n    Welcome Guest<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> Chào khách<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> hãy đăng nhập\r\n@endadmin</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Nếu như trước đây bạn phải viết nhiều code hơn <em>(xem hình)</em>:</p>\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" title=\"Cập nhật Laravel 5.5: Blade::if() Directives\" src=\"/image/posts/laravel/blade-if-twitter-newfeed.jpg\" alt=\"Cập nhật Laravel 5.5: Blade::if() Directives\" width=\"1168\" height=\"682\">\r\n<figcaption>Một đoạn code dài trước khi có <strong>Blade::if() Directives</strong></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p>Thì bây giờ trong <strong>Laravel 5.5</strong> chỉ còn như thế này thôi:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">Blade<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'prod\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">app</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">environment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'production\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Bạn có thể thêm tham số để trở nên linh động hơn:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">Blade<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'env\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$env</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">app</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">environment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$env</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Và lúc này ngoài views template chỉ cần viết thế này thôi:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Tôi chỉ muốn đoạn mã script này chạy trên server thôi</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Còn trên local thì miễn đi</span>\r\n@<span class=\"token function\">env</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'production\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n  \r\n@endenv\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Laravel thật là trất\'ss phải không nào các bro!!</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bohv396m1\">&nbsp;</h2>\r\n            </div>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/cap-nhat-laravel-5-5-blade-if-directives', 1, 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 2: Blade::if() Directives', 'Trong phi&ecirc;n bản laravel 5.5 sẽ bổ sung th&ecirc;m 1&nbsp;Directives mới hỗ trợ c&uacute; ph&aacute;p if trong blade views.', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-2-bladeif-directives', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Trong phi&ecirc;n bản laravel 5.5 sẽ bổ sung th&ecirc;m 1&nbsp;Directives mới hỗ trợ c&uacute; ph&aacute;p if trong blade views.');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(20, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:20:59', '2019-08-11 14:20:10', 1, 'Laravel response json with UTF-8 charset', 'laravel-response-json-with-utf-8-charset', '<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n              <p>Trong laravel khi muốn response với&nbsp;Content-type&nbsp;là application/json thì nhưng ký tự sẽ bị mã hóa rất khó đọc như ví dụ dưới đây</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">response</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">json</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'もう、投稿でした。\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Và đây là kết quả:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-markup\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-markup\">\"\\u3082\\u3046\\u3001\\u6295\\u7a3f\\u3067\\u3057\\u305f\\u3002\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Thêm đoạn headers sau kết quả sẽ khác ngay:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">response</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">json</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'もう、投稿でした。\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">200</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Content-type\'</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'application/json; charset=utf-8\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token constant\">JSON_UNESCAPED_UNICODE</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"img-thumbnail\" title=\"Laravel response json with UTF-8 charset\" src=\"/image/laravel-response-json-with-utf-8-charset.png\" alt=\"Laravel response json with UTF-8 charset\" width=\"464\" height=\"126\"></p>\r\n            </div>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-response-json-with-utf-8-charset', 1, 1, 'Laravel response json with UTF-8 charset', 'Trong laravel khi muốn response với&nbsp;Content-type&nbsp;l&agrave; application/json th&igrave; nhưng k&yacute; tự sẽ bị m&atilde; h&oacute;a rất kh&oacute; đọc như v&iacute; dụ dưới đ&acirc;y', 'laravel-response-json-with-utf-8-charset', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Trong laravel khi muốn response với&nbsp;Content-type&nbsp;l&agrave; application/json th&igrave; nhưng k&yacute; tự sẽ bị m&atilde; h&oacute;a rất kh&oacute; đọc như v&iacute; dụ dưới đ&acirc;y'),
(21, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:21:01', '2019-08-11 14:21:36', 1, 'Có gì mới trong phiên bản laravel 5.5 sắp tới?', 'co-gi-moi-trong-phien-ban-laravel-55-sap-toi', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>Phi&ecirc;n bản tiếp theo của <strong>Laravel</strong> l&agrave; <strong>Laravel 5.5</strong> (hiện tại l&agrave; 5.4) được l&ecirc;n kế hoạch ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 7 năm 2017, vậy sẽ c&oacute; g&igrave; đ&aacute;ng mong đợi ở phi&ecirc;n bản n&agrave;y?</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bet3cot07\">1. Laravel 5.5 sẽ y&ecirc;u cầu PHP 7.0+</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu bạn vẫn đang sử dụng PHP 5.x tr&ecirc;n m&aacute;y của m&igrave;nh th&igrave; bạn n&ecirc;n bắt đầu suy nghĩ về việc n&acirc;ng cấp l&ecirc;n PHP 7+ đi th&ocirc;i, PHP 7 tuyệt hơn PHP 5.x nhiều v&agrave; cũng v&igrave; Laravel 5.5 sẽ y&ecirc;u cầu PHP 7+ đấy</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bet3cot18\">2. Laravel 5.5 sẽ l&agrave; bản LTS Release tiếp theo</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Phi&ecirc;n bản Laravel 5.1 l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n bản LTS (Long Term Support - Hỗ trợ d&agrave;i hạn) ch&iacute;nh thức đầu ti&ecirc;n của <strong>Laravel</strong> v&agrave; <strong>Laravel 5.5</strong> sẽ l&agrave; phi&ecirc;n bản LTS tiếp theo.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bet3cot19\">3. &quot;vendor:publish&quot; command sẽ xuất hiện nhắc nhở khi chạy</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Với phi&ecirc;n bản hiện tại, command<code> vendor:publish</code> sẽ publish mọi thứ n&oacute; t&igrave;m thấy, bao gồm <code>configs</code>, <code>views</code>, <code>migrations</code> v&agrave; nhiều hơn nữa, nhưng trong phi&ecirc;n bản <strong>Laravel 5.5</strong>, command n&agrave;y sẽ nhắc nhở bạn để chọn lựa những g&igrave; bạn thực sự muốn publish.<br />\r\n<img alt=\"Có gì mới trong phiên bản laravel 5.5 sắp tới?\" height=\"424\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/co-gi-moi-trong-phien-ban-laravel-5-5-sap-toi-1.png\" title=\"Có gì mới trong phiên bản laravel 5.5 sắp tới?\" width=\"825\" /><br />\r\nNgo&agrave;i ra bạn cũng c&oacute; thể th&ecirc;m flag --all hoặc --provider để chỉ cho n&oacute; biết bạn muốn publish những g&igrave;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bet3cot1a\">4. Bạn c&oacute; thể render trực tiếp Mailables l&ecirc;n tr&igrave;nh duyệt</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Bạn đ&atilde; từng lặp đi lặp lại c&ugrave;ng 1 việc l&agrave; gửi m&atilde;i một bức thư để xem giao diện của n&oacute; như thế n&agrave;o? Qu&ecirc;n đi, với <strong>Laravel 5.5</strong> mọi việc trở n&ecirc;n dễ d&agrave;ng hơn nhiều.<br />\r\nĐể tạo UserWelcome Mailable:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">php artisan make:mail UserWelcome --markdown=emails.user.welcome</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>V&agrave; bạn c&oacute; thể xem ngay giao diện của &quot;bức thư&quot; n&agrave;y bằng c&aacute;ch:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;/demo&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Mail<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>UserWelcome</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Truy cập v&agrave;o domain/demo v&agrave; mọi thứ hiện ra<br />\r\n<img alt=\"Có gì mới trong phiên bản laravel 5.5 sắp tới?\" height=\"430\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/co-gi-moi-trong-phien-ban-laravel-5-5-sap-toi-2.png\" title=\"Có gì mới trong phiên bản laravel 5.5 sắp tới?\" width=\"600\" /><br />\r\nThật qu&aacute; easỳ đ&uacute;ng kh&ocirc;ng n&agrave;o!</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bet3cot1b\">5. Tự viết theme cho Mailables</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Tạo một file css chứa định dạng bạn mong muốn cho Mailables theo đường dẫn:</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>resources/views/vendor/mail/html/themes/my-theme.css</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau đ&oacute; update lại file cấu h&igrave;nh mail.php như sau</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;markdown&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;theme&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;my-theme&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;paths&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token function\">resource_path</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;views/vendor/mail&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Cuối c&ugrave;ng, đơn giản l&agrave; sử dụng theme cho mail của bạn th&ocirc;i</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">SendInvoice</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Mailable</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$theme</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;my-theme&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bet3cot1c\">6. Laravel Migrate Fresh Command</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi bạn chạy lệnh php artisan migrate:refresh</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">Rolling back: 2014_10_12_100000_create_password_resets_table\r\nRolled back: 2014_10_12_100000_create_password_resets_table\r\nRolling back: 2014_10_12_000000_create_users_table\r\nRolled back: 2014_10_12_000000_create_users_table\r\nMigrating: 2014_10_12_000000_create_users_table\r\nMigrated: 2014_10_12_000000_create_users_table\r\nMigrating: 2014_10_12_100000_create_password_resets_table\r\nMigrated: 2014_10_12_100000_create_password_resets_table</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>V&agrave; khi chạy lệnh php artisan migrate:fresh mới tr&ecirc;n Laravel 5.5</p>\r\n\r\n<pre>\r\nDropped all tables successfully.\r\nMigration table created successfully.\r\nMigrating: 2014_10_12_000000_create_users_table\r\nMigrated: 2014_10_12_000000_create_users_table\r\nMigrating: 2014_10_12_100000_create_password_resets_table\r\nMigrated: 2014_10_12_100000_create_password_resets_table</pre>\r\n\r\n<p>Sự kh&aacute;c biệt l&agrave; command migrate:fresh sẽ drop to&agrave;n bộ table thay v&igrave; rollback lại c&aacute;c migrate.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1bet3cot1d\">7. Adds Frontend Presets</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Bắt đầu từ phi&ecirc;n bản 5.3, Laravel đ&atilde; được bao gồm <strong>Bootstrap</strong> v&agrave; <strong>Vue.js</strong> để bạn c&oacute; thể nhanh ch&oacute;ng tạo một ứng dụng bạn mong muốn.<br />\r\nSang phi&ecirc;n bản 5.5 bạn sẽ c&oacute; thể lựa chọn để sử dụng g&igrave; v&agrave; loại bỏ g&igrave; khỏi ứng dụng của m&igrave;nh với command preset</p>\r\n\r\n<p>React Preset<br />\r\n<code>php artisan preset react</code><br />\r\nSau khi chạy, n&oacute; sẽ thay thế Vue.js bằng React trong ứng dụng của bạn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bootstrap Preset<br />\r\n<code>php artisan preset bootstrap</code><br />\r\nLệnh n&agrave;y sẽ chỉ giữ lại Bootstrap CSS, kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n Vue.j hay React...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Loại bỏ cả Bootstrap v&agrave; Vue.js<br />\r\n<code>php artisan preset none</code><br />\r\nSẽ kh&ocirc;ng c&ograve;n g&igrave; nữa, kh&ocirc;ng Bootstrap, kh&ocirc;ng Vue.js</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Laravel 5.5 sẽ rất đ&aacute;ng mong đợi phải kh&ocirc;ng mọi người!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/co-gi-moi-trong-phien-ban-laravel-5-5-sap-toi', 1, 1, 'Có gì mới trong phiên bản laravel 5.5 sắp tới?', 'Phi&ecirc;n bản tiếp theo của Laravel l&agrave; Laravel 5.5 (hiện tại l&agrave; 5.4) được l&ecirc;n kế hoạch ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 7 năm 2017, vậy sẽ c&oacute; g&igrave; đ&aacute;ng mong đợi ở phi&ecirc;n bản n&agrave;y?', 'co-gi-moi-trong-phien-ban-laravel-55-sap-toi', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Phi&ecirc;n bản tiếp theo của Laravel l&agrave; Laravel 5.5 (hiện tại l&agrave; 5.4) được l&ecirc;n kế hoạch ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 7 năm 2017, vậy sẽ c&oacute; g&igrave; đ&aacute;ng mong đợi ở phi&ecirc;n bản n&agrave;y?'),
(24, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:21:12', '2019-08-11 13:56:35', 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 14: What&#039;s New in Laravel Mix', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-14-what039s-new-in-laravel-mix', '<div class=\"text-left\">               <p>https://laracasts.com/series/whats-new-in-laravel-5-5/episodes/11</p>             </div>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/cap-nhat-laravel-5-5-phan-14-what-s-new-in-laravel-mix', 1, 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 14: What&#039;s New in Laravel Mix', 'https://laracasts.com/series/whats-new-in-laravel-5-5/episodes/11', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-14-what039s-new-in-laravel-mix', '[\"\"]', 1, 'https://laracasts.com/series/whats-new-in-laravel-5-5/episodes/11'),
(31, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:21:26', '2019-08-11 14:25:04', 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 7: Render Mail trực tiếp trên browser', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-7-render-mail-truc-tiep-tren-browser', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>Trước đ&acirc;y để l&agrave;m việc về phần email bạn sẽ phải cấu h&igrave;nh driver smtp hay qua c&aacute;c mail services kh&aacute;c tốn rất nhiều k&igrave; c&ocirc;ng, sau đ&oacute; gửi email đến ch&iacute;nh email của m&igrave;nh, hoặc sử dụng c&aacute;c phương thức test kh&aacute;c để cuối c&ugrave;ng gửi 1 bản email ho&agrave;n chỉnh cho kh&aacute;ch h&agrave;ng hay người d&ugrave;ng của trang web m&igrave;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Với sự thay đổi mới n&agrave;y trong Laravel 5.5 bạn c&oacute; thể render email markdown template trực tiếp tr&ecirc;n browser. Chạy command dưới đ&acirc;y:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">php artisan make:mail OrderShipped --markdown=emails.orders.shipped</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>File&nbsp;<code>app\\Mail\\OrderShipped.php</code>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Mail</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Bus<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Queueable</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Mail<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Mailable</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Queue<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>SerializesModels</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Contracts<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Queue<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>ShouldQueue</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">OrderShipped</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Mailable</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Queueable</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> SerializesModels<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Create a new message instance.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">__construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">//</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Build the message.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return $this\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">build</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">markdown</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;emails.orders.shipped&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Khai b&aacute;o route sau trong&nbsp;<code>routes\\web.php</code></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;order-ship&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Mail<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>OrderShipped</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Chạy url tr&ecirc;n tr&igrave;nh duyệt</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 7: Render Mail trực tiếp trên browser\" height=\"523\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel/cap-nhat-laravel-5-5-phan-7-render-mail-truc-tiep-tren-browser.png\" title=\"Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 7: Render Mail trực tiếp trên browser\" width=\"695\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Với mọi chỉnh sửa của bạn trong file&nbsp;<code>resources\\views\\emails\\orders\\shipped.blade.php</code> sẽ&nbsp;cho ra kết quả ngay tr&ecirc;n browser m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng phải kỳ c&ocirc;ng như trước.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/cap-nhat-laravel-5-5-phan-7-render-mail-truc-tiep-tren-browser', 1, 1, 'Cập nhật Laravel 5.5 Phần 7: Render Mail trực tiếp trên browser', 'Trước đ&acirc;y để l&agrave;m việc về phần email bạn sẽ phải cấu h&igrave;nh driver smtp hay qua c&aacute;c mail services kh&aacute;c tốn rất nhiều k&igrave; c&ocirc;ng, sau đ&oacute; gửi email đến ch&iacute;nh email của m&igrave;nh, hoặc sử dụng c&aacute', 'cap-nhat-laravel-55-phan-7-render-mail-truc-tiep-tren-browser', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Trước đ&acirc;y để l&agrave;m việc về phần email bạn sẽ phải cấu h&igrave;nh driver smtp hay qua c&aacute;c mail services kh&aacute;c tốn rất nhiều k&igrave; c&ocirc;ng, sau đ&oacute; gửi email đến ch&iacute;nh email của m&igrave;nh, hoặc sử dụng c&aacute;'),
(32, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:21:34', '2019-08-11 14:25:49', 1, 'Cấu hình Laravel', 'cau-hinh-laravel', '<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n              <h2 id=\"Giới_thiệu\">Giới thiệu</h2>\r\n<p>Tất cả các file cấu hình cho Laravel được lưu trong thư mục&nbsp;<code>config</code>. Mỗi thông số đều được ghi chú lại, vì thế hãy xem nội dung các file để làm quen với các thông số mà bạn có thể sử dụng.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"Truy_xuất_vào_các_giá_trị_cấu_hình\">Truy xuất vào các giá trị cấu hình</h2>\r\n<p>Bạn có thể dễ dàng truy xuất vào các giá trị cấu hình sử dụng hàm helper&nbsp;<code>config</code>&nbsp;tại bất cứ đâu trong Laravel. Giá trị cấu hình có thể được lấy ra sử dụng cú pháp \"dot\", bao gồm tên file và tên thông số bạn muốn lấy ra. Giá trị mặc định có thể được trả về nếu thông số về cấu hình đó không tồn tại:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$value</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">config</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'app.timezone\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Để thiết lập giá trị cấu hình lúc thực thi, truyền vào một mảng cho helper&nbsp;<code>config</code>:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token function\">config</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'app.timezone\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'America/Chicago\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h2 id=\"Cấu_hình_môi_trường\">Cấu hình môi trường</h2>\r\n<p>Thông thường, có nhiều giá trị cấu hình khác nhau tuỳ thuộc vào môi trường đang chạy sẽ khá là hữu ích. Ví dụ, bạn có thể sử dụng một cache driver khác với khi chạy trên server production. Việc sử dụng môi trường dựa trên cấu hình cũng khá là dễ dàng.</p>\r\n<p>Laravel tận dụng thư viện&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/vlucas/phpdotenv\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">DotEnv</a>&nbsp;được phát triển Vance Lucas để thực hiện điều này. Với một ứng dụng cài mới, tại thư mục gốc sẽ có chứa một file&nbsp;<code>.env.example</code>. Nếu bạn cài Laravel thông qua Composer, file này sẽ được tự động đổi tên thành&nbsp;<code>.env</code>. Nếu không thì bạn cần tự chỉnh lại tên file.</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%; height: auto; clear: none;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-1450596627252330\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; background-color: transparent;\"><ins id=\"aswift_1_expand\" style=\"display: inline-table; border: none; height: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 698px; background-color: transparent;\"><ins id=\"aswift_1_anchor\" style=\"display: block; border: none; height: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 698px; background-color: transparent; overflow: visible; opacity: 1;\"><iframe width=\"698\" height=\"175\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" onload=\"var i=this.id,s=window.google_iframe_oncopy,H=s&amp;&amp;s.handlers,h=H&amp;&amp;H[i],w=this.contentWindow,d;try{d=w.document}catch(e){}if(h&amp;&amp;d&amp;&amp;(!d.body||!d.body.firstChild)){if(h.call){setTimeout(h,0)}else if(h.match){try{h=s.upd(h,i)}catch(e){}w.location.replace(h)}}\" id=\"aswift_1\" name=\"aswift_1\" style=\"left:0;position:absolute;top:0;border:0px;width:698px;height:175px;\"></iframe></ins></ins></ins></div>\r\n<p>Tất cả các biến liệt kê trong file sẽ được load lên vào trong biến super-global&nbsp;<code>$_ENV</code>&nbsp;của PHP khi ứng dụng nhận một request. Tuy nhiên, bạn có thể sử dụng hàm helper&nbsp;<code>env</code>&nbsp;để nhận các giá trị này từ các biến trong file cấu hình. Thực tế thì, nếu bạn xem nội dung file cấu hình của Laravel, bạn sẽ để ý thấy có vài thông số đã sử dụng hàm helper này rồi:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'debug\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token function\">env</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'APP_DEBUG\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Giá trị thứ hai truyền vào trong&nbsp;<code>env</code>&nbsp;là <em><strong>\"giá trị mặc định\"</strong></em>. Giá trị này sẽ được sử dụng nếu <code>APP_DEBUG</code> không tồn tại trong file <code>.env</code>.</p>\r\n<p>File&nbsp;<code>.env</code>&nbsp;là file được dùng để tùy biến cho nhiều ngườikhông nên được lưu trong source control của ứng dụng, vì mỗi lập trình viên hay server sử dụng có thể yêu cầu các thông số môi trường khác nhau.</p>\r\n<p>Nếu bạn đang phát triển với một team, bạn có thể muốn tiếp tục lưu lại file&nbsp;<code>.env.example</code>&nbsp;trong ứng dụng. Bằng cách đặt các giá trị ví dụ vào trong file cấu hình, các lập trình viên khác trong team có thể thấy rõ ràng biến môi trường nào là cần thiết để chạy ứng dụng.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"Xác_định_môi_trường_hiện_tại\">Xác định môi trường hiện tại</h3>\r\n<p>Môi trường hiện tại của ứng dụng được xác định thông qua biến&nbsp;<code>APP_ENV</code>&nbsp;trong file&nbsp;<code>.env</code>. Bạn có thể lấy giá trị này thông qua hàm&nbsp;<code>environment</code>&nbsp;trong&nbsp;<code>App</code>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/petehouston/laravel-docs-vn/blob/master/docs/%7B%7Bversion%7D%7D/facades\">facade</a>:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$environment</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> App<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">environment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Bạn cũng có thể truyền tham số vào trong hàm&nbsp;<code>environment</code>&nbsp;để kiểm tra xem môi trường có khớp không. Nếu cần thiết, bạn có thể truyền vào nhiều giá trị cho hàm&nbsp;<code>environment</code>. Nếu môi trường đúng với giá trị truyền vào, hàm sẽ trả về&nbsp;<code>true</code>:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>App<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">environment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'local\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Nếu môi trường là local</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>App<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">environment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'local\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'staging\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Nếu môi trường là local hoặc staging...</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Đối tượng truy xuất ứng dụng cũng có thể được sử dụng thông qua helper&nbsp;<code>app</code>:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$environment</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">app</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">environment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h2 id=\"Thực_hiện_cache_cấu_hình\">Thực hiện cache cấu hình</h2>\r\n<p>Để tăng tốc cho ứng dụng, bạn nên cache lại các file cấu hình sử dụng câu lệnh Artisan&nbsp;<code>config:cache</code>. Lệnh này sẽ gộp tất cả các thông số cấu hình trong ứng dụng vào trong một file để có thể được load lên nhanh chóng.</p>\r\n<p>Bạn nên chạy lệnh&nbsp;<code>php artisan config:cache</code>&nbsp;trong quá trình triển khai môi trường production. Lệnh này không nên chạy ở môi trường phát triển vì các thông số cấu hình sẽ liên tục bị thay đổi trong khi phát triển.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"Chế_độ_bảo_trì\">Chế độ bảo trì</h2>\r\n<p>Khi ứng dụng của bạn ở trong chế độ bảo trì, một view riêng được hiển thị cho tất cả các request tới ứng dụng. Điều này làm cho việc \"disable\" ứng dụng dễ dàng hơn khi bạn đang thực hiện cập nhật hay khi đang thực hiện bảo trì. Việc kiểm tra bảo trì nằm trong stack middleware mặc định. Nếu ứng dụng nằm trong chế độ bảo trì, thì một exception là&nbsp;<code>HttpException</code>&nbsp;sẽ được bắn ra với status code là 503.</p>\r\n<p>Để kích hoạt chế độ bảo trì, đơn giản gõ lệnh&nbsp;<code>down</code>:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-bash\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-bash\">php artisan down</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Bạn cũng có thể cung cấp các tùy chọn&nbsp;<code class=\"  language-php\" style=\"font-family: \'Operator Mono\', \'Fira Code\', Consolas, Monaco, \'Andale Mono\', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #f4645f; border-radius: 3px; background-color: #f0f2f1; padding: 1px 5px; word-spacing: 0px; text-shadow: #ffffff 0px 1px; line-height: 2; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle;\">message</code><span style=\"color: #525252; font-family: \'Whitney SSm A\', \'Whitney SSm B\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;và&nbsp;<code class=\"  language-php\" style=\"font-family: \'Operator Mono\', \'Fira Code\', Consolas, Monaco, \'Andale Mono\', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #f4645f; border-radius: 3px; background-color: #f0f2f1; padding: 1px 5px; word-spacing: 0px; text-shadow: #ffffff 0px 1px; line-height: 2; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle;\">retry</code><span style=\"color: #525252; font-family: \'Whitney SSm A\', \'Whitney SSm B\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;cho lệnh&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #e83e8c; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 14px; background-color: #bfe6ff;\">down</span>. Giá trị&nbsp;<code class=\"  language-php\" style=\"font-family: \'Operator Mono\', \'Fira Code\', Consolas, Monaco, \'Andale Mono\', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #f4645f; text-shadow: #ffffff 0px 1px; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 2; background-color: #f0f2f1; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle;\">message</code><span style=\"color: #525252; font-family: \'Whitney SSm A\', \'Whitney SSm B\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;có thể được sử dụng để hiển thị hoặc ghi lại log, trong khi giá trị&nbsp;<code class=\"  language-php\" style=\"font-family: \'Operator Mono\', \'Fira Code\', Consolas, Monaco, \'Andale Mono\', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #f4645f; text-shadow: #ffffff 0px 1px; word-spacing: 0px; line-height: 2; background-color: #f0f2f1; padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle;\">retry</code><span style=\"color: #525252; font-family: \'Whitney SSm A\', \'Whitney SSm B\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;sẽ được đặt làm&nbsp;<code class=\"  language-php\" style=\"font-family: \'Operator Mono\', \'Fira Code\', Consolas, Monaco, \'Andale Mono\', monospace; font-size: 12px; color: #f4645f; border-radius: 3px; background-color: #f0f2f1; padding: 1px 5px; word-spacing: 0px; text-shadow: #ffffff 0px 1px; line-height: 2; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.125) 0px 1px 1px; vertical-align: middle;\">Retry<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>After</code><span style=\"color: #525252; font-family: \'Whitney SSm A\', \'Whitney SSm B\', sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp; trong&nbsp;</span>HTTP header:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-bash\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-bash\">php artisan down --message<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Upgrading Database\"</span> --retry<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>60</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Để tắt chế độ bảo trì, sử dụng lệnh&nbsp;<code>up</code>:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-bash\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-bash\">php artisan up</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"Template_ở_chế_độ_bảo_trì\">Template ở chế độ bảo trì</h3>\r\n<p>Template sử dụng cho chế độ bảo trì nằm tại&nbsp;<code>resources/views/errors/503.blade.php</code>. Bạn hoàn toàn có quyền thay đổi view này theo ý riêng của bạn. Nếu file này chưa có, bạn hãy tự tạo ra nhé.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"Chế_độ_bảo_trì_và_queue\">Chế độ bảo trì và queue</h3>\r\n<p>Khi ứng dụng của bạn ở trong trạng thái bảo trì, queued jobs&nbsp;sẽ ngưng thực hiện. Các jobs sẽ tiếp tục được xử lý bình thường khi nào mà ứng dụng không còn trong trạng thái bảo trì nữa.</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"Giải_pháp_khác_cho_chế_độ_bảo_trì\">Giải pháp khác cho chế độ bảo trì</h3>\r\n<p>Vì chế độ bảo trì yêu cầu ứng dụng của bạn bị down trong vài giây, bạn có thể sử dụng cách khác như&nbsp;Envoyer&nbsp;để không có thời gian down khi triển khai với <strong>Laravel</strong>.</p>\r\n            </div>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/cau-hinh-laravel', 1, 1, 'Cấu hình Laravel', 'Tất cả c&aacute;c file cấu h&igrave;nh cho Laravel được lưu trong thư mục&nbsp;config. Mỗi th&ocirc;ng số đều được ghi ch&uacute; lại, v&igrave; thế h&atilde;y xem nội dung c&aacute;c file để l&agrave;m quen với c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng số m&agrave; bạn c&o', 'cau-hinh-laravel', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Tất cả c&aacute;c file cấu h&igrave;nh cho Laravel được lưu trong thư mục&nbsp;config. Mỗi th&ocirc;ng số đều được ghi ch&uacute; lại, v&igrave; thế h&atilde;y xem nội dung c&aacute;c file để l&agrave;m quen với c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng số m&agrave; bạn c&oa');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(33, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:21:36', '2019-08-11 14:26:47', 1, 'Cài đặt Laravel', 'cai-dat-laravel', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cgo2tbr60\">Y&ecirc;u cầu Server</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Laravel framework</strong> c&oacute; một v&agrave;i y&ecirc;u cầu về hệ thống. Hiển nhi&ecirc;n l&agrave; c&aacute;c y&ecirc;u cầu n&agrave;y đ&atilde; được đầy đủ trong&nbsp;<a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/master/homestead\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Laravel Homestead\">Laravel Homestead</a>, v&igrave; thế Laravel rất khuyến kh&iacute;ch c&aacute;c bạn sử dụng <strong>Homestead</strong> cho m&ocirc;i trường ph&aacute;t triển. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n với những bạn kh&ocirc;ng r&agrave;nh cấu h&igrave;nh phức tạp c&oacute; thể d&ugrave;ng web server phổ biến tr&ecirc;n localhost l&agrave; XAMPP.&nbsp;C&agrave;i đặt localhost tr&ecirc;n m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh với XAMPP, xem b&agrave;i&nbsp;<a href=\"/posts/cai-dat-localhost-tren-may-tinh-voi-xampp\" title=\"Cài đặt localhost trên máy tính với XAMPP\">C&agrave;i đặt localhost tr&ecirc;n m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh với XAMPP</a> để tham khảo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu bạn kh&ocirc;ng sử dụng <strong>Homestead</strong>, bạn cần đảm bảo server đ&aacute;p ứng c&aacute;c y&ecirc;u cầu sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>PHP &gt;= 7.1.3 (<strong>Laravel 5.6</strong>)</li>\r\n	<li>OpenSSL PHP Extension</li>\r\n	<li>PDO PHP Extension</li>\r\n	<li>Mbstring PHP Extension</li>\r\n	<li>Tokenizer PHP Extension</li>\r\n	<li>XML PHP Extension</li>\r\n	<li>Ctype PHP Extension</li>\r\n	<li>JSON PHP Extension</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cgo2tbr61\">C&agrave;i đặt Laravel</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Laravel tận dụng <a href=\"/posts/composer-cong-cu-tuyet-voi-danh-cho-php\" title=\"Composer\">Composer</a> để quản l&yacute; c&aacute;c dependencies. V&igrave; thế, trước khi sử dụng Laravel, h&atilde;y chắc chắn l&agrave; bạn đ&atilde; c&agrave;i Composer tr&ecirc;n m&aacute;y. Tham khảo b&agrave;i viết:&nbsp;<a href=\"/posts/composer-cong-cu-tuyet-voi-danh-cho-php\" title=\"Composer - Công cụ tuyệt vời dành cho PHP\">Composer - C&ocirc;ng cụ tuyệt vời d&agrave;nh cho PHP</a>&nbsp;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1cgo2tbr62\">C&aacute;ch 1:&nbsp;Sử dụng Laravel Installer</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Đầu ti&ecirc;n, download tool c&agrave;i đặt Laravel installer sử dụng Composer, ch&uacute;ng ta mở terminal l&ecirc;n (Windows l&agrave; PowerShell) v&agrave; chạy l&ecirc;n sau</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-bash\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-bash\">composer global require <span class=\"token string\">&quot;laravel/installer&quot;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Laravel Installer\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel-installer.png\" title=\"Laravel Installer\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-bash\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-bash\">Changed current directory to C:/Users/nguye/AppData/Roaming/Composer\r\nUsing version ^2.0 <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span> laravel/installer\r\n./composer.json has been updated\r\nLoading composer repositories with package information\r\nUpdating dependencies <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>including require-dev<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\nPackage operations: 1 install, 0 updates, 0 removals\r\n  - Installing laravel/installer <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>v2.0.1<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>: Loading from cache\r\nWriting lock <span class=\"token function\">file</span>\r\nGenerating autoload files</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau khi c&agrave;i đặt, sử dụng c&acirc;u lệnh&nbsp;<code>laravel new</code>&nbsp;để c&agrave;i đặt một project Laravel trong thư mục bạn muốn (<code>D:\\xampp\\htdocs</code> chẳng hạn). V&iacute; dụ,&nbsp;<code>laravel new blog</code>&nbsp;sẽ tạo một thư mục t&ecirc;n l&agrave;&nbsp;<code>blog</code>&nbsp;v&agrave; c&oacute; chứa to&agrave;n bộ m&atilde; nguồn đầy đủ của Laravel c&ugrave;ng với tất cả c&aacute;c dependencies cần thiết. Phương ph&aacute;p n&agrave;y thực hiện c&agrave;i đặt&nbsp; rất nhanh</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-bash\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">cd</span> D:\\xampp\\htdocs\r\nlaravel new blog</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1cgo2tbr63\">C&aacute;ch 2:&nbsp;Sử dụng Composer Create-Project</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Một c&aacute;ch kh&aacute;c, bạn c&oacute; thể sử dụng Composer <code>create-project</code> tr&ecirc;n terminal:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">composer create-project --prefer-dist laravel/laravel blog</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1cgo2tbr64\">C&aacute;ch 3: C&agrave;i đặt thủ c&ocirc;ng</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Bạn clone project laravel tr&ecirc;n github tại địa chỉ&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/laravel/laravel\">https://github.com/laravel/laravel</a>&nbsp;sau đ&oacute; tại thư mục gốc của project chạy lệnh terminal sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-bash\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-bash\">composer <span class=\"token function\">install</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1cgo2tbr65\">Local Development Server - Cấu h&igrave;nh m&ocirc;i trường ph&aacute;t triển</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Để chạy được website bạn chắc chắn m&igrave;nh đ&atilde; c&agrave;i đặt php hoặc web server như XAMPP, WAMP, ...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Chạy project bằng php: <code>php artisan serve</code></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mở tr&igrave;nh duyệt web nhập địa chỉ: <a href=\"http://localhost:8000\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">http://localhost:8000</a>, nếu muốn chạy port kh&aacute;c bạn c&oacute; thể chạy lệnh: <code>php artisan serve --port=81</code> .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh bạn c&agrave;i đặt xampp l&agrave;m web server th&igrave; bạn c&oacute; thể tham khảo b&agrave;i viết&nbsp;<a href=\"/posts/cau-hinh-virtual-domain-ten-mien-ao-trong-xampp\" title=\"Cấu hình virtual domain (tên miền ảo) trong XAMPP\">Cấu h&igrave;nh virtual domain (t&ecirc;n miền ảo) trong XAMPP</a></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cgo2tbr66\">Cấu h&igrave;nh laravel</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1cgo2tbr67\">Quyền hạn thư mục</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Bạn phải chắc chắn rằng 2 thư mục storage v&agrave;&nbsp;bootstrap/cache phải c&oacute; quyền ghi bởi web server (nginx, apache,...)&nbsp;nếu kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave; Laravel sẽ kh&ocirc;ng chạy được. Tr&ecirc;n windows th&ocirc;ng thường k cần phải cấu h&igrave;nh g&igrave;, c&ograve;n tr&ecirc;n linux, macOS chạy lệnh sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-bash\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># Chỉ định nginx sở hữu website, nếu đang ở tr&ecirc;n vps linux</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">chown</span> -R nginx:nginx /home/chungnguyenblog\r\n<span class=\"token comment\"># Thiết lập quyền ghi cho thư mục</span>\r\n<span class=\"token function\">chmod</span> -R 777 storage/ bootstrap/cache/\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu bạn d&ugrave;ng hosting kh&ocirc;ng chạy được lệnh th&ocirc;ng qua ssh th&igrave; bạn h&atilde;y d&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c ftp client như File Zilla&nbsp;&rArr; Click chuột phải v&agrave;o folder&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">&rArr; File Permissions...&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">&rArr; Numberic Value 777&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">&rArr; Check v&agrave;o &ocirc; Recurse into subdirectories&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">&rArr; OK&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">&rArr; Xong.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1cgo2tbr68\">Application Key</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu bạn c&agrave;i laravel theo c&aacute;ch 1 v&agrave; c&aacute;ch 2 như ở tr&ecirc;n th&igrave;&nbsp;<strong>Application Key</strong> mặc định được tạo, nếu l&agrave;m thủ c&ocirc;ng bạn phải đổi t&ecirc;n hoặc copy file <code>.env.example</code> th&agrave;nh <code>.env</code>, sau đ&oacute; chạy lệnh terminal sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-bash\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-bash\">php artisan key:generate</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu <strong>application key</strong> kh&ocirc;ng được thiết lập, c&aacute;c user sessions v&agrave; c&aacute;c dữ liệu m&atilde; ho&aacute; kh&aacute;c sẽ <strong>kh&ocirc;ng được bảo mật an to&agrave;n!</strong>. V&agrave; project sẽ b&aacute;o lỗi kh&ocirc;ng chạy được.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quyền hạn thư mục v&agrave;&nbsp;Application Key kh&ocirc;ng được cấu h&igrave;nh đầy đủ th&igrave; 99% project sẽ b&aacute;o lỗi khi đưa l&ecirc;n vps - hosting v&agrave; khiến những bạn newbie rất bối rối kh&ocirc;ng biết c&aacute;ch xử l&yacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cgo3bk348\">Tổng kết</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr&ecirc;n đ&acirc;y <a href=\"/posts/cai-dat-laravel\" title=\"chungnguyenblog \">chungnguyenblog</a> giới thiệu cho bạn c&aacute;ch để start 1 website laravel đơn giản, nhanh, hiệu quả =))</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu gặp kh&oacute; khăn g&igrave; trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh c&agrave;i đặt, h&atilde;y để lại comment dưới đ&acirc;y nh&eacute;!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/cai-dat-laravel', 1, 1, 'Cài đặt Laravel', 'Laravel framework c&oacute; một v&agrave;i y&ecirc;u cầu về hệ thống. Hiển nhi&ecirc;n l&agrave; c&aacute;c y&ecirc;u cầu n&agrave;y đ&atilde; được đầy đủ trong&nbsp;Laravel Homestead, v&igrave; thế Laravel rất khuyến kh&iacute;ch c&aacute;c bạn sử dụng H', 'cai-dat-laravel', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Laravel framework c&oacute; một v&agrave;i y&ecirc;u cầu về hệ thống. Hiển nhi&ecirc;n l&agrave; c&aacute;c y&ecirc;u cầu n&agrave;y đ&atilde; được đầy đủ trong&nbsp;Laravel Homestead, v&igrave; thế Laravel rất khuyến kh&iacute;ch c&aacute;c bạn sử dụng Ho'),
(34, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:21:39', '2019-08-11 14:27:14', 1, 'Laravel Error: In UrlGenerator.php line 111', 'laravel-error-in-urlgeneratorphp-line-111', '<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n              <p>Mô tả</p>\r\n<p>Khi chạy lệnh artisan: <code>php artisan config:cache</code>,&nbsp;<code>php artisan route:list</code> hoặc <code>php artisan route:cache</code> sẽ gặp thông báo lỗi như sau</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-markup\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-markup\">In UrlGenerator.php line 111:\r\n\r\nArgument 2 passed to Illuminate\\Routing\\UrlGenerator::__construct() must be an instance of Illuminate\\Http\\Request, null given, called in \\vendor\\laravel\\framework\\src\\Illuminate\\Routing\\RoutingServiceProvider.php on line 61</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Nguyên nhân:</p>\r\n<p>Do trong config file có chứa các hàm liên quan đến xử lý url (generate) như asset, url</p>\r\n<p>⇒ Xóa chúng đi và thay bằng <code>env</code>, <code>config</code> helper function</p>\r\n            </div>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-error-in-urlgenerator-php-line-111', 1, 1, 'Laravel Error: In UrlGenerator.php line 111', 'M&ocirc; tả', 'laravel-error-in-urlgeneratorphp-line-111', '[\"\"]', 1, 'M&ocirc; tả');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(35, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:21:41', '2019-08-11 14:29:23', 1, '[Laravel Sitemap] Tạo sitemap - sơ đồ web cho website laravel', 'laravel-sitemap-tao-sitemap-so-do-web-cho-website-laravel', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cftv8h03ml\">1. Sitemap l&agrave; g&igrave;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #1b1b1b; font-family: Roboto, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Helvetica Neue, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: -0.048px;\">Sitemap hay c&ograve;n gọi l&agrave; sơ đồ trang web theo đ&uacute;ng như t&ecirc;n gọi sitemap giống như l&agrave; một bản đồ thu nhỏ tập hợp c&aacute;c đường dẫn URL của một trang web, hỗ trợ điều hướng h&agrave;nh vi của người d&ugrave;ng tr&ecirc;n website đồng thời c&ograve;n gi&uacute;p cho con <code>Bot của Google</code> dễ thu thập dữ liệu v&agrave; đ&aacute;nh chỉ mục website của bạn.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"[Laravel Sitemap] Tạo sitemap - sơ đồ web cho website laravel\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/sitemap/sitemap1.png?_t=1528937606\" title=\"[Laravel Sitemap] Tạo sitemap - sơ đồ web cho website laravel\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu bạn đang l&agrave;m <strong>SEO</strong> hay đang t&igrave;m hiểu về <strong>SEO</strong> th&igrave; <strong>Sitemap</strong> l&agrave; một yếu tố kh&ocirc;ng thể bỏ qua cho bất kỳ 1 website n&agrave;o. Trước khi đi v&agrave;o tạo sitemap bạn phải hiểu r&otilde; được bản chất đặc điểm của n&oacute; l&agrave; g&igrave;, lợi &iacute;ch m&agrave; n&oacute; mang lại đối với qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh SEO như thế n&agrave;o?</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cftv8h03mm\">2. T&aacute;c dụng của sitemap đối với SEO</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Tạo sitemap l&agrave; việc quan trọng đối với bất kỳ 1 website n&agrave;o, tuy n&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng ảnh hưởng trưc tiếp đến thứ hạng của website nhưng n&oacute; sẽ gi&uacute;p điều hướng h&agrave;nh vi người d&ugrave;ng một c&aacute;ch tốt nhất, th&acirc;n thiện với c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng cụ t&igrave;m kiếm:<img alt=\"Tạo sitemap - sơ đồ web cho website laravel\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/sitemap/sitemap2.jpg?_t=1528937908\" title=\"Tạo sitemap - sơ đồ web cho website laravel\" /><br />\r\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-1450596627252330\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; background-color: transparent;\"><ins style=\"display:inline-table;border:none;height:165px;margin:0;padding:0;position:relative;visibility:visible;width:658px;background-color:transparent;\"><ins style=\"display:block;border:none;height:165px;margin:0;padding:0;position:relative;visibility:visible;width:658px;background-color:transparent;\">Sitemap gi&uacute;p khai b&aacute;o cho c&aacute;c c&ocirc;ng cụ t&igrave;m kiếm (Google, Yahoo, Bing, Coccoc, v..v) biết được <strong>sơ đồ c&aacute;c li&ecirc;n kết trong website</strong> gi&uacute;p cho việc <strong>lập chỉ mục</strong> diễn ra một c&aacute;ch dễ d&agrave;ng v&agrave; ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c</ins></ins></ins></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong>Cải thiện tốc độ index cho website</strong>: Việc tạo 1 sitemap sẽ gi&uacute;p bạn gia tăng tốc độ index một c&aacute;ch nhanh ch&oacute;ng c&aacute;c trang tr&ecirc;n site</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Ph&aacute;t hiện được c&aacute;c lỗi li&ecirc;n kết (404, 500 ...)</strong>: <strong>Google bot</strong> gặp phải lỗi kh&ocirc;ng thu thập th&ocirc;ng tin cũng l&agrave; chuyện kh&ocirc;ng thể tr&aacute;nh khỏi. Khi tạo sitemap bạn sẽ kiểm so&aacute;t c&aacute;c li&ecirc;n kết lỗi một c&aacute;ch dễ d&agrave;ng hơn</li>\r\n	<li>C&aacute;c nh&agrave; quản trị website c&oacute; thể quản l&yacute; hệ thống của m&igrave;nh một c&aacute;ch tổng quan ph&acirc;n cấp nội dung tr&ecirc;n trang một c&aacute;ch ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Site map c&oacute; 2 loại, loại thứ nhất l&agrave; xml, loại thứ 2 l&agrave; html. Trong b&agrave;i n&agrave;y t&ocirc;i sẽ giới thiệu cho bạn c&aacute;ch tạo file sitemap bằng xml:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>loc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n        https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/tao-sitemap-so-do-web-cho-website-laravel\r\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>loc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>priority</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>priority</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>lastmod</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>2018-06-14T08:57:48+07:00<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>lastmod</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>changefreq</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>daily<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>changefreq</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>loc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n        https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-nginx-loai-bo-index-php-tren-url-toi-uu-seo\r\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>loc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>priority</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>priority</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>lastmod</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>2018-06-08T21:16:46+07:00<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>lastmod</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>changefreq</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>daily<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>changefreq</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\r\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cftv8h03mn\">3. Tạo sitemap file bằng code laravel</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Thực ra tạo sitemap file c&oacute; nhiều website tr&ecirc;n mạng hỗ trợ bạn l&agrave;m việc n&agrave;y, nhưng điểm bất lợi của n&oacute; l&agrave; n&oacute; giới hạn độ lớn website của bạn (tức l&agrave; chỉ được tối đa bao nhi&ecirc;u link tr&ecirc;n b&agrave;i viết), hay l&agrave; mỗi khi website của bạn c&oacute; b&agrave;i mới n&oacute; sẽ kh&ocirc;ng tự động cập nhập v&agrave;o sitemap, sẽ rất bất tiện khi lần n&agrave;o cũng sẽ phải l&ecirc;n website đ&oacute; rồi tạo sitemap xong download về rồi lại upload l&ecirc;n host của m&igrave;nh đ&uacute;ng kh&ocirc;ng n&agrave;o.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Một sitemap tự động bằng code với bất kỳ đường link n&agrave;o bạn muốn, v&agrave; bạn c&oacute; thể đặt lịch cho n&oacute; chạy hằng ng&agrave;y ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n tự động.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong b&agrave;i n&agrave;y t&ocirc;i sẽ d&ugrave;ng <strong>thư viện laravel-sitemap</strong> của t&aacute;c giả RoumenDamianoff c&aacute;c bạn c&oacute; thể tham khảo tại đậy <a href=\"https://github.com/RoumenDamianoff/laravel-sitemap\">https://github.com/RoumenDamianoff/laravel-sitemap</a> .</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1cftv8h03mo\">A. C&agrave;i đặt thư viện</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"text-danger\">Lưu &yacute;:&nbsp;Laravel 5.5 trở l&ecirc;n kh&ocirc;ng phải l&agrave;m bước 2 v&agrave; 3</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Bạn mở terminal l&ecirc;n chạy lệnh sau:&nbsp;<code>composer require roumen/sitemap</code>&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Add v&agrave;o service Provider d&ograve;ng sau: <code>Roumen\\Sitemap\\SitemapServiceProvider::class,</code></li>\r\n	<li>Chạy lệnh <code>php artisan vendor:publish --provider=&quot;Roumen\\Sitemap\\SitemapServiceProvider&quot;</code> để pubic những file config.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>Như vậy ch&uacute;ng ra đ&atilde; c&agrave;i đặt xong thư viện, tiếp theo ch&uacute;ng ta sẽ tạo sitemap cho website. C&oacute; 2 c&aacute;ch để tạo ra laravel sitemap của bạn t&ugrave;y v&agrave;o độ lớn của website v&agrave; điều kiện bạn c&oacute; sở hữu VPS ri&ecirc;ng hay kh&ocirc;ng?</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1cftv8h03mp\">B1. Tạo Laravel sitemap bằng c&aacute;ch xuất ra file xml</h3>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"font-weight-bold text-danger text-uppercase\">Điều kiện: Sở hữu VPS hoặc hosting c&oacute; thể chạy được cronjob để chạy tự động hoặc chạy thủ c&ocirc;ng dưới local rồi upload file xml l&ecirc;n hosting</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Đầu ti&ecirc;n bạn chạy lệnh sau trong terminal: <code>php artisan make:command CreateSiteMap --command=sitemap:create</code> lệnh n&agrave;y sẽ tạo ra 1 file l&agrave; <code>CreateSiteMap.php</code> trong thư mục <code>app/console/commands</code> c&oacute; nội dung như sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Console<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Commands</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Console<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Command</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">CreateSiteMap</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Command</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * The name and signature of the console command.\r\n     *\r\n     * @var string\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$signature</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;sitemap:create&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * The console command description.\r\n     *\r\n     * @var string\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$description</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Command description&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Create a new command instance.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">__construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">parent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">__construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Execute the console command.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return mixed\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">handle</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">//</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>H&agrave;m handle sẽ được viết lại thư sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">handle</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$sitemap</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> \\<span class=\"token package\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">make</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;sitemap&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// add home pages mặc định</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$sitemap</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\\<span class=\"token package\">URL</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">to</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;/&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> \\<span class=\"token package\">Carbon</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">now</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;daily&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// add b&agrave;i viết</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$posts</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> \\<span class=\"token package\">DB</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;blog_posts&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">orderBy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;created_at&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;desc&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">foreach</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$posts</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$post</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">//$sitemap-&gt;add(url, thời gian, độ ưu ti&ecirc;n, thời gian quay lại)</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$sitemap</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">route</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;post.show&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$post</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">slug</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$post</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">updated_at</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;daily&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// lưu file v&agrave; ph&acirc;n quyền</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$sitemap</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">store</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;xml&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;sitemap&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\\<span class=\"token package\">File</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">exists</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">public_path</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;sitemap.xml&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token function\">chmod</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">public_path</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;sitemap.xml&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0777</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong thư mục của project của bạn chạy lệnh sau: <code>php artisan sitemap:create</code>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>G&otilde; tr&ecirc;n tr&igrave;nh duyệt <code>yourdomain.com/sitemap.xml</code> nếu thấy xuất hiện thế n&agrave;y tức l&agrave; bạn đ&atilde; th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Tạo sitemap - sơ đồ web cho website laravel\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/sitemap/sitemap3.png\" title=\"Tạo sitemap - sơ đồ web cho website laravel\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Như vậy l&agrave; xong c&aacute;ch tạo sitemap bằng code hoằn to&agrave;n tự động, b&acirc;y giờ bạn c&oacute; thể config cronjob tr&ecirc;n server của bạn để n&oacute; chạy hằng ng&agrave;y hoặc hằng tuần nếu bạn muốn.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Config&nbsp;cronjob chạy tự động tr&ecirc;n server</h4>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>bật editor cronjob tr&ecirc;n vps:&nbsp;<code>EDITOR=nano crontab -e</code></li>\r\n	<li>add cronjob (thay đường dẫn đến file artisan nha):&nbsp;<code>* * * * * php /home/chungnguyen.xyz/public_html/artisan schedule:run &gt;&gt; /dev/null 2&gt;&amp;1</code></li>\r\n	<li>Trong file: <code>\\app\\Console\\Kernel.php</code> function&nbsp;<code>schedule()</code> th&ecirc;m lịch chạy command</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n	<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Console</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Console<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Scheduling<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Schedule</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Foundation<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Console<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Kernel</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> ConsoleKernel<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Kernel</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ConsoleKernel</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * The Artisan commands provided by your application.\r\n     *\r\n     * @var array\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$commands</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n        Commands\\<span class=\"token package\">CreateSiteMap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">//</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Define the application&#39;s command schedule.\r\n     *\r\n     * @param  \\Illuminate\\Console\\Scheduling\\Schedule  $schedule\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">schedule</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Schedule <span class=\"token variable\">$schedule</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$schedule</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">command</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;sitemap:create&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">dailyAt</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;1:00&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Register the commands for the application.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">commands</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">load</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token constant\">__DIR__</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;/Commands&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">require</span> <span class=\"token function\">base_path</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;routes/console.php&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n	<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n	<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n	</li>\r\n	<li>Sitemap sẽ được tạo tự động mỗi ng&agrave;y v&agrave;o l&uacute;c 1h s&aacute;ng, bạn ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n c&oacute; thể t&ugrave;y &yacute; chỉnh dailyAt th&agrave;nh thời gian bạn mong muốn, nếu vậy <a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/master/scheduling#schedule-frequency-options\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"xem thêm tài liệu ở đây\">xem th&ecirc;m t&agrave;i liệu ở đ&acirc;y</a>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"mcetoc_1cftvng4jnq\">B2. Tạo Laravel sitemap trực tiếp tr&ecirc;n url</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong <code>...\\routes\\web.php</code> th&ecirc;m&nbsp;Route::get(&#39;sitemap&#39;, &#39;HomeController@sitemap&#39;);</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong <code>...\\app\\Http\\Controllers\\HomeController.php</code> function <code>sitemap()</code></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">sitemap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$sitemap</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">app</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">make</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;sitemap&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Cache kết quả 60 ph&uacute;t</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$sitemap</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">setCache</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;chungnguyenblog.sitemap.index&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">60</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token variable\">$sitemap</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">isCached</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$sitemap</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;/&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> \\<span class=\"token package\">Carbon</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">now</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;daily&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// add b&agrave;i viết</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$posts</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> \\<span class=\"token package\">DB</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;blog_posts&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">orderBy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;created_at&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;desc&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">foreach</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$posts</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$post</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token comment\">//$sitemap-&gt;add(url, thời gian, độ ưu ti&ecirc;n, thời gian quay lại)</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$sitemap</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">route</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;post.show&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$post</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">slug</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$post</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">updated_at</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;daily&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// show your sitemap (options: &#39;xml&#39; (default), &#39;html&#39;, &#39;txt&#39;, &#39;ror-rss&#39;, &#39;ror-rdf&#39;)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$sitemap</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;xml&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>G&otilde; tr&ecirc;n tr&igrave;nh duyệt <code>yourdomain.com/sitemap</code>&nbsp;nếu thấy xuất hiện thế n&agrave;y tức l&agrave; bạn đ&atilde; th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/tao-sitemap-so-do-web-cho-website-laravel', 1, 1, '[Laravel Sitemap] Tạo sitemap - sơ đồ web cho website laravel', 'Sitemap hay c&ograve;n gọi l&agrave; sơ đồ trang web theo đ&uacute;ng như t&ecirc;n gọi sitemap giống như l&agrave; một bản đồ thu nhỏ tập hợp c&aacute;c đường dẫn URL của một trang web, hỗ trợ điều hướng h&agrave;nh vi của người d&ugrave;ng tr&ecirc;n we', 'laravel-sitemap-tao-sitemap-so-do-web-cho-website-laravel', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Sitemap hay c&ograve;n gọi l&agrave; sơ đồ trang web theo đ&uacute;ng như t&ecirc;n gọi sitemap giống như l&agrave; một bản đồ thu nhỏ tập hợp c&aacute;c đường dẫn URL của một trang web, hỗ trợ điều hướng h&agrave;nh vi của người d&ugrave;ng tr&ecirc;n web'),
(36, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:21:44', '2019-08-11 14:30:29', 1, 'Laravel Nginx loại bỏ /index.php/ trên URL tối ưu SEO', 'laravel-nginx-loai-bo-indexphp-tren-url-toi-uu-seo', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<h2 id=\"Vấn_đề\">Vấn đề</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu web site của bạn đang chạy Laravel tr&ecirc;n VPS th&igrave; c&aacute;c bạn biết Laravel điều hướng to&agrave;n bộ request ở file public/index.php như vậy tr&ecirc;n thực tế website sẽ c&oacute; index.php trong URL. V&iacute; dụ:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/index.php\">https://chungnguyen.xyz/index.php</a></li>\r\n	<li><a href=\"/index.php/posts/kich-hoat-office-professional-2016-don-gian\">https://chungnguyen.xyz/index.php/posts/kich-hoat-office-professional-2016-don-gian</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Điều n&agrave;y cũng chẳng c&oacute; g&igrave; quan trọng, nếu như&nbsp;Google kh&ocirc;ng lập chỉ mục phi&ecirc;n bản index.php&nbsp; những URL n&agrave;y lại, v&agrave; tất nhi&ecirc;n ảnh hưởng đến SEO website</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/image/posts/vps/laravel-nginx-remove-index-php-0.png?_t=1528466087\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"Giải_quyết\">Giải quyết</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong block server của file .conf (/etc/nginx/conf.d/chungnguyen.xyz.conf vps của Chung Nguyễn Blog) th&ecirc;m đoạn config sau v&agrave;o.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">server {\r\n    # Nginx conf ...\r\n\r\n    rewrite ^/index.php/(.*) /$1  permanent;\r\n    if ($request_uri ~* &quot;^(.*/)index\\.php$&quot;) {\r\n        return 301 $1;\r\n    }\r\n\r\n\r\n    # Nginx conf ...\r\n\r\n}</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/image/posts/vps/laravel-nginx-remove-index-php.png?_t=1528467349\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-nginx-loai-bo-index-php-tren-url-toi-uu-seo', 1, 1, 'Laravel Nginx loại bỏ /index.php/ trên URL tối ưu SEO', 'Nếu web site của bạn đang chạy Laravel tr&ecirc;n VPS th&igrave; c&aacute;c bạn biết Laravel điều hướng to&agrave;n bộ request ở file public/index.php như vậy tr&ecirc;n thực tế website sẽ c&oacute; index.php trong URL. V&iacute; dụ:', 'laravel-nginx-loai-bo-indexphp-tren-url-toi-uu-seo', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Nếu web site của bạn đang chạy Laravel tr&ecirc;n VPS th&igrave; c&aacute;c bạn biết Laravel điều hướng to&agrave;n bộ request ở file public/index.php như vậy tr&ecirc;n thực tế website sẽ c&oacute; index.php trong URL. V&iacute; dụ:');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(37, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:21:45', '2019-08-11 14:31:19', 1, '20 mẹo khi làm việc với Laravel Eloquent', '20-meo-khi-lam-viec-voi-laravel-eloquent', '<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n              <h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cbo56s0b0\">1. Increments và Decrements</h2>\r\n<p>Thay vì:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$article</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Article<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$article_id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$article</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">read_count</span><span class=\"token operator\">++</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$article</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">save</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Bạn có thể rút gọn thành như thế này:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$article</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Article<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$article_id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$article</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">increment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'read_count\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Như thế này cũng ok:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">Article<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$article_id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">increment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'read_count\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nArticle<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$article_id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">increment</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'read_count\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// tăng +10</span>\r\nProduct<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$produce_id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">decrement</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'stock\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// giảm -1</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<hr>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cbo56s0b1\">2. Hàm X hoặc Y</h2>\r\n<p><strong>Eloquent</strong> có khá một vài hàm kết hợp hai hàm lại với nhau, kiểu như “vui lòng thực hiện X còn không thì thực hiện Y”. Điều này làm cho code rất clear và cool, các bạn hãy cố gắng sử dụng nếu có thể.</p>\r\n<p>Ví dụ 1&nbsp;–&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>findOrFail()</code>:</p>\r\n<p>Thay vì viết như thế này:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$user</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> User<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token variable\">$user</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> abort <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">404</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Hãy thử viết lại như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$user</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> User<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">findOrFail</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Ví dụ 2&nbsp;–&nbsp;<code>firstOrCreate()</code>:</p>\r\n<p>Thay vì viết như thế này:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$user</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> User<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">where</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'email\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$email</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">first</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token variable\">$user</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  User<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'email\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$email</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Chỉ cần viết như thế này:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$user</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> User<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">firstOrCreate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'email\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$email</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<hr>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cbo56s0b2\">3. Model boot() method</h2>\r\n<p>Trong Eloquent có 1 nơi huyền diệu (magical place) được gọi là boot(), ở đó bạn có thể ghi đè lên các hành vi mặc định (default behavior):</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">User</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Model</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">boot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">parent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">boot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">updating</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$model</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token comment\">// do some logging</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token comment\">// override some property like $model-&gt;something = transform($something);</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Có lẽ một trong những ví dụ phổ biến nhất là thiết lập một số giá trị trường tại thời điểm tạo đối tượng (<span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">model object)</span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">. Giả sử bạn muốn tạo trường UUID tại thời điểm model được tạo.</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">boot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">parent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">boot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n  self<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">creating</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$model</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$model</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">uuid</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>string<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>Uuid<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">generate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// trường uuid được sinh tự động</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<hr>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cbo56s0b3\">4. Relationship with conditions and ordering</h2>\r\n<p>Mối quan hệ với điều kiện và sắp xếp.</p>\r\n<p>Đây là một cách điển hình để xác định mối quan hệ:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// liên kết với bảng users</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">users</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">hasMany</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'App\\User\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>    \r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Nhưng bạn có biết rằng vào thời điểm này, chúng ta đã có thể thêm where hoặc orderBy?<br>Ví dụ, nếu bạn muốn có mối quan hệ cụ thể cho một số loại người dùng, và cũng được sắp xếp theo email, bạn có thể viết lại như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">approvedUsers</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// liên kết với bảng users, user đó phải được approved và sắp xếp các kết quả có được theo email</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">hasMany</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'App\\User\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">where</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'approved\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">orderBy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'email\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<hr>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cbo56s0b4\">5. Model properties: timestamps, appends etc.</h2>\r\n<p>Có một vài \"tham số (<span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">parameters)</span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">\" của một mô hình Eloquent, dưới dạng các thuộc tính của lớp đó. Các kiểu phổ biến nhất có lẽ là:</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">User</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Model</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'users\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$fillable</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'email\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'password\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// trường nào có thể fill với User::create()</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$dates</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'created_at\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'deleted_at\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// trường nào sẽ là Carbon-ized</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$appends</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'field1\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'field2\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// giá trị bổ sung được trả về trong JSON</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Chờ chút, có nhiều hơn bạn nghĩ:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$primaryKey</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'uuid\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// xác định khóa chính cho bảng, mặc định là id</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$incrementing</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// bỏ tính năng increment</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$perPage</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">25</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// mặc định phân trang là 15, bạn có thể tăng giảm tùy ý</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token constant\">CREATED_AT</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'created_at\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token constant\">UPDATED_AT</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'updated_at\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// mặc định created_at, updated_at có thể thay bằng ngay_tao, ngay_cap_nhat</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$timestamps</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// không sử dụng timestamp</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Và có nhiều hơn nữa, mình đã liệt kê những điều thú vị nhất, để biết thêm hãy kiểm tra <a title=\"abstract Model class\" href=\"https://github.com/laravel/framework/blob/5.6/src/Illuminate/Database/Eloquent/Model.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">code của lớp mô hình trừu tượng</a> mặc định và kiểm tra tất cả các Traits được sử dụng (HasAttributes, HasEvents, HasGlobalScopes, HasRelationships, HasTimestamps ...).</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cbo56s0b5\">6. Find multiple entries - tìm nhiều entries</h2>\r\n<p>Mọi người đều biết phương thức <code>find()</code>, đúng không?</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$user</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> User<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Mình khá ngạc nhiên khi ít người biết rằng nó có thể chấp nhận nhiều ID như một mảng:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$users</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> User<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<hr>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cbo56s0b6\">7. WhereX</h2>\r\n<p>Có một cách tao nhã hơn để làm điều này:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$users</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> User<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">where</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'approved\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>thành điều này:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$users</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> User<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">whereApproved</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> </code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Vâng, bạn có thể thay đổi tên của bất kỳ trường nào và thêm nó vào như một hậu tố \"where\" và nó sẽ hoạt động bằng ma thuật. Ví dụ: status -&gt; whereStatus, user_id -&gt; whereUserId</p>\r\n<p>Ngoài ra, có một số phương pháp được xác định trước trong Eloquent, liên quan đến ngày / giờ:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">User<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">whereDate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'created_at\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Y-m-d\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nUser<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">whereDay</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'created_at\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'d\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nUser<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">whereMonth</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'created_at\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'m\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nUser<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">whereYear</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'created_at\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Y\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<hr>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cbo56s0b7\">8. Order by relationship</h2>\r\n<p>Một \"mẹo nhỏ\" phức tạp hơn một chút. Điều gì sẽ xảy ra nếu bạn có 1 chủ đề (topic) trên diễn đàn nhưng muốn sắp xếp chúng theo bài đăng mới nhất? Yêu cầu khá phổ biến trong các diễn đàn với các chủ đề cập nhật mới nhất ở trên cùng, phải không?</p>\r\n<p>Đầu tiên, mô tả mối quan hệ riêng biệt cho bài đăng mới nhất về chủ đề:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">latestPost</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">hasOne</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\\<span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Post</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">latest</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Và sau đó, trong controller, chúng ta có thể thử viết như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$users</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Topic<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">with</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'latestPost\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">sortByDesc</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'latestPost.created_at\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<hr>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cbo56s0b8\">9. Eloquent::when() – no more if-else’s</h2>\r\n<p>Nhiều người trong chúng ta viết các truy vấn có điều kiện với \"if-else\",&nbsp;trông giống như thế này:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// nếu lọc bởi likes</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'filter_by\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'likes\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$query</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">where</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'likes\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'&gt;\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'likes_amount\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// nếu lọc bởi date</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'filter_by\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'date\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$query</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">orderBy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'created_at\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'ordering_rule\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'desc\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Nhưng có một cách tốt hơn - khi sử dụng&nbsp;when():</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$query</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Author<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">query</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$query</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">when</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'filter_by\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'likes\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$q</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$q</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">where</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'likes\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'&gt;\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'likes_amount\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$query</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">when</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'filter_by\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'date\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$q</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$q</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">orderBy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'created_at\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'ordering_rule\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'desc\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Có thể trông không ngắn hơn hoặc thanh lịch hơn, nhưng mạnh nhất ở đây là khi truyền các tham số động, câu query sẽ trở nên rất gọn gàng:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$query</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> User<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">query</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// thay vì phải viết nhiều if, else thì chỉ cần 1</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$query</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">when</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token function\">request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'role\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$q</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$role</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> \r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$q</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">where</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'role_id\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$role</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$authors</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$query</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<hr>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cbo56s0b9\">10. BelongsTo Default Models</h2>\r\n<p>Giả sử bạn có <code>Post</code> belonging to <code>Author</code> và trong code trong file Blade như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$post</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">author</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">name</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Nhưng nếu tác giả bị xóa hoặc không được đặt vì lý do nào đó thì sao? Bạn sẽ nhận được một lỗi, một cái gì đó giống như “property of non-object”.</p>\r\n<p>Tất nhiên, bạn có thể ngăn chặn nó như thế này:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$post</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">author</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">name</span> <span class=\"token operator\">?</span><span class=\"token operator\">?</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'\'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Nhưng bạn có thể làm điều đó trên <strong>Eloquent relationship level</strong>:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">author</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">belongsTo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'App\\Author\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">withDefault</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Trong ví dụ, <code>author()</code>&nbsp;relation sẽ trả về đối tượng <code>App\\Author</code>&nbsp;rỗng, nếu không có tác giả nào được đính kèm vào bài viết.</p>\r\n<p>Hơn nữa, chúng ta có thể gán giá trị thuộc tính mặc định cho mô hình mặc định đó.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">author</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">belongsTo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'App\\Author\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">withDefault</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'name\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Guest Author\'</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// tên tác giả mặc định</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<hr>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cbo56s0ba\">11. Order by Mutator</h2>\r\n<p>Hãy tưởng tượng bạn có điều này:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">getFullNameAttribute</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">attributes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'first_name\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\' \'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">attributes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'last_name\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Bây giờ, bạn muốn sắp xếp theo full name ư? Nó sẽ không chạy đâu:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$clients</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Client<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">orderBy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'full_name\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// báo lỗi</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Giải pháp rất đơn giản. Chúng ta cần sắp xếp kết quả sau khi lấy được chúng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$clients</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Client<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">sortBy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'full_name\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// works!</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Lưu ý rằng tên hàm là khác nhau - nó không phải orderBy, nó là sortBy.</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cbo56s0bb\">12. Default ordering in global scope</h2>\r\n<p>Điều gì sẽ xảy ra nếu bạn muốn có <code>User::all()</code> luôn được sắp xếp theo 1 trường nào đó chẳng hạn <em>name</em>? Bạn có thể gán vào global scope. Hãy quay trở lại phương thức boot() lúc nãy:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">boot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">parent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">boot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Order by name ASC</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">static</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">addGlobalScope</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'order\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Builder <span class=\"token variable\">$builder</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$builder</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">orderBy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'asc\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Xem kỹ hơn&nbsp;<a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/5.6/eloquent#query-scopes\">Query Scopes ở đây</a>.</p>\r\n<hr>\r\n<h2 id=\"mcetoc_1cbo56s0bc\">13. Raw query methods</h2>\r\n<p>Đôi khi, chúng ta cần thêm các truy vấn thô vào các câu lệnh Eloquent. May mắn thay, có chức năng cho điều đó.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// whereRaw</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$orders</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token constant\">DB</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/20-meo-khi-lam-viec-voi-laravel-eloquent', 1, 1, '20 mẹo khi làm việc với Laravel Eloquent', 'Thay v&igrave;:', '20-meo-khi-lam-viec-voi-laravel-eloquent', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Thay v&igrave;:');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(42, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:21:57', '2019-08-11 14:33:04', 1, 'Hãy dùng Laravel Mix cho các dự án Laravel', 'hay-dung-laravel-mix-cho-cac-du-an-laravel', '<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n              <p>Khi được hỏi Laravel có gì đặc biệt? từ các nhà phỏng vấn tuyển dụng ắt hẳn nhiều bạn không hề có ý nghĩ đưa ra câu trả lời là: <strong>Laravel Mix</strong></p>\r\n<p>Thường khi nói đến <strong>Laravel Mix</strong> một số bạn newbie sẽ có những comment vui như thế này: \"chưa nghe <strong>Laravel Mix</strong> bao giờ ???\", \"sao không dùng webpack, gulp cho khỏe ?\"... Trong bài viết hôm nay, Chung sẽ mổ xẻ Laravel Mix và hướng dẫn các bạn dùng Laravel trong các dự án Laravel nhé!</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"1._Laravel_Mix_là_gì?\">1. Laravel Mix là gì?</h2>\r\n<p><strong>Laravel Mix</strong> cung cấp một API sạch, linh hoạt để định nghĩa các bước xây dựng webpack cơ bản cho ứng dụng Laravel của bạn. <strong>Laravel Mix</strong> hỗ trợ một số bộ xử lý trước CSS và JavaScript phổ biến.</p>\r\n<p>Nói ngắn gọn là: <strong>Laravel Mix</strong> quản lý tất cả tài nguyên (assets) như img, css, js trong dự án của bạn, đồng thời nó dự trên base là webpack build tất cả các file css, js pre-processors như SCSS, SASS thành css, chuyển ES6 thành ES5 (trình duyệt không hiểu cú pháp ES6).</p><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%; height: auto; clear: none;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-1450596627252330\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; background-color: transparent;\"><ins id=\"aswift_1_expand\" style=\"display: inline-table; border: none; height: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 698px; background-color: transparent;\"><ins id=\"aswift_1_anchor\" style=\"display: block; border: none; height: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 698px; background-color: transparent; overflow: visible; opacity: 1;\"><iframe width=\"698\" height=\"175\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" onload=\"var i=this.id,s=window.google_iframe_oncopy,H=s&amp;&amp;s.handlers,h=H&amp;&amp;H[i],w=this.contentWindow,d;try{d=w.document}catch(e){}if(h&amp;&amp;d&amp;&amp;(!d.body||!d.body.firstChild)){if(h.call){setTimeout(h,0)}else if(h.match){try{h=s.upd(h,i)}catch(e){}w.location.replace(h)}}\" id=\"aswift_1\" name=\"aswift_1\" style=\"left:0;position:absolute;top:0;border:0px;width:698px;height:175px;\"></iframe></ins></ins></ins></div>\r\n<p>Đọc đoạn trên nhiều bạn thắc mắc là mình có cần phải biết webpack hay không?&nbsp;⇒ Không bắt buộc nhé.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"2._Sử_dụng_Laravel_Mix_trong_Laravel_project\">2. Sử dụng Laravel Mix trong Laravel project</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"2.1._Cài_Nodejs_&amp;_NPM\">2.1. Cài Nodejs &amp; NPM</h3>\r\n<p>Vào trang chủ nodejs cài đặt theo hướng dẫn nhé&nbsp;<a href=\"https://nodejs.org/en/download/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://nodejs.org/en/download/</a>&nbsp;quá easy nên mình không viết vào đây.</p>\r\n<p>Sau khi cài xong bạn kiểm tra trên terminal lệnh:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-bash\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-bash\">node -v\r\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> -v</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Có trả về version thì ok nhé</p>\r\n<p>Bạn có thể cài thêm yarn, vì yarn quản lý packages nhanh hơn npm, mình khuyến khích bạn cài thêm cái này:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://yarnpkg.com/lang/en/docs/install/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://yarnpkg.com/lang/en/docs/install/</a>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"2.2._Cài_đặt_các_gói_phụ_thuộc\">2.2. Cài đặt các gói phụ thuộc</h3>\r\n<p>Trong project Laravel mặc định có file package.json, file này định nghĩa các gói cần thiết cơ bản để <strong>Laravel Mix</strong> chạy suôn sẻ. Bạn hãy chạy lệnh sau để cài đặt các gói phụ thuộc: <kbd>npm install</kbd> hoặc <kbd>yarn install</kbd> nếu dùng yarn</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"2.3._Chạy_Laravel_Mix\">2.3. Chạy Laravel Mix</h3>\r\n<p><strong>Laravel Mix</strong> là 1 lớp phủ bên ngoài của webpack nên bạn không cần biết bên trong như thế nào chỉ cần chạy lệnh sau là sẽ auto compiles các file assets theo cài đặt như cài đặt trong file <kbd>webpack.mix.js</kbd> (phần cấu hình compile nói ở dưới)</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-bash\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-bash\">// Chạy trên môi trường dev, local\r\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> run dev\r\n// Chạy khi đưa lên host, deploy app, 2 lệnh này giống nhau\r\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> run prod\r\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> run production\r\n// Chạy khi vừa dev, vừa chỉnh các <span class=\"token function\">file</span> assets\r\n<span class=\"token function\">npm</span> run <span class=\"token function\">watch</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"2.4._Làm_việc_với_các_file_CSS\">2.4. Làm việc với các file CSS</h3>\r\n<h4>+ LESS</h4>\r\n<p>Giả sử bạn có file&nbsp;<kbd>resources/assets/less/app.less</kbd> và muốn build nó thành css bỏ vào thư mục&nbsp;<kbd>public/css/app.css</kbd></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-javascript\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-javascript\">mix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">less</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\'resources/assets/less/app.less\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'public/css\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Giả sử muốn build thêm 1 file&nbsp;<kbd>resources/assets/less/admin.less</kbd> nữa.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-markup\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-markup\">mix.less(\'resources/assets/less/app.less\', \'public/css\')\r\n   .less(\'resources/assets/less/admin.less\', \'public/css\');</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Nếu bạn không muốn output app.less ra app.css mà muốn ra thành style.css thì:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-javascript\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-javascript\">mix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">less</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\'resources/assets/less/app.less\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'public/stylesheets/styles.css\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h4 style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; color: #212529;\">+ SASS, SCSS</h4>\r\n<p>Giả sử bạn có file&nbsp;<kbd>resources/assets/sass/app.scss</kbd> và muốn build nó thành css bỏ vào thư mục&nbsp;<kbd>public/css/app.css</kbd></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-javascript\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-javascript\">mix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sass</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\'resources/assets/sass/app.scss\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'public/css\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Giả sử muốn build thêm 1 file&nbsp;<kbd>resources/assets/sass/admin.scss</kbd> nữa.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-javascript\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-javascript\">mix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sass</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\'resources/assets/sass/app.scss\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'public/css\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sass</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\'resources/assets/sass/admin.scss\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'public/css\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Nếu bạn không muốn output app.scss ra app.css mà muốn ra thành style.css thì:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-javascript\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-javascript\">mix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sass</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\'resources/assets/sass/app.scss\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'public/stylesheets/styles.css\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h4>+&nbsp;Stylus</h4>\r\n<p>Cũng giống như Less, Sass</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-javascript\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-javascript\">mix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">stylus</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\'resources/assets/stylus/app.styl\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'public/css\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h4>+ File CSS thường</h4>\r\n<p>Nếu bạn muốn gộp chục file css thành một file css thì:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-javascript\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-javascript\">mix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">styles</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token string\">\'public/css/vendor/normalize.css\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token string\">\'public/css/vendor/videojs.css\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token operator\">...</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'public/css/all.css\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h4>+ Javascript</h4>\r\n<p><strong>Laravel Mix</strong> có thể compiles</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>file js thường</li>\r\n<li>cú pháp es2015</li>\r\n<li>file vue</li>\r\n<li>modules</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>bằng 1 hàm duy nhất</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-javascript\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-javascript\">mix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">js</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\'resources/assets/js/app.js\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'public/js\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"+_React_JS\">+ React JS</h3>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-javascript\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-javascript\">mix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">react</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\'resources/assets/js/app.jsx\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'public/js\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h4>+ Vanilla JS</h4>\r\n<p>Tương tự như <code>mix.styles()</code>, biên dịch nhiều file JavaScript gộp thành một file nào bằng phương thức <code>scripts()</code>:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-javascript\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-javascript\">mix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">scripts</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token string\">\'public/js/admin.js\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token string\">\'public/js/dashboard.js\'</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'public/js/all.js\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"2.5._Tùy_chỉnh_cấu_hình_Webpack\">2.5. Tùy chỉnh cấu hình Webpack</h3>\r\n<p>Như đã nói ở trên <strong>Laravel Mix</strong> là một lớp phủ bên ngoài webpack và việc biên dịch file vẫn phải chạy trên webpack. Nên hoàn toàn có thể tùy chỉnh cấu hình webpack thông qua file <code>webpack.mix.js</code>. Cái này cần phải có kiến thức về webpack nè&nbsp;??</p>\r\n<h3 id=\"2.6._Sao_chép_tệp_và_thư_mục\">2.6.&nbsp;Sao chép tệp và thư mục</h3>\r\n<p>Giả sử bạn cần copy file <code>node_modules/foo/bar.css</code> ra thư mục <code>public/css/bar.css</code> thì:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-javascript\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-javascript\">mix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">copy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\'node_modules/foo/bar.css\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'public/css/bar.css\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Giả sử bạn cần copy thư mục <code>assets/img</code> ra thư mục <code>public/img</code> thì:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-javascript\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-javascript\">mix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">copyDirectory</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\'assets/img\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'public/img\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"2.7._Quản_lý_phiên_bản/Xóa_cache\">2.7. Quản lý phiên bản/Xóa cache</h3>\r\n<p>Khi các file assets có sự sửa đổi và build lại, nghiễm nhiên nó sẽ không thay đổi ngay với tất cả mọi người, bởi vì trình duyệt đã cache lại. Cho nên <code>version()</code> chính là giải pháp hoàn hảo, ép trình duyệt phải lấy về file mới nhất.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-javascript\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-javascript\">mix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">js</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\'resources/assets/js/app.js\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\'public/js\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p><strong>Laravel Mix</strong> sẽ generate ra một mã hash tại thời điểm chạy, và bạn sẽ không muốn gõ tay cái mã này đâu&nbsp;?? hãy dùng Laravel helper function <code>mix()</code> nhé</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>link rel<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"stylesheet\"</span> href<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"{{ mix(\'/css/app.css\') }}\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Nếu bạn chỉ muốn gắn version khi build production thì:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-javascript\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// chạy npm run prod sẽ generate ra version</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">inProduction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    mix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">version</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"2.8._Tắt_thông_báo\">2.8. Tắt thông báo</h3>\r\n<p>Nếu bạn dùng npm run watch thì mỗi khi file thay đổi, webpack sẽ phát hiện và biên dịch lại, biên dịch xong thì phải báo message done hay fail chứ, nếu bạn chỉnh sửa liên tục sẽ rất phiền. Muốn tắt thì:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-javascript\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// easy</span>\r\nmix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">disableNotifications</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Hãy thả&nbsp;?❤️cho Chung nhé!</p>\r\n            </div>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/hay-dung-laravel-mix-cho-cac-du-an-laravel', 1, 1, 'Hãy dùng Laravel Mix cho các dự án Laravel', 'Khi được hỏi Laravel c&oacute; g&igrave; đặc biệt? từ c&aacute;c nh&agrave; phỏng vấn tuyển dụng ắt hẳn nhiều bạn kh&ocirc;ng hề c&oacute; &yacute; nghĩ đưa ra c&acirc;u trả lời l&agrave;: Laravel Mix', 'hay-dung-laravel-mix-cho-cac-du-an-laravel', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Khi được hỏi Laravel c&oacute; g&igrave; đặc biệt? từ c&aacute;c nh&agrave; phỏng vấn tuyển dụng ắt hẳn nhiều bạn kh&ocirc;ng hề c&oacute; &yacute; nghĩ đưa ra c&acirc;u trả lời l&agrave;: Laravel Mix');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(43, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:21:59', '2019-08-11 14:34:15', 1, 'Laravel 5.7 Email Verification', 'laravel-57-email-verification', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<h2 id=\"1._Giới_thiệu\">1. Giới thiệu</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhiều ứng dụng web y&ecirc;u cầu người d&ugrave;ng x&aacute;c minh địa chỉ email của họ trước khi sử dụng ứng dụng. Thay v&igrave; buộc bạn phải thực hiện lại điều n&agrave;y tr&ecirc;n mỗi ứng dụng, Laravel đ&atilde; cung cấp c&aacute;c phương thức để gửi v&agrave; x&aacute;c minh c&aacute;c y&ecirc;u cầu x&aacute;c minh email một c&aacute;ch thuận tiện hơn.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"2._Tích_hợp_Email_Verification_cho_các_phiên_bản_Laravel_5.7_trở_về_trước\">2. T&iacute;ch hợp&nbsp;Email Verification cho c&aacute;c phi&ecirc;n bản Laravel 5.7 trở về trước</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Đối với c&aacute;c ứng dụng Laravel 5.7 mới chắc chắn đ&atilde; t&iacute;ch hợp sẵn t&iacute;nh năng n&agrave;y, n&ecirc;n b&agrave;i viết n&agrave;y d&ugrave;ng để &aacute;p dụng cho c&aacute;c phi&ecirc;n bản trước t&iacute;ch hợp t&iacute;nh năng v&agrave;o ứng dụng hiện tại.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"2.1._Implements_MustVerifyEmail_vào_User_model\">2.1.&nbsp;Implements&nbsp;MustVerifyEmail v&agrave;o User model</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>File laravel\\app\\User.php cần&nbsp;implements MustVerifyEmail class</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"token package\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Notifications<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Notifiable</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Contracts<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Auth<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>MustVerifyEmail</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Foundation<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Auth<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>User</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> Authenticatable<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">User</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Authenticatable</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">implements</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MustVerifyEmail</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Notifiable</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * The attributes that are mass assignable.\r\n     *\r\n     * @var array\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$fillable</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;name&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;email&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;password&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * The attributes that should be hidden for arrays.\r\n     *\r\n     * @var array\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$hidden</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;password&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;remember_token&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"2.2._Thêm_cột_email_verified_at_vào_bảng_users\">2.2. Th&ecirc;m cột&nbsp;email_verified_at v&agrave;o bảng users</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Chạy lệnh artisan sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">php artisan make:migration add_email_verified_at_to_users --table=users</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Sẽ sinh ra file <code>database\\migrations\\2018_08_23_102246_add_email_verified_at_to_users.php</code> ta sửa lại như sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Support<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Facades<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Schema</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Database<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Schema<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Blueprint</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Database<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Migrations<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Migration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">AddEmailVerifiedAtToUsers</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Migration</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Run the migrations.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">up</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        Schema<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;users&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Blueprint <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">timestamp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;email_verified_at&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">nullable</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Reverse the migrations.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">down</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        Schema<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;users&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Blueprint <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">dropColumn</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;email_verified_at&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Chạy lệnh&nbsp;<code>php artisan migrate</code> để th&ecirc;m cột v&agrave;o bảng</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"2.3._Chỉnh_lại_route\">2.3. Chỉnh lại route</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu bạn sử dụng&nbsp;authentication mặc định của Laravel (<kbd>php artisan make:auth</kbd>) th&igrave; trong file <kbd>routes\\web.php</kbd> của bạn chắc chắn c&oacute; d&ograve;ng sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Auth<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">routes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Bạn chỉnh lại như dưới đ&acirc;y để bật t&iacute;nh năng email&nbsp;verification nh&eacute;:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Auth<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">routes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;verify&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"2.4._Bảo_vệ_routes_bằng_verified_middleware\">2.4. Bảo vệ routes bằng verified middleware</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu bạn muốn trong ứng dụng của bạn, người d&ugrave;ng truy cập v&agrave;o trang profile th&igrave; bắt buộc phải x&aacute;c nhận email rồi mới được v&agrave;o bạn l&agrave;m như sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong file <code>app\\Http\\Kernel.php</code> th&ecirc;m middleware <code>verified</code>:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$routeMiddleware</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;verified&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> \\<span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Auth<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Middleware<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>EnsureEmailIsVerified</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Vậy l&agrave; ngo&agrave;i routes bạn c&oacute; thể bảo vệ routes&nbsp;verified middleware</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;profile&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// Chỉ những người d&ugrave;ng x&aacute;c nhận email rồi mới được v&agrave;o</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">middleware</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;verified&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"2.5._Views\">2.5. Views</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Bạn h&atilde;y chạy lệnh artisan php artisan make:auth một lần nữa nếu chạy rồi. Bạn sẽ thấy file <kbd>resources\\views\\auth\\verify.blade.php</kbd> nh&eacute;, bạn thoải m&aacute;i chỉnh sửa file n&agrave;y theo &yacute; muốn của bạn.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"2.6._VerificationController\">2.6.&nbsp;VerificationController</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Phần quan trọng nhất l&agrave; controller xử l&yacute; email verify. Nếu trong ứng dụng bạn chưa c&oacute; file <kbd>app\\Http\\Controllers\\Auth\\VerificationController.php</kbd> th&igrave; bạn c&oacute; thể tạo bằng tay hoặc chạy lệnh artisan sau nh&eacute;: <kbd>php artisan make:controller Auth/VerificationController</kbd></p>\r\n\r\n<p>File&nbsp;<code>app\\Http\\Controllers\\Auth\\VerificationController.php</code> c&oacute; nội dung như sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Http<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Controllers<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Auth</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Http<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Routing<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Controller</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Foundation<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Auth<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>VerifiesEmails</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">VerificationController</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Controller</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/*\r\n    |--------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n    | Email Verification Controller\r\n    |--------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n    |\r\n    | This controller is responsible for handling email verification for any\r\n    | user that recently registered with the application. Emails may also\r\n    | be resent if the user did not receive the original email message.\r\n    |\r\n    */</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">VerifiesEmails</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Where to redirect users after verification.\r\n     *\r\n     * @var string\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$redirectTo</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;/home&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Create a new controller instance.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">__construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">middleware</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;auth&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">middleware</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;signed&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">only</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;verify&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">middleware</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;throttle:6,1&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">only</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;verify&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;resend&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Bạn c&oacute; thể thấy&nbsp;<code>protected $redirectTo = &#39;/home&#39;;</code> ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; đường dẫn chuyển hướng người d&ugrave;ng sau khi x&aacute;c nhận email. Như vậy bạn c&oacute; thể thay th&agrave;nh đường dẫn bạn muốn chẳng hạn:&nbsp;<code>protected $redirectTo = &#39;/dashboard&#39;;</code> hay&nbsp;<code>protected $redirectTo = &#39;/&#39;;</code></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-5-7-email-verification', 1, 1, 'Laravel 5.7 Email Verification', 'Nhiều ứng dụng web y&ecirc;u cầu người d&ugrave;ng x&aacute;c minh địa chỉ email của họ trước khi sử dụng ứng dụng. Thay v&igrave; buộc bạn phải thực hiện lại điều n&agrave;y tr&ecirc;n mỗi ứng dụng, Laravel đ&atilde; cung cấp c&aacute;c phương thức để gử', 'laravel-57-email-verification', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Nhiều ứng dụng web y&ecirc;u cầu người d&ugrave;ng x&aacute;c minh địa chỉ email của họ trước khi sử dụng ứng dụng. Thay v&igrave; buộc bạn phải thực hiện lại điều n&agrave;y tr&ecirc;n mỗi ứng dụng, Laravel đ&atilde; cung cấp c&aacute;c phương thức để gửi');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(44, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:01', '2019-08-11 14:34:53', 1, 'Pivot tables và mối quan hệ nhiều-nhiều (many-to-many relationship) trong Laravel', 'pivot-tables-va-moi-quan-he-nhieu-nhieu-many-to-many-relationship-trong-laravel', '<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n              <p>Hôm nay chúng ta cùng tìm hiểu về Eloquent trong Laravel với mối quan hệ nhiều - nhiều (many to many relationship). Thoạt đầu, có thể sẽ hơi lạ và khó định nghĩa cụm từ pivot tables nhưng tính năng này rất hữu dụng trong việc build many-to-many relationship với Laravel framework. Pivot tables về cơ bản là một bảng trung gian giữa 2 bảng chính (main tables). Chúng ta sẽ cùng tìm hiểu cụ thể ở ví dụ thực tế dưới đây.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"1._Ví_dụ_thực_tế_về_bảng_Pivot\">1. Ví dụ thực tế về bảng Pivot</h2>\r\n<p>Trên thực tế có rất nhiều ví dụ về mối quan hệ nhiều-nhiều, một người dùng (User) có nhiều vai trò (Role) và một role được gắn bởi nhiều user, một người lái xe (Drive) thì có thể lái nhiều chiếc xe (Car), và một chiếc xe được lái bởi nhiều người, hay như một cửa hàng (Shop) bán nhiều sản phẩm (Product) và một sản phẩm thì được bán ở nhiều cửa hàng... và còn vô vàn những ví dụ nữa.</p>\r\n<p>Mình sẽ lấy ví dụ Shop - Product làm ví dụ trong bài viết này nhé. Chúng ta sẽ phát thảo sơ qua database như thế này:</p>\r\n<p>Bảng: shops</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>– id</li>\r\n<li>– name</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bảng:&nbsp;products</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>– id</li>\r\n<li>– name</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bảng:&nbsp;product_shop</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>– product_id</li>\r\n<li>– shop_id</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Bảng cuối cùng trong danh sách&nbsp;product_shop chính là bảng Pivot. Bảng pivot là bảng nối giữa 2 bảng, đúng như tên gọi \"trục xoay\" của nó.</p>\r\n<p>Vậy bảng Pivot cần phải tuân thủ 1 số nguyên tắc sau đây, các bạn lưu ý khi thiết kế cơ sở dữ liệu (csdl) nhé:</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li>Tên của pivot table bao gồm tên của 2 bảng chính (ở dạng số ít đó là shop và product)</li>\r\n<li>Ngăn cách nhau bởi dấu gạch dưới (underscore product<span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>_</strong></span>shop)</li><div class=\"google-auto-placed ap_container\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%; height: auto; clear: none;\"><ins data-ad-format=\"auto\" class=\"adsbygoogle adsbygoogle-noablate\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-1450596627252330\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\" style=\"display: block; margin: auto; background-color: transparent;\"><ins id=\"aswift_1_expand\" style=\"display: inline-table; border: none; height: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 658px; background-color: transparent;\"><ins id=\"aswift_1_anchor\" style=\"display: block; border: none; height: 0px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; position: relative; visibility: visible; width: 658px; background-color: transparent; overflow: visible; opacity: 1;\"><iframe width=\"658\" height=\"165\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" hspace=\"0\" allowtransparency=\"true\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" onload=\"var i=this.id,s=window.google_iframe_oncopy,H=s&amp;&amp;s.handlers,h=H&amp;&amp;H[i],w=this.contentWindow,d;try{d=w.document}catch(e){}if(h&amp;&amp;d&amp;&amp;(!d.body||!d.body.firstChild)){if(h.call){setTimeout(h,0)}else if(h.match){try{h=s.upd(h,i)}catch(e){}w.location.replace(h)}}\" id=\"aswift_1\" name=\"aswift_1\" style=\"left:0;position:absolute;top:0;border:0px;width:658px;height:165px;\"></iframe></ins></ins></ins></div>\r\n<li>Sắp xếp theo thứ tự bảng chữ cái (alphabetical: p đứng trước s nên phải là product_shop).</li>\r\n<li>Phải chứa 2 cột là khóa ngoại của 2 bảng tham chiếu theo công thức&nbsp;tên bảng tham chiếu số ít + \"_id\" cho nên ta có:&nbsp;product_id và&nbsp;shop_id</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<h2 id=\"2._Tạo_migration\">2. Tạo migration</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"2.1._Tạo_migration_cho_Shop_model\">2.1.&nbsp;Tạo migration cho Shop model</h3>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-markup\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-markup\">php artisan make:model Shop -m</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Chúng ta sẽ có 2 file&nbsp;<code style=\"font-size: 14px;\">app\\Shop.php</code>&nbsp;và&nbsp;<code style=\"font-size: 14px;\">database\\migrations\\2018_08_22_194022_create_shops_table.php</code>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">app\\Shop.php</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">// app\\Shop.php\r\n<span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"token package\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Database<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Eloquent<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Model</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Shop</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Model</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">belongsToMany</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Product<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">database\\migrations\\2018_08_22_194022_create_shops_table.php</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\">// database\\migrations\\2018_08_22_194022_create_shops_table.php\r\n<span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Support<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Facades<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Schema</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Database<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Schema<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Blueprint</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Database<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Migrations<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Migration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">CreateShopsTable</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Migration</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Run the migrations.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">up</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        Schema<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'shops\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Blueprint <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">increments</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'id\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'name\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">timestamps</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Reverse the migrations.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">down</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        Schema<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">dropIfExists</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'shops\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"2.2._Tạo_migration_cho_Product_model\">2.2.&nbsp;Tạo migration cho Product model</h3>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-markup\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-markup\">php artisan make:model Product -m</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Chúng ta sẽ có 2 file <code>app\\Product.php</code> và <code>database\\migrations\\2018_08_22_194151_create_products_table.php</code>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">app\\Product.php</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"