pan class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h2 id=\"3._Thao_tác_với_cơ_sở_dữ_liệu\">3. Thao tác với cơ sở dữ liệu</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"3.1_attach()_-_thêm\">3.1&nbsp;attach() - thêm</h3>\r\n<p>Giả sử Shop của bạn có id là $shopId muốn thêm một sản phẩm có id là $productId chúng ta làm như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Shop<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$shopId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">attach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$productId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Kết quả là trong bảng Pivot: product_shop có thêm 1 row mới chứa giá trị $shopId và $productId.</p>\r\n<p>Ngược lại muốn attach Product và Shop ta làm ngược lại:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$product</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Product<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$productId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$product</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">shops</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">attach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$shopId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Cũng giả sử như trên nhưng thay vì muốn thêm 1 sản phẩm, ta muốn thêm nhiều sản phẩm có id là $productId1,&nbsp;$productId2,&nbsp;$productId3 thì đơn giản như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Shop<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$shopId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">attach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$productId1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$productId2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$productId3</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Nếu bảng Pivot ngoài product_id và shop_id mà bạn còn thêm trường a, b, c&nbsp; mà bạn muốn thêm thông tin cho trường đó thì đơn giản như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Shop<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$shopId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// attach một</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">attach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$productId</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'a\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'value\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'b\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'value\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'c\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'value\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// attach nhiều</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">attach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$productId1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$productId2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$productId3</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'a\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'value\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'b\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'value\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'c\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'value\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"3.2_detach()_-_xóa\">3.2 detach() - xóa</h3>\r\n<p>Ngược lại với attach,&nbsp;detach cũng hỗ trợ xóa 1 hoặc nhiều records trong bảng Pivot (product_shop).</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Shop<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// xóa một sản phẩm ra khỏi shop</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">detach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// xóa nhiều sản phẩm ra khỏi shop</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">detach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$productId1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$productId2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$productId3</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// xóa tất cả sản phẩm ra khỏi shop</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">detach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"3.3_sync()_-_đồng_bộ\">3.3 sync() - đồng bộ</h3>\r\n<p>Sync là sự kết hợp giữa attch và detach ở trên. Khi truyền vào tham số là $productId, hoặc mảng tham số [<span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">$productId1,&nbsp;$productId2,&nbsp;$productId3] thì sync sẽ kiểm tra, cái nào không có sẽ loại bỏ, cái nào đang có thì giữ nguyên và cái nào mới thì thêm vào.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">Giả sử hiện tại Shop có $id là 1 hiện đang liên kết với các Product có $id là 1 và 2</span></p>\r\n<table class=\"table\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 72px;\" border=\"1\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 24px;\">id</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 24px;\">product_id</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 24px;\">shop_id</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 24px;\">1</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 24px;\">1</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 24px;\">1</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style=\"height: 24px;\">\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 24px;\">2</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 24px;\">2</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 33.3333%; height: 24px;\">1</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p>Bây giờ ta muốn Shop có $id là 1 chỉ bán Product có $id là 2 và 3 ta làm như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Shop<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// đồng bộ</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">sync</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Tương đương với</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">attach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">detach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Khi bạn muốn sync nhưng kiểm tra có mới thì thêm vào, còn không có thì cũng đừng có xóa đi thì làm như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Shop<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">find</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// đồng bộ</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">syncWithoutDetaching</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Tương đương với</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">attach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"3.4_Toggle_-_Bật_tắt\">3.4 Toggle - Bật tắt</h3>\r\n<p>Giống như công tắc, đang bật thì tắt mà đang tắt thì bật. Vậy thì nếu đã attach rồi thì detach và ngược lại.</p>\r\n<p>Giả sử giống như ở trên: hiện tại Shop có $id là 1 hiện đang liên kết với các Product có $id là 1 và 2</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Giả sử hiện tại Shop có $id là 1 hiện đang liên kết với các Product có $id là 1 và 2</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">toggle</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Tương đương với</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">attach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$shop</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">products</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">detach</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Cảm ơn bạn đã đọc hết bài viết này =))</p>\r\n            </div>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/pivot-tables-va-moi-quan-he-nhieu-nhieu-many-to-many-relationship-trong-laravel', 2, 1, 'Pivot tables và mối quan hệ nhiều-nhiều (many-to-many relationship) trong Laravel', 'H&ocirc;m nay ch&uacute;ng ta c&ugrave;ng t&igrave;m hiểu về Eloquent trong Laravel với mối quan hệ nhiều - nhiều (many to many relationship). Thoạt đầu, c&oacute; thể sẽ hơi lạ v&agrave; kh&oacute; định nghĩa cụm từ pivot tables nhưng t&iacute;nh năng n&', 'pivot-tables-va-moi-quan-he-nhieu-nhieu-many-to-many-relationship-trong-laravel', '[\"\"]', 1, 'H&ocirc;m nay ch&uacute;ng ta c&ugrave;ng t&igrave;m hiểu về Eloquent trong Laravel với mối quan hệ nhiều - nhiều (many to many relationship). Thoạt đầu, c&oacute; thể sẽ hơi lạ v&agrave; kh&oacute; định nghĩa cụm từ pivot tables nhưng t&iacute;nh năng n&a');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(45, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:03', '2019-08-11 14:36:18', 1, 'Laravel 5.7 Cải thiện thông báo lỗi', 'laravel-57-cai-thien-thong-bao-loi', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>Laravel 5.7 gi&uacute;p việc theo d&otilde;i c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o lỗi dễ d&agrave;ng hơn bao giờ hết nguy&ecirc;n do l&agrave; bởi v&igrave; c&aacute;c cuộc gọi động (dynamic call) đến c&aacute;c Eloquent models.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Xem h&igrave;nh ảnh dưới đ&acirc;y, bạn sẽ thấy r&otilde; r&agrave;ng hơn về lỗi do bị thiếu phương thức (method) g&acirc;y ra thay v&igrave;&nbsp;nhầm lẫn b&aacute;o lỗi do đối tượng nằm b&ecirc;n dưới g&acirc;y ra:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/image/posts/laravel/laravel-5-7-cai-thien-thong-bao-loi.png\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel/laravel-5-7-cai-thien-thong-bao-loi.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ở phi&ecirc;n bản 5.6 giả sử trong đoạn code của ch&uacute;ng ta c&oacute; đoạn viết như sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">App\\<span class=\"token package\">User</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">forst</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngay lập tức ta nhận được ngay message dưới đ&acirc;y:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">BadMethodCallException with message &#39;Method Illuminate/Database/Query/Builder::forst does not exist.&#39;</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Qu&aacute; mơ hồ v&agrave; kh&oacute; hiểu phải kh&ocirc;ng n&agrave;o, class App\\User kế thừa từ h&agrave;ng đống class kh&aacute;c v&agrave; Builder ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; class nằm ở tầng s&acirc;u nhất. Vậy cho n&ecirc;n khi gọi đến phương thức chưa được định nghĩa, hệ thống b&aacute;o lỗi sẽ l&ocirc;i thằng cuối c&ugrave;ng ra chịu trận m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng phải l&agrave; ch&iacute;nh ngay d&ograve;ng code bị lỗi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kể từ phi&ecirc;n bản Laravel 5.7 sẽ cải thiện c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o lỗi n&agrave;y trong c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh phần của framework Laravel.<br />\r\nXin gửi lời cảm ơn to lớn đến&nbsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/joseph_silber\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Joseph Silber\">Joseph Silber</a>&nbsp;d&agrave;nh cho cộng đồng Laravel</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-5-7-cai-thien-thong-bao-loi', 1, 1, 'Laravel 5.7 Cải thiện thông báo lỗi', 'Laravel 5.7 gi&uacute;p việc theo d&otilde;i c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o lỗi dễ d&agrave;ng hơn bao giờ hết nguy&ecirc;n do l&agrave; bởi v&igrave; c&aacute;c cuộc gọi động (dynamic call) đến c&aacute;c Eloquent models.', 'laravel-57-cai-thien-thong-bao-loi', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Laravel 5.7 gi&uacute;p việc theo d&otilde;i c&aacute;c th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o lỗi dễ d&agrave;ng hơn bao giờ hết nguy&ecirc;n do l&agrave; bởi v&igrave; c&aacute;c cuộc gọi động (dynamic call) đến c&aacute;c Eloquent models.'),
(46, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:05', '2019-08-11 14:36:53', 1, 'Laravel 5.7 Callable Action URLs', 'laravel-57-callable-action-urls', '<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n              <p>Để bắt đầu một website <strong>Laravel</strong>, chúng ta phải định nghĩa các routes cho website và khi số lượng routes bắt đầu nhiều lên thì việc quản lý bắt đầu phức tạp dần. Nhất là khi ở ngoài view chúng ta phải sinh (generate) url ở nhiều nơi.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Laravel</strong> cung cấp các phương thức generate route như: <code>url()</code>, <code>route()</code>, <code>action()</code>. Trong đó <strong>url</strong> và <strong>route</strong> có lẽ là 2 thứ anh em xài nhiều nhất nhỉ. Chung nói qua một chút về generate route bằng phương thức <code>action()</code> helper này nhé.</p>\r\n<p>Giả sử bạn định nghĩa 2 route sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// không có parameter</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'/posts\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'PostsController@index\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// có parameter</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'/posts/{slug}\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'PostsController@show\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Như vậy chúng ta sẽ có 2 url ngoài web như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-markup\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-markup\">// không có parameter\r\nhttps://chungnguyen.xyz/posts\r\n// có parameter\r\nhttps://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-5-7-callable-action-urls</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Để generate 2 url trên bằng phương thức <code>action()</code> phiên bản <strong>Laravel 5.6</strong> trở về trước ta làm như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// không có parameter</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$url</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">action</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'PostsController@index\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// có parameter</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$url</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">action</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'PostsController@show\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'slug\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'laravel-5-7-callable-action-urls\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Ở phiên bản Laravel 5.7 sẽ có 1 sự thay đổi, ta có thể gọi nó là \"<strong>callable array syntax</strong>\" (<span style=\"color: #0f2149; font-family: \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem;\">cú pháp mảng có thể gọi</span><span style=\"font-size: 1rem;\">) như sau:</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// không có parameter</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$url</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">action</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>PostsController<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'index\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// có parameter</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$url</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">action</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>PostsController<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'show\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'slug\'</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'laravel-5-7-callable-action-urls\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Một lợi ích của định dạng \"callable array syntax\" mới là khả năng điều hướng trực tiếp đến <strong>Controller</strong> nếu bạn sử dụng trình soạn thảo văn bản hoặc IDE hỗ trợ điều hướng mã (code navigation).</p>\r\n<p>Bạn có thể tìm thấy nó trong tài liệu sắp tới để <a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/master/urls#urls-for-controller-actions\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">tạo URL</a> và nếu bạn quan tâm đến các thay đổi code được thực hiện để hỗ trợ tính năng này, bạn có thể checkout pull request này <a href=\"https://github.com/laravel/framework/pull/24738\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">5.7 Tuple notation for UrlGenerator actions</a>.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">Tham khảo:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://laravel-news.com/callable-action-urls\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">laravel-news</a></p>\r\n            </div>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-5-7-callable-action-urls', 1, 1, 'Laravel 5.7 Callable Action URLs', 'Để bắt đầu một website Laravel, ch&uacute;ng ta phải định nghĩa c&aacute;c routes cho website v&agrave; khi số lượng routes bắt đầu nhiều l&ecirc;n th&igrave; việc quản l&yacute; bắt đầu phức tạp dần. Nhất l&agrave; khi ở ngo&agrave;i view ch&uacute;ng ta', 'laravel-57-callable-action-urls', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Để bắt đầu một website Laravel, ch&uacute;ng ta phải định nghĩa c&aacute;c routes cho website v&agrave; khi số lượng routes bắt đầu nhiều l&ecirc;n th&igrave; việc quản l&yacute; bắt đầu phức tạp dần. Nhất l&agrave; khi ở ngo&agrave;i view ch&uacute;ng ta');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(47, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:08', '2019-08-11 14:37:28', 1, 'Laravel Excel import 100.000 record mất bao lâu?', 'laravel-excel-import-100000-record-mat-bao-lau', '<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n              <p>Trên các group trên mạng, mình thấy các bạn hay than thở là có cách nào import nhanh không chứ sao mới có vài nghìn record mà đã mất rất nhiều thời gian rồi!! Nên hôm nay rảnh rổi mình quyết định thử xem là mất bao lâu.</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"Chuẩn_bị\">Chuẩn bị</h2>\r\n<p>File excel 1 trăm ngàn record (<a href=\"http://eforexcel.com/wp/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/100000-Sales-Records.zip\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">tải về - mình có đính kèm trong source code</a>) nặng 12 MB, có 14 cột</p>\r\n<h2 id=\"Bắt_đầu_thôi.\">Bắt đầu thôi.</h2>\r\n<h3 id=\"Bước_1:_Tạo_project_laravel_mới\">Bước 1: Tạo project laravel mới</h3>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-bash\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-bash\">composer create-project --prefer-dist laravel/laravel excel-import-100000-record-sample</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"Bước_2:_Tạo_database\">Bước 2: Tạo database</h3>\r\n<p>Tạo database có tên là:&nbsp;excel-import-100000-record sau đó config trong file <code>.env</code></p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-markup\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-markup\">DB_CONNECTION=mysql\r\nDB_HOST=127.0.0.1\r\nDB_PORT=3306\r\nDB_DATABASE=excel-import-1million-record\r\nDB_USERNAME=root\r\nDB_PASSWORD=</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"Bước_3:_Tạo_bảng_imports_bằng_migration\">Bước 3: Tạo bảng imports bằng migration</h3>\r\n<p>Mình sẽ tạo 1 bảng có tên là: <code>imports</code> có chưa 14 cột tương ứng với 14 cột trong file excel ở trên kia.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-bash\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-bash\">php artisan make:migration create_imports_table --create<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>imports</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>File&nbsp;xxxx_xx_xx_xxxxxx_create_imports_table.php sẽ sinh tự động, mình sẽ chỉnh sửa một chút như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Support<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Facades<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Schema</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Database<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Schema<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Blueprint</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Database<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Migrations<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Migration</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">CreateImportsTable</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Migration</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Run the migrations.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">up</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        Schema<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'imports\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Blueprint <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">increments</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'id\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col1\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col2\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col3\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col4\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col5\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col6\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col7\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col8\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col9\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col10\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col11\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col12\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col13\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$table</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">string</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col14\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Reverse the migrations.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">down</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        Schema<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">dropIfExists</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'imports\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Trong file laravelcms\\app\\Providers\\AppServiceProvider.php function boot() thêm dòng này để chạy migrate khỏi bị lỗi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">boot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    \\<span class=\"token package\">Schema</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">defaultStringLength</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">191</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Chạy migrate</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-bash\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-bash\">php artisan migrate</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"Bước_4:_Cài_thư_viện_Excel\">Bước 4: Cài thư viện Excel</h3>\r\n<p>Mình sẽ cài thư viện&nbsp;Laravel-Excel bằng cách chạy artisan command</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-bash\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-bash\">composer require maatwebsite/excel</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"Bước_5:_Đọc_file_excel_và_lưu_vào_database\">Bước 5: Đọc file excel và lưu vào database</h3>\r\n<p>Vì khi chạy không thông qua giao diện nên mình sẽ tạo 1 command excel:import như sau:</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-bash\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-bash\">php artisan make:command ImportExcel --command<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>excel:import</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Sau khi file <code>app\\Console\\Commands\\ImportExcel.php</code> được tự động sinh ra, mình sẽ viết logic cho nó như sau</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-php\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Console<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Commands</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Console<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Command</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ImportExcel</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">extends</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Command</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * The name and signature of the console command.\r\n     *\r\n     * @var string\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$signature</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'excel:import\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * The console command description.\r\n     *\r\n     * @var string\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$description</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Command description\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Create a new command instance.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">__construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">parent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">__construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Execute the console command.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return mixed\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">handle</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token function\">ini_set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'memory_limit\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'-1\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token function\">set_time_limit</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">300</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Thời gian bắt đầu</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">showTime</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Đọc file excel</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$inputFileName</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">public_path</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$path</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'100000 Sales Records.csv\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$reader</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>PhpOffice<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>PhpSpreadsheet<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Reader<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Csv</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$reader</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">setSheetIndex</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$spreadsheet</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$reader</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">load</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$inputFileName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Load xong file</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">showTime</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Nạp rows</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$rows</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$spreadsheet</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">getSheet</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">toArray</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">showTime</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$arrKeys</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col1\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col2\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col3\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col4\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col5\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col6\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col7\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col8\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col9\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col10\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col11\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col12\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col13\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'col14\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$count</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">count</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$rows</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">foreach</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$rows</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$key</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$row</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token variable\">$insert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">array_combine</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$arrKeys</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$row</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n            <span class=\"token comment\">// Cứ mỗi 1000 rows thì insert db 1 lần</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$key</span><span class=\"token operator\">%</span><span class=\"token number\">1000</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">999</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$key</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$count</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n                \\<span class=\"token package\">DB</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'imports\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">insert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$insert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n                <span class=\"token variable\">$insert</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Done</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">showTime</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">showTime</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">microtime</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$micro</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">sprintf</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"%06d\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$t</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token function\">floor</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$t</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$d</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>DateTime</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> <span class=\"token function\">date</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Y-m-d H:i:s.\'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token variable\">$micro</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$t</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">error</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">\'Time: \'</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$d</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">format</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">\"Y-m-d H:i:s.u\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$d</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n</span></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<h3 id=\"Kết_quả\">Kết quả</h3>\r\n<p>Chạy lệnh: <code>php artisan excel:import</code> và cùng xem kết quả nhé</p>\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\" language-bash\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"54\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 54 14\" class=\"d-block mb-2\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" r=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\" language-bash\">// Thời gian bắt đầu\r\nTime: 2018-08-27 15:04:45.989660\r\n// Load xong <span class=\"token function\">file</span>\r\nTime: 2018-08-27 15:05:10.979576\r\n// Nạp rows\r\nTime: 2018-08-27 15:05:28.178913\r\n// Done\r\nTime: 2018-08-27 15:05:37.860093</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div></div></div>\r\n<p>Đọc xong file 12MB, 100.000 rows, 14 cột mất 25 giây.</p>\r\n<p>Insert 100.000 rows vào DB hết gần 10s</p>\r\n<p>Source code cho anh em nào cần:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/nguyentranchung/excel-import-100000-record-sample\">https://github.com/nguyentranchung/excel-import-100000-record-sample</a>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Vậy thôi&nbsp;???</p>\r\n            </div>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-excel-import-100-000-record-mat-bao-lau', 1, 1, 'Laravel Excel import 100.000 record mất bao lâu?', 'Tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c group tr&ecirc;n mạng, m&igrave;nh thấy c&aacute;c bạn hay than thở l&agrave; c&oacute; c&aacute;ch n&agrave;o import nhanh kh&ocirc;ng chứ sao mới c&oacute; v&agrave;i ngh&igrave;n record m&agrave; đ&atilde; mất rất nhiều thời gian', 'laravel-excel-import-100000-record-mat-bao-lau', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Tr&ecirc;n c&aacute;c group tr&ecirc;n mạng, m&igrave;nh thấy c&aacute;c bạn hay than thở l&agrave; c&oacute; c&aacute;ch n&agrave;o import nhanh kh&ocirc;ng chứ sao mới c&oacute; v&agrave;i ngh&igrave;n record m&agrave; đ&atilde; mất rất nhiều thời gian r');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(48, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:10', '2019-08-11 15:26:16', 1, 'Tích hợp Google reCAPTCHA v2  vào dự án Laravel', 'tich-hop-google-recaptcha-v2-vao-du-an-laravel', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<h2 id=\"1._Captcha_là_gì?\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; color: #212529;\">1. Captcha l&agrave; g&igrave;?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>CAPTCHA l&agrave; một c&ocirc;ng cụ x&aacute;c thực tr&ecirc;n website để đảm bảo rằng website của bạn kh&ocirc;ng bị SPAM bằng một c&ocirc;ng cụ tự động. Theo truyền thống captcha l&agrave; một h&igrave;nh ảnh với d&ograve;ng c&aacute;c chữ kh&oacute; ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch bởi một chương tr&igrave;nh tự động, người d&ugrave;ng phải nhập lại d&ograve;ng chữ giống với chữ tr&ecirc;n h&igrave;nh ảnh để chứng minh họ kh&ocirc;ng phải l&agrave; c&aacute;i m&aacute;y. CAPTCHA truyền thống c&oacute; thể đ&aacute;p ứng được y&ecirc;u cầu đặt ra tuy nhi&ecirc;n đ&ocirc;i khi kh&aacute; phiền phức, c&aacute;c d&ograve;ng chữ CAPTCHA đ&ocirc;i khi rất kh&oacute; đọc đối với người d&ugrave;ng.</p>\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Hình ảnh một CAPTCHA truyền thống\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/recaptcha/tich-hop-google-recaptcha-v2-vao-du-an-laravel-05.png\" title=\"Hình ảnh một CAPTCHA truyền thống\" />\r\n<figcaption><span style=\"text-align: left; background-color: #ffffff;\">H&igrave;nh ảnh một CAPTCHA truyền thống</span></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"2._reCaptcha\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; color: #212529;\">2. reCaptcha</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>reCAPTCHA</strong> l&agrave; một dịch vụ <strong>CAPTCHA của Google</strong> miễn ph&iacute; gi&uacute;p website của bạn chống lại SPAM, c&aacute;c đăng k&yacute; độc hại, hoặc c&aacute;c h&igrave;nh thức tấn c&ocirc;ng kh&aacute;c, nơi m&agrave; c&aacute;c chương tr&igrave;nh tấn c&ocirc;ng cố gắng che giấu bản th&acirc;n tạo ra c&aacute;c h&agrave;nh vi giống con người. reCAPTCHA với giao diện đơn giản, c&oacute; thể dễ d&agrave;ng th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o blog, forum hoặc website của bạn,...</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/image/posts/recaptcha/recaptcha-google.gif\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/recaptcha/recaptcha-google.gif\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>H&igrave;nh minh họa dưới đ&acirc;y m&ocirc; tả nguy&ecirc;n tắc hoạt động của reCAPTCHA:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/image/posts/recaptcha/tich-hop-google-recaptcha-v2-vao-du-an-laravel-06.png\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/recaptcha/tich-hop-google-recaptcha-v2-vao-du-an-laravel-06.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"3._Tích_hợp_reCaptcha_vào_Laravel\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; color: #212529;\">3. T&iacute;ch hợp reCaptcha v&agrave;o Laravel</h2>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"3.1_Đăng_ký_site_key_và_secret_key\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; color: #212529;\">3.1 Đăng k&yacute; site key v&agrave; secret key</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Truy cập trang&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin\">https://www.google.com/recaptcha/admin</a>&nbsp;v&agrave; tiến h&agrave;nh đăng k&yacute;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu lười bạn cũng c&oacute; thể d&ugrave;ng site key v&agrave; secret key TEST do Google cung cấp, nhưng khi public th&igrave; nhớ đăng k&yacute; nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>site key: 6LeIxAcTAAAAAJcZVRqyHh71UMIEGNQ_MXjiZKhI</li>\r\n	<li>secret key: 6LeIxAcTAAAAAGG-vFI1TnRWxMZNFuojJ4WifJWe</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"3.2_Tạo_project_Laravel\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; color: #212529;\">3.2 Tạo project Laravel</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch&uacute; &yacute;: nếu bạn đ&atilde; c&oacute; sẵn project Laravel rồi th&igrave; bỏ qua bước n&agrave;y đến bước 3.3 nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px;\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">composer create-project --prefer-dist laravel/laravel recaptcha</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"3.3_Tạo_database_recaptcha\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; color: #212529;\">3.3 Tạo database recaptcha</h3>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/image/posts/recaptcha/tich-hop-google-recaptcha-v2-vao-du-an-laravel-04.png\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/recaptcha/tich-hop-google-recaptcha-v2-vao-du-an-laravel-04.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mở file&nbsp;<code style=\"font-size: 14px;\">.env</code>&nbsp;v&agrave; sửa lại th&ocirc;ng tin database</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px;\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">DB_CONNECTION=mysql\r\nDB_HOST=127.0.0.1\r\nDB_PORT=3306\r\nDB_DATABASE=recaptcha\r\nDB_USERNAME=root\r\nDB_PASSWORD=</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"3.4_Run_migrate\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; color: #212529;\">3.4 Run migrate</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong file <code>recaptcha\\app\\Providers\\AppServiceProvider.php</code> function&nbsp;<code>boot()</code> bạn th&ecirc;m d&ograve;ng sau để chạy migrate khỏi bị lỗi</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">boot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        \\<span class=\"token package\">Schema</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">defaultStringLength</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">191</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Chạy <code>artisan</code> command sau</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px;\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">php artisan migrate</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Run migrate m&agrave; gặp lỗi&nbsp;1071 - Specified key was too long; max key length is 767 bytes th&igrave; xem b&agrave;i viết n&agrave;y nh&eacute;&nbsp;<a href=\"/go/THJ7Xl\" title=\"Lỗi Laravel: 1071 - Specified key was too long; max key length is 767 bytes\"><strong>Lỗi Laravel: 1071 - Specified key was too long; max key length is 767 bytes</strong></a></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"3.5_Cài_gói_guzzlehttp\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; color: #212529;\">3.5 C&agrave;i g&oacute;i&nbsp;guzzlehttp</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Để x&aacute;c minh phản hồi của người d&ugrave;ng, ch&uacute;ng ta cần gửi request đến Google api n&ecirc;n cần d&ugrave;ng g&oacute;i n&agrave;y. Th&ecirc;m g&oacute;i n&agrave;y v&agrave;o composer</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px;\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">cd recaptcha\r\ncomposer require guzzlehttp/guzzle</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"3.6_Khai_báo_site_key_và_secret_key_Google_reCaptcha\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; color: #212529;\">3.6 Khai b&aacute;o site key v&agrave; secret key Google reCaptcha</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Mở file&nbsp;<code style=\"font-size: 14px;\">.env</code>&nbsp;v&agrave; th&ecirc;m d&ograve;ng sau v&agrave;o cuối file</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px;\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">GOOGLE_RECAPTCHA_KEY=6LeIxAcTAAAAAJcZVRqyHh71UMIEGNQ_MXjiZKhI\r\nGOOGLE_RECAPTCHA_SECRET=6LeIxAcTAAAAAGG-vFI1TnRWxMZNFuojJ4WifJWe</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"3.7_Tích_hợp_reCaptcha_vào_validate_form_đăng_ký\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; color: #212529;\">3.7 T&iacute;ch hợp reCaptcha v&agrave;o validate form đăng k&yacute;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Chạy l&ecirc;n artisan command sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px;\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">php artisan make:auth</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong&nbsp;<code style=\"font-size: 14px;\">recaptcha\\resources\\views\\layouts\\app.blade.php</code>&nbsp;phần&lt;head&gt; tag th&ecirc;m đoạn script n&agrave;y v&agrave;o:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px;\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&quot;</span>https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">&quot;</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">async</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">defer</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong&nbsp;<code style=\"font-size: 14px;\">recaptcha\\resources\\views\\auth\\register.blade.php</code>&nbsp;ta chỉnh sửa 1 ch&uacute;t bằng c&aacute;ch th&ecirc;m tag Google reCaptcha v&agrave;o</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px;\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0