er\">http://localhost/recaptcha/public/register</a>&nbsp;bạn sẽ thấy như thế n&agrave;y l&agrave; ok</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/image/posts/recaptcha/tich-hop-google-recaptcha-v2-vao-du-an-laravel-03.png\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/recaptcha/tich-hop-google-recaptcha-v2-vao-du-an-laravel-03.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"3.8_Validate_phía_Server\" style=\"font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\'; color: #212529;\">3.8 Validate ph&iacute;a Server</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau khi t&iacute;ch v&agrave;o n&uacute;t&nbsp;I&#39;m not a robot v&agrave; nhấn n&uacute;t Register sẽ gửi request l&ecirc;n server để xử l&yacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tạo mới reCaptcha validate rule</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px;\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">php artisan make:rule ValidRecaptcha</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong file&nbsp;<code style=\"font-size: 14px;\">recaptcha\\app\\Http\\Controllers\\Auth\\RegisterController.php</code>&nbsp;function&nbsp;<code style=\"font-size: 14px;\">validator</code>&nbsp;th&ecirc;m&nbsp;<code style=\"font-size: 14px;\">&#39;g-recaptcha-response&#39; =&gt; [&#39;required&#39;, new \\App\\Rules\\ValidRecaptcha]</code></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px;\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">    <span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">validator</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">array</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$data</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> Validator<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">make</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$data</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;name&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;required|string|max:255&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;email&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;required|string|email|max:255|unique:users&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;password&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;required|string|min:6|confirmed&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;g-recaptcha-response&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;required&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Rules<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>ValidRecaptcha</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Tiến h&agrave;nh định nghĩa rule cho class&nbsp;<code style=\"font-size: 14px;\">ValidRecaptcha</code>&nbsp;(<em>recaptcha\\app\\Rules\\ValidRecaptcha.php</em>)</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-spacing: 0px;\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Rules</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Contracts<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Validation<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Rule</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">GuzzleHttp<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Client</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">ValidRecaptcha</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">implements</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Rule</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Create a new rule instance.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return void\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">__construct</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">//</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Determine if the validation rule passes.\r\n     *\r\n     * @param  string  $attribute\r\n     * @param  mixed  $value\r\n     * @return bool\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">passes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$attribute</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$value</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Khởi tạo http client</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$client</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Client</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;base_uri&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;https://google.com/recaptcha/api/&#39;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Gửi dữ liệu đến cho google recaptcha xử l&yacute;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$response</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$client</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">post</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;siteverify&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;query&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n                <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;secret&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token function\">env</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;GOOGLE_RECAPTCHA_SECRET&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n                <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;response&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$value</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Google reCaptcha trả về kết quả đ&uacute;ng/sai</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">json_decode</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$response</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">getBody</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">success</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Get the validation error message.\r\n     *\r\n     * @return string\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">message</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Message th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o khi kết quả trả về l&agrave; sai</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;ReCaptcha verification failed.&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"Done!\">Done!</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Bạn thử đăng k&yacute; user mới thử xem ok chưa nh&eacute;!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Source code m&igrave;nh đ&atilde; up l&ecirc;n github, bạn n&agrave;o cần c&oacute; thể checkout về xem lại nha</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/nguyentranchung/laravel-recaptcha-sample\">https://github.com/nguyentranchung/laravel-recaptcha-sample</a>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/tich-hop-google-recaptcha-v2-vao-du-an-laravel', 2, 1, 'Tích hợp Google reCAPTCHA v2  vào dự án Laravel', 'CAPTCHA l&agrave; một c&ocirc;ng cụ x&aacute;c thực tr&ecirc;n website để đảm bảo rằng website của bạn kh&ocirc;ng bị SPAM bằng một c&ocirc;ng cụ tự động. Theo truyền thống captcha l&agrave; một h&igrave;nh ảnh với d&ograve;ng c&aacute;c chữ kh&oacute; ph', 'tich-hop-google-recaptcha-v2-vao-du-an-laravel', '[\"\"]', 1, 'CAPTCHA l&agrave; một c&ocirc;ng cụ x&aacute;c thực tr&ecirc;n website để đảm bảo rằng website của bạn kh&ocirc;ng bị SPAM bằng một c&ocirc;ng cụ tự động. Theo truyền thống captcha l&agrave; một h&igrave;nh ảnh với d&ograve;ng c&aacute;c chữ kh&oacute; ph&');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(49, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:13', '2019-08-11 14:41:55', 1, 'Laravel 5.7 Thay đổi cấu trúc thư mục Resources', 'laravel-57-thay-doi-cau-truc-thu-muc-resources', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>Taylor Otwell <a href=\"https://twitter.com/taylorotwell/status/1024391862445113344\">th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o tr&ecirc;n twitter</a>&nbsp; rằng trong Laravel 5.7 thư mục t&agrave;i nguy&ecirc;n sẽ được l&agrave;m phẳng thay v&igrave; chứa trong thư mục assets như trước:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Laravel 5.7 Resources Directory Changes\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel/laravel-5-7-thay-doi-cau-truc-thu-muc-resources.jpg\" title=\"Laravel 5.7 Resources Directory Changes\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ở phi&ecirc;n bản 5.6 như thế n&agrave;y</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">resources\r\n├── assets\r\n│   ├── js\r\n│   └── sass\r\n├── lang\r\n│   └── en\r\n└── views</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>V&agrave; thư mục Resources sắp tới sẽ tr&ocirc;ng giống như sau trong Laravel 5.7:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">resources\r\n├── js\r\n├── lang\r\n├── sass\r\n└── views</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu bạn đang h&aacute;o hức đ&oacute;n chờ phi&ecirc;n bản Laravel 5.7, bạn c&oacute; thể thay đổi những điều sau đ&acirc;y</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thứ nhất,&nbsp;bạn cần cập nhật cấu h&igrave;nh của Laravel Mix</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-javascript\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> mix <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">&#39;laravel-mix&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\nmix<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">js</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">&#39;resources/js/app.js&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">&#39;public/js&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">sass</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">&#39;resources/sass/app.scss&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">&#39;public/css&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Sau đ&oacute;, bạn cần di chuyển, sắp xếp lại thư mục:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr&ecirc;n terminal (Linux, MacOS)</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">mv resources/assets/* resources\r\nrm -Rf resources/assets/</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Tr&ecirc;n windows (l&agrave;m thủ c&ocirc;ng)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Copy to&agrave;n bộ files, folders c&oacute; trong thư mục assets ra thư mục resources, sau đ&oacute; x&oacute;a thư mục assets đi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sự cập nhật n&agrave;y c&oacute; thể sẽ kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; &yacute; nghĩa với nhiều bạn cho lắm, với c&aacute; nh&acirc;n m&igrave;nh th&igrave; sự l&agrave;m phẳng n&agrave;y, &iacute;t nhiều giảm bớt đi sự ph&acirc;n cấp folder khi code.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">Tham khảo từ:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://laravel-news.com/laravel-5-7-resources-directory-changes\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"laravel-news.com\">laravel-news.com</a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-5-7-thay-doi-cau-truc-thu-muc-resources', 1, 1, 'Laravel 5.7 Thay đổi cấu trúc thư mục Resources', 'Taylor Otwell th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o tr&ecirc;n twitter&nbsp; rằng trong Laravel 5.7 thư mục t&agrave;i nguy&ecirc;n sẽ được l&agrave;m phẳng thay v&igrave; chứa trong thư mục assets như trước:', 'laravel-57-thay-doi-cau-truc-thu-muc-resources', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Taylor Otwell th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o tr&ecirc;n twitter&nbsp; rằng trong Laravel 5.7 thư mục t&agrave;i nguy&ecirc;n sẽ được l&agrave;m phẳng thay v&igrave; chứa trong thư mục assets như trước:');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(50, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:15', '2019-08-11 14:42:35', 1, 'Laravel Routing - Toàn tập về định tuyến trong Laravel', 'laravel-routing-toan-tap-ve-dinh-tuyen-trong-laravel', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>Ch&agrave;o c&aacute;c bạn, chắc hẳn mỗi khi bắt đầu t&igrave;m hiểu về <strong>Laravel</strong> th&igrave; c&aacute;c kiến thức cơ bản như <strong>Routing</strong>, <strong>Middleware</strong>, <strong>Controllers</strong>, <strong>Requests</strong>, <strong>Responses</strong>, <strong>Views</strong> l&agrave; những kh&aacute;i niệm đầu ti&ecirc;n bạn cần phải biết để c&oacute; thể sử dụng v&agrave; l&agrave;m quen với <strong>Laravel</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong b&agrave;i viết n&agrave;y, m&igrave;nh sẽ đi s&acirc;u v&agrave;o t&igrave;m hiểu về việc <strong>định tuyến trong Laravel</strong>.&nbsp;Đầu ti&ecirc;n, mục đ&iacute;ch của Routing l&agrave; để định tuyến c&aacute;c request của người d&ugrave;ng sẽ được đưa đến 1 Controller cụ thể n&agrave;o đ&oacute; để xử l&yacute;. Ở trong <strong>Laravel</strong> ta c&oacute; thể ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n xử l&yacute; c&aacute;c dữ liệu đ&oacute; trong phần <strong>Router</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"Router_được_viết_ở_đâu?\">Router được viết ở đ&acirc;u?</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Phi&ecirc;n bản Laravel 5.2 trở về trước router được viết v&agrave;o file <code>routes.php</code> nằm ở&nbsp;<code>app/Http/routes.php</code>. Kể từ phi&ecirc;nbản Laravel&nbsp;5.3 router được t&aacute;ch ra 1 thư mục ri&ecirc;ng c&oacute; t&ecirc;n l&agrave; <code>routes</code> v&agrave; đồng thời chia nhỏ (<em>api, channels, console, web</em>) c&aacute;c loại router để dễ quản l&yacute;. B&agrave;i viết n&agrave;y&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><code>routes\\web.php</code>: định nghĩa c&aacute;c router tr&ecirc;n tr&igrave;nh duyệt web, sử dụng cookie, session, bảo vệ csrf,...</li>\r\n	<li><code>routes\\api.php</code>: định nghĩa c&aacute;c&nbsp;restful API</li>\r\n	<li><code>routes\\channels.php</code>: d&ugrave;ng cho việc broadcasting</li>\r\n	<li><code>routes\\console.php</code>:&nbsp;l&agrave; nơi để bạn định nghĩa tất cả c&aacute;c Closure based console commands</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"1._Router_cơ_bản\">1. Router cơ bản</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>C&aacute;c router Laravel cơ bản nhất chấp nhận một URI v&agrave; một Closure, cung cấp một phương thức x&aacute;c định rất đơn giản v&agrave; r&otilde; r&agrave;ng:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// http://chungnguyen.xyz/hello</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;hello&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Hello World&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Router Laravel c&oacute; hỗ trợ c&aacute;c phương thức giống với http request method như GET, POST, PUT, PATCH, DELETE, OPTIONS, ...</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$uri</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">post</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$uri</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">put</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$uri</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">patch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$uri</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">delete</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$uri</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">options</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$uri</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$callback</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Ngo&agrave;i ra, laravel cũng hỗ trợ ta định nghĩa một route m&agrave; c&oacute; thể xử l&yacute; nhiều loại method với chung một response bằng c&aacute;ch sử dụng phương thức <code>match</code> v&agrave; <code>any</code>.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Gửi http request get hoặc post đều trả về kết quả l&agrave; match</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">match</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;get&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;post&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;/match&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;match&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Gửi bất kỳ http request method n&agrave;o cũng đều trả về kết quả l&agrave; any</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">any</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;any&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;any&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"1.1_Bảo_vệ_CSRF\">1.1 Bảo vệ CSRF</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Tất cả c&aacute;c router được phủ bởi <code>web</code> middleware sẽ được bảo vệ CSRF với c&aacute;c method POST, PUT, DELETE. Khi bạn gửi request POST, PUT, DELETE l&ecirc;n server m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng k&egrave;m theo crsf token th&igrave; sẽ bị server từ chối v&igrave; l&yacute; do bảo mật, c&aacute;c bạn lưu &yacute; nh&eacute;. Để ch&egrave;n crsf token v&agrave;o form c&aacute;c bạn l&agrave;m như sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>form method<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">&quot;POST&quot;</span> action<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token double-quoted-string string\">&quot;/profile&quot;</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span>\r\n    @csrf\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>form<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"1.2_Chuyển_hướng_Routes\">1.2 Chuyển hướng Routes</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Mục đ&iacute;ch l&agrave; chuyển hướng routes, chẳng hạn bạn kh&ocirc;ng d&ugrave;ng routes đ&oacute; nữa hoặc chuyển sang địa chỉ mới..</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">redirect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;/dia-chi-cu&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;/dia-chi-moi&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$statusCode</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">301</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"1.3_View_Routes\">1.3&nbsp;View Routes</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu route của bạn chỉ đơn thuần muốn trả về 1 view m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; xử l&yacute; logic g&igrave; hết th&igrave; đ&acirc;y l&agrave; c&aacute;ch đơn giản hơn l&agrave; phải trỏ về controller rồi controller lại trả về view.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;/welcome&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;welcome&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;/welcome&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;welcome&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$datas</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;name&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Chung Nguyễn&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"2._Route_có_tham_số\">2. Route c&oacute; tham số</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Route c&oacute; tham số l&agrave; tập hợp 1 số route c&oacute; c&ugrave;ng logic xử l&yacute;, ph&ugrave; hợp cho t&iacute;nh linh động trong PHP.<br />\r\nTham số route lu&ocirc;n lu&ocirc;n phải nằm trong dấu ngoặc nhọn <code>{}</code>&nbsp;v&agrave; c&aacute;c tham số route kh&ocirc;ng được ph&eacute;p chứa k&yacute; tự <code>-</code>&nbsp;nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Route c&oacute; tham số c&oacute; 2 loại l&agrave;:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Bắt buộc:&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #e83e8c; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 14px; background-color: #bfe6ff;\">{ten_tham_so}</span>&nbsp;kh&ocirc;ng truyền tham số khi gọi sẽ bị b&aacute;o lỗi.</li>\r\n	<li>Kh&ocirc;ng bắt buộc (th&ecirc;m dấu <code>?</code> sau t&ecirc;n của parameter):&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #e83e8c; font-family: SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, \'Liberation Mono\', \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 14px; background-color: #bfe6ff;\">{ten_tham_so?}</span>&nbsp;bạn h&atilde;y chắc chắn rằng đ&atilde; khai b&aacute;o gi&aacute; trị mặc định</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// v&iacute; dụ về Route kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; tham số</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;hello/chung&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;hello chung&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;hello/nguyen&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;hello nguyen&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;hello/blog&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;hello blog&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Route c&oacute; tham số bắt buộc</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;hello/{name}&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;hello &#39;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Route c&oacute; tham số kh&ocirc;ng bắt buộc</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;hello/{name?}&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$name</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Chung&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;hello &#39;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"3.1_Ràng_buộc_biểu_thức_chính_quy_cho_tham_số\">3.1&nbsp;R&agrave;ng buộc biểu thức ch&iacute;nh quy cho tham số</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>R&otilde; r&agrave;ng với tham số truyền v&agrave;o, ch&uacute;ng ta muốn giới hạn quy tắc cho tham số để r&agrave;ng buộc bằng method <code>where</code>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;user/{name}&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// giới hạn t&ecirc;n l&agrave; chữ c&aacute;i hoa, thường.</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">where</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;name&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;[A-Za-z]+&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;user/{id}&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// giới hạn id chỉ được l&agrave; số từ 0 - 9</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">where</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;id&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;[0-9]+&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;user/{id}/{name}&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// r&agrave;ng buộc cả id v&agrave; name như đ&atilde; giải th&iacute;ch ở tr&ecirc;n</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">where</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;id&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;[0-9]+&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;name&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;[a-z]+&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h4>R&agrave;ng buộc biểu thức ch&iacute;nh quy to&agrave;n cục (Global)</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Giả sử bạn muốn hễ tham số l&agrave; id th&igrave; phải l&agrave; số từ 0-9 bạn kh&ocirc;ng thể copy-paste m&atilde;i như vậy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bạn n&ecirc;n định nghĩa r&agrave;ng buộc trong h&agrave;m <code>boot</code> của <code>app\\Providers\\RouteServiceProvider.php</code>:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n * Define your route model bindings, pattern filters, etc.\r\n *\r\n * @return void\r\n */</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">boot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">pattern</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;id&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;[0-9]+&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">pattern</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;name&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;[A-Za-z]+&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">parent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">boot</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"4._Đặt_tên_cho_các_Route\">4. Đặt t&ecirc;n cho c&aacute;c Route</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Việc đặt t&ecirc;n cho c&aacute;c route rất c&oacute; &yacute; nghĩa v&agrave; hữu dụng khi bạn muốn thay đổi URI m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng phải thay đổi qu&aacute; nhiều code. V&iacute; dụ: link đăng nhập trang web l&agrave; <a href=\"/login\">https://chungnguyen.xyz/login</a>&nbsp;v&agrave; ở thời điểm n&agrave;o đ&oacute; m&igrave;nh thay đổi th&agrave;nh&nbsp;<code>https://chungnguyen.xyz/dang-nhap</code>&nbsp;như vậy m&igrave;nh sẽ phải đi l&ugrave;ng hết trong code chỗ n&agrave;o c&oacute; <code>/login</code> m&igrave;nh phải đổi th&agrave;nh <code>/dang-nhap</code>. M&igrave;nh khuy&ecirc;n c&aacute;c bạn đặt name cho to&agrave;n bộ route, v&agrave; gọi output route bằng name để quản l&yacute; chặt chẽ c&aacute;c li&ecirc;n kết tr&ecirc;n website của m&igrave;nh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Để đặt t&ecirc;n một route ta sử dụng phương thức <code>name</code></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;user/profile&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;profile&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Tạo_URL_từ_route_đã_đặt_tên\">Tạo URL từ route đ&atilde; đặt t&ecirc;n</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Một khi route đ&atilde; được đặt t&ecirc;n, ta c&oacute; thể sử dụng t&ecirc;n n&agrave;y qua phương thức <code>route</code>:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// Tạo URLs...</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$url</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">route</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;profile&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Tạo Redirects...</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">redirect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">route</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;profile&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu t&ecirc;n route được <strong>định nghĩa với tham số</strong>, bạn phải khai b&aacute;o một đối số thứ hai trong phương thức <code>route</code>. C&aacute;c đối số sẽ được ch&egrave;n v&agrave;o theo đ&uacute;ng thứ tự ch&iacute;nh x&aacute;c tr&ecirc;n URLs:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;user/{id}/profile&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$id</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">//</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;profile&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Tạo URL profile</span>\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$url</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">route</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;profile&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$params</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;id&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Kiểm_tra_route_hiện_tại\">Kiểm tra route hiện tại</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Một khi route đ&atilde; được đặt t&ecirc;n bạn ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n c&oacute; thể kiểm tra request đang gửi tới c&oacute; thuộc name n&agrave;o? v&agrave; code&nbsp;logic theo y&ecirc;u cầu</p>\r\n\r\n<p>V&iacute; dụ: bạn c&oacute; thể kiểm tra name route hiện tại từ middleware:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n * Handle an incoming request.\r\n *\r\n * @param  \\Illuminate\\Http\\Request  $request\r\n * @param  \\Closure  $next\r\n * @return mixed\r\n */</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">handle</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Closure <span class=\"token variable\">$next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$request</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">route</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">named</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;profile&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">//</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"5._Nhóm_route\">5. Nh&oacute;m route</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi c&aacute;c route c&oacute; chung tiền tố, chung middle, chung namespace, ... th&igrave; c&aacute;c bạn n&ecirc;n gom ch&uacute;ng lại với nhau m&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng cần định nghĩa lại ch&uacute;ng tr&ecirc;n mỗi route ri&ecirc;ng.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>V&iacute; dụ chung middleware</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">middleware</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;first&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;second&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">group</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;/&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Uses first &amp; second Middleware</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n    Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;user/profile&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Uses first &amp; second Middleware</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>V&iacute; dụ chung namespace</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;User&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">group</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// controller sẽ sử dụng App\\Http\\Controllers\\User l&agrave;m namespace</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>V&iacute; dụ chung tiền tố:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">prefix</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;admin&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">group</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;users&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// https://chungnguyen.xyz/admin/users</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;settings&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// https://chungnguyen.xyz/admin/settings</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>V&iacute; dụ chung tiền tố name route</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;admin.&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">prefix</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;admin&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">group</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;users&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Tạo url: $url = route(&#39;admin.users&#39;)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;users&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;settings&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// Tạo url: $url = route(&#39;admin.settings&#39;)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;settings&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"6._Truy_cập_route_hiện_tại\">6. Truy cập route hiện tại</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Bạn c&oacute; thể sử dụng phương thức <code>current</code>, <code>currentRouteName</code>, v&agrave; <code>currentRouteAction</code> tr&ecirc;n <code>Route</code> facade để truy cập th&ocirc;ng tin về resquest route xử l&yacute; đang đến:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token variable\">$route</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">current</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$name</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">currentRouteName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token variable\">$action</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">currentRouteAction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-routing-toan-tap-ve-dinh-tuyen-trong-laravel', 1, 1, 'Laravel Routing - Toàn tập về định tuyến trong Laravel', 'Ch&agrave;o c&aacute;c bạn, chắc hẳn mỗi khi bắt đầu t&igrave;m hiểu về Laravel th&igrave; c&aacute;c kiến thức cơ bản như Routing, Middleware, Controllers, Requests, Responses, Views l&agrave; những kh&aacute;i niệm đầu ti&ecirc;n bạn cần phải biết để c&', 'laravel-routing-toan-tap-ve-dinh-tuyen-trong-laravel', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Ch&agrave;o c&aacute;c bạn, chắc hẳn mỗi khi bắt đầu t&igrave;m hiểu về Laravel th&igrave; c&aacute;c kiến thức cơ bản như Routing, Middleware, Controllers, Requests, Responses, Views l&agrave; những kh&aacute;i niệm đầu ti&ecirc;n bạn cần phải biết để c&o');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(51, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:17', '2019-08-11 14:43:16', 1, 'Tìm hiểu cấu trúc thư mục của Laravel', 'tim-hieu-cau-truc-thu-muc-cua-laravel', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<h2 id=\"Giới_thiệu\">Giới thiệu</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Mặc định cấu tr&uacute;c thư mục ứng dụng&nbsp;<strong>Laravel</strong>&nbsp;được thiết kế để x&acirc;y dựng cả ứng dụng nhỏ v&agrave; ứng dụng lớn. Tất nhi&ecirc;n, bạn c&oacute; thể ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n tổ trức lại cấu tr&uacute;c thư mục theo &yacute; bạn muốn.&nbsp;<strong>Laravel</strong>&nbsp;hầu như kh&ocirc;ng &aacute;p đặt những hạn chế về nơi c&aacute;c class nằm ở thư mục n&agrave;o - miễn l&agrave; Composer c&oacute; thể tự động tải được c&aacute;c class.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Models_ở_đâu?\">Thư mục Models ở đ&acirc;u?</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi bắt đầu l&agrave;m việc với Laravel, rất nhiều developer bị bối rối v&igrave; cảm thấy thiếu thiếu một folder&nbsp;<code>models</code>. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n,&nbsp;<strong>Laravel</strong>&nbsp;đ&atilde; cố &yacute; kh&ocirc;ng tạo một folder models đ&oacute;. Ch&uacute;ng ta thấy từ &quot;<em>models</em>&quot; l&agrave; mơ hồ v&igrave; n&oacute; c&oacute; rất nhiều nghĩa kh&aacute;c nhau từ nhiều người kh&aacute;c nhau. Một số developer xem &quot;<em>model</em>&quot; như l&agrave; to&agrave;n bộ logic của ứng dụng, trong khi những s&ocirc; kh&aacute;c th&igrave; xem &quot;<em>models</em>&quot; như l&agrave; c&aacute;c class c&oacute; thể tương t&aacute;c với database.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; l&yacute; do đấy,&nbsp;<strong>Laravel</strong>&nbsp;chọn đặt&nbsp;<strong>Eloquent model</strong>&nbsp;mặc định ở thư mục&nbsp;<code>app</code>, v&agrave; cho ph&eacute;p c&aacute;c developer c&oacute; thể đặt ch&uacute;ng ở nơi kh&aacute;c m&agrave; họ muốn.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"Thư_mục_gốc\">Thư mục gốc</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel/laravel-thu-muc-goc.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_App\">Thư mục App</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Thư mục&nbsp;<code>app</code>, như bạn mong đợi, n&oacute; sẽ chứa tất cả c&aacute;c cốt l&otilde;i trong ứng dụng của bạn. Ch&uacute;ng ta sẽ kh&aacute;m ph&aacute; vhi tiết về n&oacute; sớm th&ocirc;i; tuy nhi&ecirc;n, hầu hết c&aacute;c class trong ứng dụng của bạn đều ở trong đ&acirc;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Bootstrap\">Thư mục Bootstrap</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Thư mục&nbsp;<code>bootstrap</code>&nbsp;chứa những file khởi động của frameword v&agrave; những file cấu h&igrave;nh autoloading. Ngo&agrave;i ra n&oacute; c&ograve;n c&oacute; thư mục&nbsp;<code>cache</code>&nbsp;chứa những file m&agrave; framework sinh ra để tăng hiệu năng như route v&agrave; services cache files.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Config\">Thư mục Config</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Thư mục&nbsp;<code>config</code>, đ&uacute;ng như c&aacute;i t&ecirc;n của n&oacute;, chứa tất cả những file cấu h&igrave;nh. Thật tuyệt vời khi bạn lướt qua tất cả c&aacute;c file của n&oacute; với những cấu h&igrave;nh c&oacute; sẵn cho bạn.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Database\">Thư mục Database</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Thư mục&nbsp;<code>database</code>&nbsp;chứa những file database migration v&agrave; seeds. Nếu bạn muốn, bạn cũng c&oacute; thể sử dụng n&oacute; để tổ chức một cơ sử dữ liệu SQLite.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Thư mục Public</h4>\r\n\r\n<p>Thư mục&nbsp;<code>public&nbsp;</code>chứa file&nbsp;<code>index.php</code>, đ&oacute; l&agrave; điểm mấu chốt cho tất cả c&aacute;c request v&agrave;o ứng dụng của bạn. Ngo&agrave;i ra n&oacute; c&ograve;n chứa một số t&agrave;i nguy&ecirc;n như ảnh, JavaScript, v&agrave; CSS.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Resources\">Thư mục Resources</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Thư mục&nbsp;<code>resources</code>&nbsp;chứa những view v&agrave; raw, những t&agrave;i nguy&ecirc;n chưa compiled như LESS, SASS, hoặc JavaScript. N&oacute; c&ograve;n chứa tất cả c&aacute;c file ng&ocirc;n ngữ trong ứng dụng của bạn.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Routes\">Thư mục Routes</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Thư mục&nbsp;<code>routes</code>&nbsp;chứa tất cả c&aacute;c định nghĩa route trong ứng dụng của bạn. Mặc định, c&oacute; ba file route được th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o với Laravel:&nbsp;<code>web.php</code>,&nbsp;<code>api.php</code>, v&agrave;&nbsp;<code>console.php</code>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>File&nbsp;<code>web.php</code>&nbsp;chứa những routes l&agrave;&nbsp;<code>RouteServiceProvider</code>&nbsp;ở trong&nbsp;<code>web</code>&nbsp;nh&oacute;m middleware, N&oacute; cung cấp c&aacute;c trạng th&aacute;i session, CSRF protection, v&agrave; cookie encryption. Nếu ứng dụng của bạn kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; stateless, RESTful API, th&igrave; hầu hết c&aacute;c routes bạn định nghĩa nằm ở file&nbsp;<code>web.php</code>.</p>\r\n<ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-1450596627252330\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\"><ins id=\"aswift_1_expand\"><ins id=\"aswift_1_anchor\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"175\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_1\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_1\" onload=\"var i=this.id,s=window.google_iframe_oncopy,H=s&amp;&amp;s.handlers,h=H&amp;&amp;H[i],w=this.contentWindow,d;try{d=w.document}catch(e){}if(h&amp;&amp;d&amp;&amp;(!d.body||!d.body.firstChild)){if(h.call){setTimeout(h,0)}else if(h.match){try{h=s.upd(h,i)}catch(e){}w.location.replace(h)}}\" scrolling=\"no\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"698\"></iframe></ins></ins></ins>\r\n\r\n<p>File&nbsp;<code>api.php</code>&nbsp;chứa những routes l&agrave;&nbsp;<code>RouteServiceProvider</code>&nbsp;ở trong&nbsp;<code>api</code>&nbsp;nh&oacute;m middleware, n&oacute; cung cấp rate limiting. Nhữn routes đ&atilde; được x&aacute;c định stateless, v&igrave; vậy những request gửi đến ứng dụng của bạn th&ocirc;ng qua routes sẽ được x&aacute;c thực bằng tokens v&agrave; sẽ kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; quyền truy cập trạng th&aacute;i session.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>File&nbsp;<code>console.php</code>&nbsp;l&agrave; nơi để bạn định nghĩa tất cả c&aacute;c Closure based console commands. Each Closure is bound to a command instance allowing a simple approach to interacting with each command&#39;s IO methods. Mặc d&ugrave; n&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng định nghĩa HTTP routes, n&oacute; định nghĩa console based entry points (routes) trong ứng dụng của bạn.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Storage\">Thư mục Storage</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Thư mục&nbsp;<code>storage</code>&nbsp;chứa c&aacute;c file compiled Blade templates của bạn, file based sessions, file caches, v&agrave; những file sinh ra từ framework. B&ecirc;n trong n&oacute; bao gồm&nbsp;<code>app</code>,&nbsp;<code>framework</code>, v&agrave;&nbsp;<code>logs</code>. Thư mục&nbsp;<code>app</code>d&ugrave;ng để chứa những file sinh ra bởi ứng dụng của bạn. Thư mục&nbsp;<code>framework</code>&nbsp;chứa những file sinh ra từ framework v&agrave; caches. Cuối c&ugrave;ng, thư mục&nbsp;<code>logs</code>&nbsp;chứa những file logs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thư mục&nbsp;<code>storage/app/public</code>&nbsp;lưu những file người d&ugrave;ng tạo ra như ảnh đại diện, n&oacute; phải được để c&ocirc;ng khai. Bạn n&ecirc;n tạo một li&ecirc;n kết tại&nbsp;<code>public/storage</code>&nbsp;đến thư mục n&agrave;y bằng c&aacute;ch sử dụng lệnh&nbsp;<code>php artisan storage:link</code>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Tests\">Thư mục Tests</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Thư mục&nbsp;<code>tests</code>&nbsp;chứa những file tests của bạn. V&iacute; dụ&nbsp;<a href=\"https://phpunit.de/\">PHPUnit</a>&nbsp;n&oacute; cung cấp rất đầy đủ. Mỗi một class test n&ecirc;n chứa hậu tố với từ&nbsp;<code>Test</code>. Bạn c&oacute; thể chạy class test của bạn bằng lệnh&nbsp;<code>phpunit</code>&nbsp;hoặc&nbsp;<code>php vendor/bin/phpunit</code>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Vendor\">Thư mục Vendor</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>The&nbsp;<code>vendor</code>&nbsp;chứa c&aacute;c dependencies của&nbsp;<a href=\"https://getcomposer.org/\">Composer</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"Tìm_hiểu_sâu_hơn_thư_mục_App\">T&igrave;m hiểu s&acirc;u hơn thư mục App</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Phần lớn c&aacute;c ứng dụng của bạn đặt ở thư mục&nbsp;<code>app</code>. Mặc định, thư mục n&agrave;y c&oacute; namespaced l&agrave;&nbsp;<code>App</code>v&agrave; được load tự động bởi Composer sử dụng&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.php-fig.org/psr/psr-4/\">PSR-4 autoloading standard</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thư mục&nbsp;<code>app</code>&nbsp;chứa một v&agrave;i thư mục con b&ecirc;n trong như&nbsp;<code>Console</code>,&nbsp;<code>Http</code>, v&agrave;&nbsp;<code>Providers</code>. H&atilde;y nghĩ về&nbsp;<code>Console</code>&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;<code>Http</code>&nbsp;l&agrave; c&aacute;c thư mục cung cấp AP cho phần code lỗi ứng dụng của bạn. Giao thức HTTP v&agrave; CLI l&agrave; hai cơ chế tương t&aacute;c với ứng dụng của bạn, nhưng n&oacute; kh&ocirc;ng thật sự chứa logic của ứng dụng. Bạn c&oacute; thể hiểu, Ch&uacute;ng ta c&oacute; hay c&aacute;ch để thực thi lệnh đến ứng dụng của bạn. Thư mục&nbsp;<code>Console</code>&nbsp;chứa tất cả c&aacute;c lệnh Artisan của bạn, trong khi thư mục&nbsp;<code>Http</code>&nbsp;chứa controllers, middleware, v&agrave; requests.</p>\r\n<ins data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-1450596627252330\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-adsbygoogle-status=\"done\"><ins id=\"aswift_2_expand\"><ins id=\"aswift_2_anchor\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowtransparency=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"175\" hspace=\"0\" id=\"aswift_2\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" name=\"aswift_2\" onload=\"var i=this.id,s=window.google_iframe_oncopy,H=s&amp;&amp;s.handlers,h=H&amp;&amp;H[i],w=this.contentWindow,d;try{d=w.document}catch(e){}if(h&amp;&amp;d&amp;&amp;(!d.body||!d.body.firstChild)){if(h.call){setTimeout(h,0)}else if(h.match){try{h=s.upd(h,i)}catch(e){}w.location.replace(h)}}\" scrolling=\"no\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"698\"></iframe></ins></ins></ins>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi bạn sử dụng lệnh&nbsp;<code>make</code>&nbsp;Artisan th&igrave; sẽ c&oacute; một loạt c&aacute;c thư mục sẽ được tạo ra b&ecirc;n trong thư mục&nbsp;<code>app</code>. V&iacute; dụ, thư mục&nbsp;<code>app/Jobs</code>&nbsp;sẽ kh&ocirc;ng tồn tại cho đến khi bạn thực thi lệnh&nbsp;<code>make:job</code>&nbsp;Artisan sinh ra một class job.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Rất nhiều class được sinh ra b&ecirc;n trong thư mục&nbsp;<code>app</code>&nbsp;bằng lệnh Artisan . Bạn c&oacute; thể xem lại những lệnh n&agrave;o đang tồn tại bằng lệnh&nbsp;<code>php artisan list make</code>&nbsp;trong terminal.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Console\">Thư mục Console</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Thư mục&nbsp;<code>Console</code>&nbsp;chứa tất cả những file Artisan commands ứng dụng của bạn. Đ&oacute; l&agrave; những lệnh được sinh ra bằng lệnh<code>make:command</code>. Ngo&agrave;i ra n&oacute; c&ograve;n chứa console kernel của ứng dụng, n&oacute; l&agrave; nơi bạn c&oacute; thể chỉnh đăng k&yacute; Artisan commands v&agrave;&nbsp;scheduled tasks&nbsp;được định nghĩa.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Events\">Thư mục Events</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Mặc định thư mục n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng tồn tại, nhưng n&oacute; sẽ được sinh ra bằng lệnh&nbsp;<code>event:generate</code>&nbsp;v&agrave; lệnh&nbsp;<code>make:event</code>. Thư mục&nbsp;<code>Events</code>, như bạn mong đợi, n&oacute; sẽ chứa c&aacute;c&nbsp;event classes. Events c&oacute; thể được sử dụng để th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o c&aacute;c phần kh&aacute;c của ứng dụng của bạn m&agrave; hạnh động đấy nhất định xảy ra, ngo&agrave;i ra n&oacute; khả năng của n&oacute; rất linh hoạt v&agrave; decoupling.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Exceptions\">Thư mục Exceptions</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Thư mục&nbsp;<code>Exceptions</code>&nbsp;chứa c&aacute;c xử l&yacute; exception trong ứng dụng của bạn ngo&agrave;i ra n&oacute; c&ograve;n l&agrave; nơi tốt để bắn ra nhiều exception bởi ứng dụng. Nếu bạn muốn t&ugrave;y chỉnh những exception hoặc rendered, bạn n&ecirc;n chỉnh lại class&nbsp;<code>Handler</code>&nbsp;b&ecirc;n trong thư mục.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Http\">Thư mục Http</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Thư mục&nbsp;<code>Http</code>&nbsp;chứa c&aacute;c controllers, middleware, v&agrave; form requests. Tất cả c&aacute;c logic xử l&yacute; requests v&agrave;o ứng dụng của bạn sẽ nằm ở trong thư mục n&agrave;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"The_Jobs_Directory\">The Jobs Directory</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Mặc định thư mục n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng tồn tại, nhưng n&oacute; sẽ được sinh ra nếu bạn thực thi lệnh&nbsp;<code>make:job</code>Artisan. Thư mục&nbsp;<code>Jobs</code>&nbsp;chứa c&aacute;c&nbsp;queueable jobs&nbsp;ứng dụng của bạn. Jobs c&oacute; thể được xếp h&agrave;ng bởi ứng dụng hoặc để chạy đồng bộ b&ecirc;n trong v&ograve;ng đời request hiện tại. Jobs c&oacute; thể chạy đồng bộ trong khi request hiện tại l&agrave; một &quot;commands&quot; khi thực hiện trong&nbsp;<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Command_pattern\">command pattern</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Listeners\">Thư mục Listeners</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Mặc định thư mục n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng tồn tại, nhưng n&oacute; sẽ được sinh ra nếu bạn thực thi lệnh&nbsp;<code>event:generate</code>hoặc&nbsp;<code>make:listener</code>&nbsp;Artisan. Thư mục&nbsp;<code>Listeners</code>&nbsp;chứa c&aacute;c class xử l&yacute; c&aacute;c&nbsp;events. Event listeners nhận được một thể hiện event v&agrave; thực hiện logic khi hồi đ&aacute;p cho sự kiện đ&atilde; được bắn ra. V&iacute; dụ, một&nbsp;<code>UserRegistered</code>&nbsp;event phải được sử l&yacute; bởi một&nbsp;<code>SendWelcomeEmail</code>&nbsp;listener.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Mail\">Thư mục Mail</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Mặc định thư mục n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng tồn tại, nhưng n&oacute; sẽ được sinh ra nếu bạn thực thi lệnh&nbsp;<code>make:mail</code>Artisan. Thư mục&nbsp;<code>Mail</code>&nbsp;chứa tất cả c&aacute;c class đại diện cho mail được gửi bởi ứng dụng của bạn. Mail objects cho ph&eacute;p bạn đ&oacute;ng g&oacute;i tất cả c&aacute;c logic th&agrave;nh một, một class c&oacute; thể được gửi bởi lệnh&nbsp;<code>Mail::send</code>.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Notifications\">Thư mục Notifications</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Mặc định thư mục n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng tồn tại, nhưng n&oacute; sẽ được sinh ra nếu bạn thực thi lệnh&nbsp;<code>make:notification</code>&nbsp;Artisan. Thư mục&nbsp;<code>Notifications</code>&nbsp;chứa tất cả c&aacute;c &quot;giao dịch&quot; th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o đ&atilde; gửi bởi ứng dụng, v&iacute; dụ đơn giải l&agrave; th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o về event xảy ra trong ứng dụng của bạn. Ngo&agrave;i ra notifications của&nbsp;<strong>Laravel</strong>&nbsp;c&ograve;n c&oacute; thể th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o cho email, Slack, SMS, hoặc lưu trong database.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Policies\">Thư mục Policies</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Mặc định thư mục n&agrave;y kh&ocirc;ng tồn tại, nhưng n&oacute; sẽ được sinh ra nếu bạn thực thi lệnh&nbsp;<code>make:policy</code>Artisan. Thư mục&nbsp;<code>Policies</code>&nbsp;chứa c&aacute;c lớp quy ước cấp quyền ứng dụng của bạn. C&aacute;c quy ước được d&ugrave;ng để quyết định user c&oacute; thể thực hiện h&agrave;nh động đối với một t&agrave;i nguy&ecirc;n n&agrave;o đ&oacute;. Để xem chi tiếp, bạn c&oacute; thể xem tại&nbsp;authorization documentation.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 id=\"Thư_mục_Providers\">Thư mục Providers</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Thư mục&nbsp;<code>Providers</code>&nbsp;chứa tất cả c&aacute;c&nbsp;service providers&nbsp;ứng dụng của bạn. Service providers khởi động ứng dụng của bạn bằng c&aacute;c services trong service container, đăng k&yacute; events, hoặc thực hiện bất kỳ một c&ocirc;ng việc kh&aacute;c để chuẩn bị cho request đến ứng dụng của bạn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi bạn mới c&agrave;i xong project, thư mục đ&atilde; chứa một số providers. Bạn c&oacute; thể thoải m&aacute;i th&ecirc;m providers của bạn v&agrave;o nếu cần.</p>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/tim-hieu-cau-truc-thu-muc-cua-laravel', 1, 1, 'Tìm hiểu cấu trúc thư mục của Laravel', 'Mặc định cấu tr&uacute;c thư mục ứng dụng Laravel được thiết kế để x&acirc;y dựng cả ứng dụng nhỏ v&agrave; ứng dụng lớn. Tất nhi&ecirc;n, bạn c&oacute; thể ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n tổ trức lại cấu tr&uacute;c thư mục theo &yacute; bạn muốn. Laravel hầu nh', 'tim-hieu-cau-truc-thu-muc-cua-laravel', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Mặc định cấu tr&uacute;c thư mục ứng dụng Laravel được thiết kế để x&acirc;y dựng cả ứng dụng nhỏ v&agrave; ứng dụng lớn. Tất nhi&ecirc;n, bạn c&oacute; thể ho&agrave;n to&agrave;n tổ trức lại cấu tr&uacute;c thư mục theo &yacute; bạn muốn. Laravel hầu như'),
(52, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:21', '2019-08-11 14:46:06', 1, 'Hướng dẫn Avatar mặc định của User là tên Viết tắt trên dự án Laravel', 'huong-dan-avatar-mac-dinh-cua-user-la-ten-viet-tat-tren-du-an-laravel', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>C&aacute;c c&aacute;c bạn khi sử dụng Android hoặc c&aacute;c ứng dụng danh bạ tr&ecirc;n điện thoại đều thấy t&ecirc;n của người kh&aacute;c được viết tắt th&agrave;nh avatar của họ. Tr&ocirc;ng kh&aacute; chuy&ecirc;n nghiệp v&agrave; nh&igrave;n cũng hay hay.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>H&ocirc;m nay m&igrave;nh sẽ hướng dẫn c&aacute;c bạn l&agrave;m như vậy với dự &aacute;n tr&ecirc;n Laravel của m&igrave;nh. Bạn c&oacute; thể xem th&agrave;nh quả m&agrave; m&igrave;nh đ&atilde; l&agrave;m tr&ecirc;n dự &aacute;n của m&igrave;nh</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/image/post/doi%20avatar%20mac%20dinh%20cua%20user%20thanh%20chu.JPG\" /><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/post/doi%20avatar%20mac%20dinh%20cua%20user%20thanh%20chu.JPG\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ok, b&acirc;y giờ bắt tay l&agrave;m nh&eacute;. Ở đ&acirc;y m&igrave;nh sẽ sử dụng&nbsp;package&nbsp;<code>laravolt/avatar</code>.&nbsp;Link của package ở đ&acirc;y :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/laravolt/avatar\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/laravolt/avatar</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Để c&agrave;i g&oacute;i n&agrave;y v&agrave;o dự &aacute;n của bạn, chạy lện sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-bash\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-bash\">composer require laravolt/avatar</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Để xem r&otilde; c&aacute;ch c&agrave;i đặt bạn c&oacute; thể l&ecirc;n GitHub m&agrave; m&igrave;nh vừa đưa ở tr&ecirc;n để xem, ở đ&acirc;y m&igrave;nh l&agrave;m tr&ecirc;n Laravel 5.6 n&ecirc;n c&aacute;c bạn x&agrave;i bản laravel cũ hơn th&igrave; xem lại Doc nha.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tiếp theo chạy lệnh sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-bash\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-bash\">php artisan vendor:publish --provider<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">&quot;Laravolt\\Avatar\\ServiceProvider&quot;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Một file config sẽ được tạo tại:&nbsp;&nbsp;<kbd>config/laravolt/avatar.php</kbd></p>\r\n\r\n<p>OK, bạn đ&atilde; c&agrave;i đặt th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng, b&acirc;y giờ điều quan trọng l&agrave; bạn phải tạo th&ecirc;m 1 cột&nbsp;<code>avatar</code>&nbsp;trong bảng&nbsp;user&nbsp;của bạn đ&atilde;. C&aacute;i n&agrave;y tự xử khỏi hướng dẫn. Bạn c&oacute; thể để gi&aacute; trị l&agrave;&nbsp;null, m&igrave;nh v&igrave; dự &aacute;n l&uacute;c trước kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; d&ugrave;ng g&oacute;i n&agrave;y n&ecirc;n để gi&aacute; trị l&agrave;&nbsp;<code>avatar.png</code>&nbsp;để lấy&nbsp;avatar&nbsp;mặc định.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>B&acirc;y giờ bạn v&agrave;o Model&nbsp;<strong>User</strong>&nbsp;để&nbsp;<strong>append</strong>&nbsp;một thuộc t&iacute;nh l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>avatar_link</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$appends</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;avatar_path&#39;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Tiếp theo m&igrave;nh dụng&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Accessors</strong>&nbsp;để kiểm tra gi&aacute; trị của avatar c&oacute; rỗng hoặc l&agrave; gi&aacute; trị mặc định hay kh&ocirc;ng ( v&iacute; dụ gi&aacute; trị của m&igrave;nh l&agrave; avatar.png). Code như sau. Nhớ l&agrave; viết ở trong model&nbsp;<strong>User</strong>&nbsp;lu&ocirc;n nh&eacute;. Bạn để &yacute; t&ecirc;n của&nbsp;<strong>function</strong>&nbsp;m&igrave;nh viết nh&eacute;, đừng sửa t&ecirc;n, nếu sửa th&igrave; sửa lu&ocirc;n c&aacute;i&nbsp;<strong>append</strong>&nbsp;nh&eacute;.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">getAvatarLinkAttribute</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">attributes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;avatar&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;avatar.png&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> Avatar<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">create</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">attributes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;name&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">toBase64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;upload/user/&#39;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">attributes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;user&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;/avatar/&#39;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">attributes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;avatar&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token property\">attributes</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;avatar&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Đoạn c&oacute; ở tr&ecirc;n m&igrave;nh viết nếu gi&aacute; trị mặc định của của cột&nbsp;<strong>avatar</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>avatar.png</strong>&nbsp;c&ograve;n nếu gi&aacute; trị của bạn l&agrave; rổng th&igrave; nhớ ghi l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong>null</strong>&nbsp;hoặc gi&aacute; trị mặc định của bạn. Đoạn&nbsp;<strong>$link</strong>&nbsp;l&agrave; để g&aacute;n&nbsp;<strong>link avatar</strong>&nbsp;của&nbsp;<strong>user</strong>&nbsp;khi họ đổi avatar của họ.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ok vậy l&agrave; xong rồi, b&acirc;y g&aacute;n v&agrave;o View th&ocirc;i</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bạn sẽ g&aacute;n như l&agrave;y, gi&aacute; trị sẽ nằm trong&nbsp;<strong>src</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>img</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&quot;</span>{{ Auth::user()-&gt;avatar_link }}<span class=\"token punctuation\">&quot;</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&quot;</span>user-image<span class=\"token punctuation\">&quot;</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">alt</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&quot;</span>User Image<span class=\"token punctuation\">&quot;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/image/post/doi%20avatar%20mac%20dinh%20cua%20user%20thanh%20chu.JPG\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ở g&oacute;i n&agrave;y v&agrave;o file config bạn c&oacute; c&aacute;c t&ugrave;y chỉnh ở trong đ&oacute;, bạn c&oacute; thể vọc chỉnh sửa thử ra sao. V&agrave; c&oacute; th&ecirc;m một số phương thức ở trong Doc bạn c&oacute; thể đọc th&ecirc;m.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/huong-dan-avatar-mac-dinh-cua-user-la-ten-viet-tat-tren-du-an-laravel', 1, 1, 'Hướng dẫn Avatar mặc định của User là tên Viết tắt trên dự án Laravel', 'C&aacute;c c&aacute;c bạn khi sử dụng Android hoặc c&aacute;c ứng dụng danh bạ tr&ecirc;n điện thoại đều thấy t&ecirc;n của người kh&aacute;c được viết tắt th&agrave;nh avatar của họ. Tr&ocirc;ng kh&aacute; chuy&ecirc;n nghiệp v&agrave; nh&igrave;n cũng h', 'huong-dan-avatar-mac-dinh-cua-user-la-ten-viet-tat-tren-du-an-laravel', '[\"\"]', 1, 'C&aacute;c c&aacute;c bạn khi sử dụng Android hoặc c&aacute;c ứng dụng danh bạ tr&ecirc;n điện thoại đều thấy t&ecirc;n của người kh&aacute;c được viết tắt th&agrave;nh avatar của họ. Tr&ocirc;ng kh&aacute; chuy&ecirc;n nghiệp v&agrave; nh&igrave;n cũng ha'),
(53, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:23', '2019-08-11 14:46:49', 1, 'Hướng dẫn thay đổi ngôn ngữ động trong Laravel', 'huong-dan-thay-doi-ngon-ngu-dong-trong-laravel', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Trong b&agrave;i trước:&nbsp;<a href=\"/posts/da-ngon-ngu-don-gian-trong-laravel\" title=\"Đa ngôn ngữ đơn giản trong Laravel\"><strong>Đa ng&ocirc;n ngữ đơn giản trong Laravel</strong></a></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">M&igrave;nh đ&atilde; hướng dẫn c&aacute;ch viết đa ng&ocirc;n ngữ, nhưng để config ng&ocirc;n ngữ bạn phải v&agrave;o file <code>app.php</code> trong config để sửa lại. H&ocirc;m nay m&igrave;nh sẽ hướng dẫn c&aacute;c bạn c&oacute; thể đổi ng&ocirc;n ngữ động, để ph&ugrave; hợp cho c&aacute;c User c&oacute; thể đổi ng&ocirc;n ngữ theo &yacute; th&iacute;ch.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Ok, Bắt tay v&agrave;o c&ocirc;ng việc. Đầu ti&ecirc;n bạn viết một Route để tạo một session:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;setLocal-{lang}&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$lang</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    Session<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">put</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;lang&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$lang</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">back</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Tiếp theo bạn tạo một Middleware t&ecirc;n l&agrave; Lang hay g&igrave; kh&aacute;c t&ugrave;y bạn</span></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-bash\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-bash\">php artisan make:middleware Lang</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Nội dung của middleware như sau</span></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token php language-php\"><span class=\"token delimiter important\">&lt;?php</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> <span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Http<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Middleware</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Closure</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">Session</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">use</span> <span class=\"token package\">App</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Lang</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n     * Handle an incoming request.\r\n     *\r\n     * @param  \\Illuminate\\Http\\Request  $request\r\n     * @param  \\Closure  $next\r\n     * @return mixed\r\n     */</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">handle</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Closure <span class=\"token variable\">$next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span> Session<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">has</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;lang&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            App<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">setLocale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Session<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;lang&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$next</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Tiếp theo, ta khai b&aacute;o Middleware vừa tạo v&agrave;o&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><code>/app/Http/Kernel.php</code>,<span style=\"color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">v&agrave;o vị tr&iacute; của Middleware web</span></p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">protected</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$middlewareGroups</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;web&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n            \\<span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Http<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Middleware<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>EncryptCookies</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n            \\<span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Cookie<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Middleware<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>AddQueuedCookiesToResponse</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n            \\<span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Session<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Middleware<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>StartSession</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token comment\">// \\Illuminate\\Session\\Middleware\\AuthenticateSession::class,</span>\r\n            \\<span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>View<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Middleware<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>ShareErrorsFromSession</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n            \\<span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Http<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Middleware<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>VerifyCsrfToken</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n            \\<span class=\"token package\">Illuminate<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Routing<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Middleware<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>SubstituteBindings</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n            \\<span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Http<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Middleware<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Lang</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token keyword\">class</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">B&acirc;y giờ test thử, Ban đầu ng&ocirc;n ngữ đang l&agrave; tiếng anh</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/image/post/en.JPG\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Sau đ&oacute; chạy Route đ&atilde; tạo v&agrave; truyển tham số&nbsp;</span><kbd>vn</kbd><span style=\"color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;v&agrave;o</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/image/post/wdd.JPG\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Th&agrave;nh quả</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/image/post/vn.JPG\" /></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; border: 0px initial initial;\">Bạn c&oacute; thể thấy l&agrave; b&acirc;y giờ ng&ocirc;n ngữ đ&atilde; được đổi, rồi đấy ??.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; border: 0px initial initial;\">Cảm ơn c&aacute;c bạn đ&atilde; xem!</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; border: 0px initial initial;\"><a href=\"/posts/da-ngon-ngu-don-gian-trong-laravel\" title=\"Đa ngôn ngữ đơn giản trong Laravel\"><strong>Đa ng&ocirc;n ngữ đơn giản trong Laravel</strong></a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/huong-dan-thay-doi-ngon-ngu-dong-trong-laravel', 1, 1, 'Hướng dẫn thay đổi ngôn ngữ động trong Laravel', 'Trong b&agrave;i trước:&nbsp;Đa ng&ocirc;n ngữ đơn giản trong Laravel', 'huong-dan-thay-doi-ngon-ngu-dong-trong-laravel', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Trong b&agrave;i trước:&nbsp;Đa ng&ocirc;n ngữ đơn giản trong Laravel');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(54, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:26', '2019-08-11 14:47:38', 1, 'Sử dụng toastr với Laravel Mix', 'su-dung-toastr-voi-laravel-mix', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>Nếu đọc qua b&agrave;i n&agrave;y <a href=\"/posts/tao-thong-bao-notification-cho-website-cuc-ngau-bang-thu-vien-jquery\" title=\"Tạo thông báo Notification cho website cực ngầu bằng thư viện jQuery\"><strong>Tạo th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o Notification cho website cực ngầu bằng thư viện jQuery</strong></a>&nbsp;hẳn c&aacute;c bạn sẽ thấy toastr được nhắc đến trong đ&oacute;. Chung&nbsp;sử dụng <strong>toastr</strong> để hiển thị cảnh b&aacute;o trong c&aacute;c ứng dụng web của m&igrave;nh. Bạn c&oacute; thể t&iacute;ch hợp v&agrave;o website dễ d&agrave;ng bằng thẻ link v&agrave; script.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nhưng với Webpack v&agrave; <strong>Laravel</strong>, ch&uacute;ng ta kh&ocirc;ng n&ecirc;n l&agrave;m như thế, kh&ocirc;ng chỉ toastr m&agrave; bất kỳ thư viện n&agrave;o phụ thuộc v&agrave;o jQuery cũng như vậy. C&aacute;ch duy nhất m&igrave;nh c&oacute; thể l&agrave;m cho n&oacute; chạy l&agrave; th&ocirc;ng qua npm - quản l&yacute; tập trung v&agrave; đ&oacute;ng g&oacute;i th&agrave;nh một file duy nhất.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>B&agrave;i viết n&agrave;y giả sử bạn đang c&oacute; một project <strong>Laravel</strong> rồi nh&eacute;, ch&uacute;ng ta sẽ đi v&agrave;o t&iacute;ch hợp toastr v&agrave;o&nbsp;<strong>Laravel web app</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"Install_toastr_thông_qua_npm_hoặc_yarn\">Install toastr th&ocirc;ng qua npm hoặc yarn</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Chọn một trong hai nh&eacute;, nếu bạn sử dụng npm</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-bash\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> toastr --save-dev</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Yarn</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-bash\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-bash\">yarn add toastr</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"Thêm_vào_app.js\">Th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o app.js</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong <code>resources\\assets\\js\\app.js</code> th&ecirc;m d&ograve;ng sau</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-javascript\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-javascript\">window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>toastr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">&#39;toastr&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"Thêm_vào_app.scss_hoặc_app.less\">Th&ecirc;m v&agrave;o app.scss hoặc app.less</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu bạn d&ugrave;ng sass th&igrave; bỏ v&agrave;o file&nbsp;<code>resources\\assets\\sass\\app.scss</code> d&ograve;ng sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-css\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@import</span> <span class=\"token string\">&quot;~toastr/toastr.scss&quot;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Nếu bạn d&ugrave;ng sass th&igrave; bỏ v&agrave;o file <code>resources\\assets\\less\\app.less</code> d&ograve;ng sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-css\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token atrule\"><span class=\"token rule\">@import</span> <span class=\"token string\">&quot;~toastr/toastr.less&quot;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Đến đ&acirc;y bạn chỉ c&ograve;n việc chạy npm run dev để build ra file app.css v&agrave; app.js d&ugrave;ng trong web của bạn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi n&agrave;o cần show th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o chỉ cần viết như vầy l&agrave; được:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-javascript\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-javascript\">toastr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">success</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">&#39;Đăng nhập th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng!&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Coi th&ecirc;m c&aacute;ch viết bằng link demo n&agrave;y:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://codeseven.github.io/toastr/demo.html\">https://codeseven.github.io/toastr/demo.html</a>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>?️?️?️?️</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/su-dung-toastr-voi-laravel-mix', 1, 1, 'Sử dụng toastr với Laravel Mix', 'Nếu đọc qua b&agrave;i n&agrave;y Tạo th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o Notification cho website cực ngầu bằng thư viện jQuery&nbsp;hẳn c&aacute;c bạn sẽ thấy toastr được nhắc đến trong đ&oacute;. Chung&nbsp;sử dụng toastr để hiển thị cảnh b&aacute;o trong c&aacute;', 'su-dung-toastr-voi-laravel-mix', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Nếu đọc qua b&agrave;i n&agrave;y Tạo th&ocirc;ng b&aacute;o Notification cho website cực ngầu bằng thư viện jQuery&nbsp;hẳn c&aacute;c bạn sẽ thấy toastr được nhắc đến trong đ&oacute;. Chung&nbsp;sử dụng toastr để hiển thị cảnh b&aacute;o trong c&aacute;c'),
(55, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:28', '2019-08-11 14:48:14', 1, 'Tại sao Laravel không có thư mục Models', 'tai-sao-laravel-khong-co-thu-muc-models', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>Tại sao <strong>Laravel</strong> kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; <strong>thư mục Models</strong> trong cấu tr&uacute;c chuẩn? c&oacute; lẽ l&agrave; thắc mắc của nhiều anh em khi mới học <strong>Laravel</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Khi mới tiếp cận <strong>Laravel</strong>, nhiều người nhầm lẫn cho rằng cấu tr&uacute;c của <strong>Laravel</strong> bị thiếu mất một thư mục Models b&ecirc;n trong thư mục app. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n việc kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; thư mục đ&oacute; l&agrave; sự cố &yacute; của T&aacute;c giả.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Đội ngũ ph&aacute;t triển của <strong>Laravel</strong> cho rằng, định nghĩa models trong ứng dụng kh&aacute; mơ hồ, chứa đựng c&aacute;c &yacute; nghĩa kh&aacute;c nhau v&iacute; dụ như một số c&aacute;c nh&agrave; ph&aacute;t triển d&ugrave;ng models l&agrave; tập hợp tất cả c&aacute;c xử l&yacute; nghiệp vụ business logic một số kh&aacute;c th&igrave; coi n&oacute; l&agrave; lớp tương t&aacute;c ch&iacute;nh với CSDL.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ch&iacute; v&igrave; thế n&ecirc;n đội ngũ ph&aacute;t tiển Laravel chọn thư mục gốc chứa c&aacute;c Eloquent Model tại app để cho c&aacute;c nh&agrave; ph&aacute;t triển c&oacute; thể đặt n&oacute; ở đ&acirc;u t&ugrave;y &yacute; v&agrave; kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; sự r&agrave;ng buộc cấu tr&uacute;c chuẩn đối với Eloquent Models&nbsp;?</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Để tạo model v&agrave;o thư mục mong muốn ta chỉ cần l&agrave;m như sau (model v&agrave; entity dường như l&agrave; sự lựa chọn nhiều nhất):</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-bash\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-bash\">php artisan make:model Models/Product</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>hoặc</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-bash\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-bash\">php artisan make:model Entities/Product</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Đơn giản chỉ c&oacute; thế&nbsp;???</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/tai-sao-laravel-khong-co-thu-muc-models', 1, 1, 'Tại sao Laravel không có thư mục Models', 'Tại sao Laravel kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; thư mục Models trong cấu tr&uacute;c chuẩn? c&oacute; lẽ l&agrave; thắc mắc của nhiều anh em khi mới học Laravel.', 'tai-sao-laravel-khong-co-thu-muc-models', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Tại sao Laravel kh&ocirc;ng c&oacute; thư mục Models trong cấu tr&uacute;c chuẩn? c&oacute; lẽ l&agrave; thắc mắc của nhiều anh em khi mới học Laravel.'),
(56, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:30', '2019-08-11 14:49:03', 1, 'Laravel 5.5 định nghĩa multiple resource', 'laravel-55-dinh-nghia-multiple-resource', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/image/posts/laravel/laravel-5-7-dinh-nghia-multiple-resource-2.png\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kể từ phi&ecirc;n bản&nbsp;<strong>Laravel 5.5</strong>&nbsp;đ&atilde; bổ sung th&ecirc;m một t&iacute;nh năng mới đ&oacute; l&agrave;&nbsp;định nghĩa multiple resource nhưng chắc &iacute;t bạn biết đến n&egrave;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trước đ&acirc;y với việc định nghĩa nhiều resource routes bạn sẽ phải l&agrave;m thế n&agrave;y</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">resource</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;books&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;BooksController&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">resource</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;genres&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;GenresController&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\nRoute<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">resource</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;authors&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;AuthorsController&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Th&igrave; giờ đ&acirc;y bạn chỉ việc nh&oacute;m ch&uacute;ng lại với nhau để dễ quản l&yacute; như dưới đ&acirc;y</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">resources</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;books&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;BookController&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;genres&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;GenreController&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;authors&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;AuthorController&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Với việc bổ sung th&ecirc;m function <code>resources()</code> trong file vendor\\laravel\\framework\\src\\Illuminate\\Routing\\Router.php. K&egrave;m theo đ&oacute; l&agrave;&nbsp;th&ecirc;m t&ugrave;y chọn chọn cho mỗi resource route trong phi&ecirc;n bản&nbsp;<strong>Laravel 5.7</strong> n&agrave;y.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">/**\r\n * Register an array of resource controllers.\r\n *\r\n * @param  array  $resources\r\n * @param  array  $options\r\n * @return void\r\n */</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">resources</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">array</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$resources</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">array</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$options</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">foreach</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$resources</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">as</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$name</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$controller</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$this</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">resource</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$controller</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$options</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>V&iacute; dụ k&egrave;m th&ecirc;m options cho multiple resource</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">resources</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;books&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;BookController&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;genres&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;GenreController&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;authors&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;AuthorController&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;only&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;except&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;name&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;&#39;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-5-5-dinh-nghia-multiple-resource', 1, 1, 'Laravel 5.5 định nghĩa multiple resource', '', 'laravel-55-dinh-nghia-multiple-resource', '[\"\"]', 1, ''),
(57, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:41', '2019-08-11 14:50:54', 1, 'Laravel gửi email smtp từ Yahoo Mail ?', 'laravel-gui-email-smtp-tu-yahoo-mail', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>H&ocirc;m nay Chung sẽ hướng dẫn mọi người cấu h&igrave;nh gửi mail smtp từ Yahoo trong Laravel nh&eacute;:</p>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"Cho_phép_đăng_nhập_từ_ứng_dụng_kém_bảo_mật_trên_yahoo\">Cho ph&eacute;p đăng nhập từ ứng dụng k&eacute;m bảo mật tr&ecirc;n yahoo</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"https://login.yahoo.com/account/security\">https://login.yahoo.com/account/security</a>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Cho phép đăng nhập từ ứng dụng kém bảo mật trên yahoo\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/yahoo-tat-kem-bao-mat.png\" title=\"Cho phép đăng nhập từ ứng dụng kém bảo mật trên yahoo\" />\r\n<figcaption>Bật l&ecirc;n mới gửi mail được nha</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"Cấu_hình_.env\">Cấu h&igrave;nh .env</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-markup\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-markup\">MAIL_DRIVER=smtp\r\nMAIL_HOST=smtp.mail.yahoo.com\r\nMAIL_PORT=587\r\nMAIL_USERNAME=&quot;chungnguyenblog@yahoo.com&quot;\r\nMAIL_PASSWORD=&quot;***********&quot;\r\nMAIL_ENCRYPTION=tls\r\nMAIL_FROM_ADDRESS=&quot;chungnguyenblog@yahoo.com&quot;</code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<h2 id=\"Test_gửi_mail\">Test gửi mail</h2>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">Route<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">get</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;test&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    \\<span class=\"token package\">Mail</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">raw</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;plain text message&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$message</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$message</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">to</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;admin@chungnguyen.xyz&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Chung Nguyen Blog&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token variable\">$message</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">subject</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Subject&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>Done nh&eacute;! Khi cấu h&igrave;nh c&aacute;c bạn ch&uacute; &yacute; MAIL_USERNAME v&agrave; MAIL_FROM_ADDRESS phải giống nhau nh&eacute; kh&ocirc;ng l&agrave;&nbsp;❌đấy.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-gui-email-smtp-tu-yahoo-mail', 1, 1, 'Laravel gửi email smtp từ Yahoo Mail ?', 'H&ocirc;m nay Chung sẽ hướng dẫn mọi người cấu h&igrave;nh gửi mail smtp từ Yahoo trong Laravel nh&eacute;:', 'laravel-gui-email-smtp-tu-yahoo-mail', '[\"\"]', 1, 'H&ocirc;m nay Chung sẽ hướng dẫn mọi người cấu h&igrave;nh gửi mail smtp từ Yahoo trong Laravel nh&eacute;:'),
(58, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:43', '2019-08-18 04:31:10', 1, 'Laravel  tạo nhiều trang lỗi 404 tùy chỉnh (custom multi 404 errors page) ?', 'laravel-tao-nhieu-trang-loi-404-tuy-chinh-custom-multi-404-errors-page', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>Trong Laravel mặc định url kh&ocirc;ng được t&igrave;m thấy sẽ hiển thị lỗi trang 404. File blade view mặc định được gọi resources\\views\\errors\\404.blade.php.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tuy nhi&ecirc;n trong nhu cầu thực tế c&oacute; trường hợp như thế n&agrave;y: bạn muốn trang admin hiển thị 1 trang lỗi kh&aacute;c v&agrave; trang d&agrave;nh cho user hiển thị một trang lỗi kh&aacute;c. Ta l&agrave;m như sau nh&eacute;:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Trong file: app\\Exceptions\\Handler.php phương thức&nbsp;render() ta sửa như sau:</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Exception <span class=\"token variable\">$exception</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// xuất hiện lỗi 404</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$exception</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">instanceof</span> <span class=\"token class-name\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Symfony<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Component<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>HttpKernel<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>Exception<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>NotFoundHttpException</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// bị lỗi ở admin</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$request</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">is</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;admin/*&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;admin.404&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;user.404&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">parent</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">render</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$request</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$exception</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>$request ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; đối tượng của Request cho n&ecirc;n bạn c&oacute; thể thoải m&aacute;i d&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c c&aacute;ch kh&aacute;c nhau để ph&acirc;n biệt nh&eacute;. Xem th&ecirc;m t&agrave;i liệu về $request tại đ&acirc;y:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://laravel.com/docs/5.6/requests\">https://laravel.com/docs/5.6/requests</a>&nbsp;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>???????</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-tao-nhieu-trang-loi-404-tuy-chinh-custom-multi-404-errors-page', 2, 1, 'Laravel  tạo nhiều trang lỗi 404 tùy chỉnh (custom multi 404 errors page) ?', 'Trong Laravel mặc định url kh&ocirc;ng được t&igrave;m thấy sẽ hiển thị lỗi trang 404. File blade view mặc định được gọi resources\\views\\errors\\404.blade.php.', 'laravel-tao-nhieu-trang-loi-404-tuy-chinh-custom-multi-404-errors-page', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Trong Laravel mặc định url kh&ocirc;ng được t&igrave;m thấy sẽ hiển thị lỗi trang 404. File blade view mặc định được gọi resources\\views\\errors\\404.blade.php.'),
(59, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:46', '2019-08-11 14:52:57', 1, 'Laravel 5.7: Bổ sung phương thức mới cho tùy chỉnh phân trang', 'laravel-57-bo-sung-phuong-thuc-moi-cho-tuy-chinh-phan-trang', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p>Kể từ phi&ecirc;n bản&nbsp;<strong>Laravel 5.7</strong> n&agrave;y, <strong>Laravel</strong> bổ sung th&ecirc;m phương thức mới hỗ trợ cho việc ph&acirc;n trang trở n&ecirc;n dễ d&agrave;ng t&ugrave;y chỉnh hơn trước. Cụ thể ở phi&ecirc;n bản&nbsp;<strong>Laravel 5.6</strong> trở về trước&nbsp;<strong>Laravel</strong> mặc định tại trang đang được active b&ecirc;n cạnh sẽ c&oacute; 3 li&ecirc;n kết</p>\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Laravel 5.7: Bổ sung phương thức mới cho tùy chỉnh phân trang\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/storage/media/31/conversions/laravel-5-7-new-pagination-link-customizations-medium.jpg\" title=\"Laravel 5.7: Bổ sung phương thức mới cho tùy chỉnh phân trang\" />\r\n<figcaption>Mặc định 3 link b&ecirc;n cạnh link active</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Phi&ecirc;n bản&nbsp;<strong>Laravel 5.7</strong> trở đi, bạn c&oacute; thể thoải m&aacute;i t&ugrave;y biến số lượng theo &yacute; muốn bằng c&aacute;ch như sau. Giả sử m&igrave;nh tăng l&ecirc;n 5.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">// trong controller</span>\r\n<span class=\"token keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">index</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token comment\">// ph&acirc;n trang users</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token variable\">$users</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> \\<span class=\"token package\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">\\</span>User</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">paginate</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">10</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token function\">view</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;home&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token function\">compact</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;users&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ngo&agrave;i blade view</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$users</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">onEachSide</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token function\">links</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<figure class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Laravel 5.7: Bổ sung phương thức mới cho tùy chỉnh phân trang\" src=\"https://chungnguyen.xyz/image/posts/laravel/laravel-5-7-new-pagination-link-customizations-3.png\" title=\"Laravel 5.7: Bổ sung phương thức mới cho tùy chỉnh phân trang\" />\r\n<figcaption>Kết quả</figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</body>\r\n</html>', 'uploads/image-post.jpg', 'https://chungnguyen.xyz/posts/laravel-5-7-bo-sung-phuong-thuc-moi-cho-tuy-chinh-phan-trang', 1, 1, 'Laravel 5.7: Bổ sung phương thức mới cho tùy chỉnh phân trang', 'Kể từ phi&ecirc;n bản&nbsp;Laravel 5.7 n&agrave;y, Laravel bổ sung th&ecirc;m phương thức mới hỗ trợ cho việc ph&acirc;n trang trở n&ecirc;n dễ d&agrave;ng t&ugrave;y chỉnh hơn trước. Cụ thể ở phi&ecirc;n bản&nbsp;Laravel 5.6 trở về trước&nbsp;Laravel mặc', 'laravel-57-bo-sung-phuong-thuc-moi-cho-tuy-chinh-phan-trang', '[\"\"]', 1, 'Kể từ phi&ecirc;n bản&nbsp;Laravel 5.7 n&agrave;y, Laravel bổ sung th&ecirc;m phương thức mới hỗ trợ cho việc ph&acirc;n trang trở n&ecirc;n dễ d&agrave;ng t&ugrave;y chỉnh hơn trước. Cụ thể ở phi&ecirc;n bản&nbsp;Laravel 5.6 trở về trước&nbsp;Laravel mặc');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `deleted_at`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `lang`, `title`, `slug`, `content`, `thumbnail`, `link`, `views`, `author`, `seo_title`, `seo_description`, `seo_keywords`, `tags`, `status`, `description`) VALUES
(60, NULL, '2019-08-11 12:22:47', '2019-08-11 14:53:39', 1, 'Đa ngôn ngữ đơn giản trong Laravel', 'da-ngon-ngu-don-gian-trong-laravel', '<html>\r\n<head>\r\n	<title></title>\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"text-left\">\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; border: 0px initial initial;\">Nếu bạn muốn l&agrave;m một dự &aacute;n với nhiều ng&ocirc;n ngữ kh&aacute;c nhau, th&igrave; b&agrave;i viết sau sẽ gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c bạn việc đ&oacute; dể d&agrave;ng hơn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; border: 0px initial initial;\">Trong laravel đ&atilde; hộ trợ sẵn c&aacute;c bạn c&aacute;c Retrieving Translation Strings . V&iacute; dụ trong blade c&oacute; thể viết 3 c&aacute;ch để viết</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">//C&aacute;ch 1</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token function\">__</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Ng&ocirc;n ngữ&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">//C&aacute;ch 2</span>\r\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token function\">trans</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Ng&ocirc;n ngữ&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">//C&aacute;ch 3</span>\r\n@<span class=\"token function\">lang</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;Ng&ocirc;n ngữ&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; border: 0px initial initial;\">Để x&aacute;c định ng&ocirc;n ngữ cho dự &aacute;n của bạn th&igrave; bạn c&oacute; thể sửa tại&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: bold;\">config/app.php&nbsp;</strong>v&agrave; thay đổi c&aacute;c c&agrave;i đặt sau</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token comment\">/**  \r\n*Bạn sửa &#39;en&#39; th&agrave;nh &#39;vn&#39; để thay đổi ng&ocirc;n ngữ sang Tiếng Việt hoặc kh&aacute;c, t&ugrave;y bạn \r\n* &#39;en&#39; hay &#39;vn&#39; hay k&yacute; tự kh&aacute;c t&ugrave;y v&agrave;o thư mục m&agrave; bạn sẽ tạo ph&iacute;a sau  \r\n*/</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">//Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; ng&ocirc;n ngữ thay đổi cho dự &aacute;n</span>\r\n<span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;locale&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;en&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>  \r\n\r\n<span class=\"token comment\">//Ng&ocirc;n ngữ dự ph&ograve;ng, ph&ograve;ng khi ng&ocirc;n ngữ đang sử dụng bị lỗi</span>\r\n<span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;fallback_locale&#39;</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">&#39;en&#39;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; border: 0px initial initial;\">Trong Laravel c&oacute; c&aacute;ch kh&aacute;c để thay đổi ng&ocirc;n ngữ l&agrave; sử dụng</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-php\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-php\">App<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span><span class=\"token function\">setLocale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token variable\">$locale</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"toolbar\">\r\n<div class=\"toolbar-item\"><a>Copy</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; border: 0px initial initial;\">Với c&aacute;ch n&agrave;y bạn c&oacute; thể lấy từ DB rồi đẩy v&agrave;o&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: bold;\">$locale</strong>&nbsp;để c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n tự đổi ng&ocirc;n ngữ theo &yacute; ri&ecirc;ng. Nhưng trong phạm vi b&agrave;i n&agrave;y, m&igrave;nh sẽ hướng dẫn c&aacute;ch để viết đa ng&ocirc;n ngữ như thế n&agrave;o, c&ograve;n việc thay đổi Options sẽ c&oacute; một b&agrave;i kh&aacute;c.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; border: 0px initial initial;\">Ok, giờ v&agrave;o phần ch&iacute;nh, bạn v&agrave;o&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: bold;\">/resources/lang&nbsp;</strong>bạn sẽ thấy một folder c&oacute; s&atilde;n l&agrave;&nbsp;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: bold;\">&lsquo;en&rsquo;</strong>&nbsp;đ&acirc;y l&agrave; thư mục chưa file ng&ocirc;n ngữ &ldquo;Tiếng Anh&rdquo; của dự &aacute;n bạn trong đấy c&oacute; file &ldquo;<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent; word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: bold;\">validation.php</strong>&rdquo; chứa c&aacute;c nội dung tiếng anh khi c&aacute;c bạn Validation trong dự &aacute;n bạn n&ecirc;n Dịch hết theo c&aacute;ch bạn muốn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 25px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; word-wrap: break-word; line-height: 1.8em; color: #414141; font-family: Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; border: 0px initial initial;\">Ngo&agrave;i ra trong đ&oacute; c&oacute; c&aacute;c chuổi t&ecirc;n kiểu c&oacute; hai chấm trước từ đ&oacute; như :</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\">\r\n<pre class=\"language-json\">\r\n<svg class=\"d-block mb-2\" height=\"14\" viewbox=\"0 0 54 14\" width=\"54\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\r\n    <g fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\" transform=\"translate(1 1)\">\r\n    <circle cx=\"6\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FF5F56\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#E0443E\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"26\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#FFBD2E\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#DEA123\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    <circle cx=\"46\" cy=\"6\" fill=\"#27C93F\" r=\"6\" stroke=\"#1AAB29\" stroke-width=\".5\"></circle>\r\n    </g>\r\n    </svg><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token operator\">:</span>attribute\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">:</span>date\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">:</span>min\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">:</span>max\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">:</span>other\r\n<span class=\"token operator\">:</span>digits\r\n<span class